me%20real.%20Rajnath%20Singh%2C%20the%20defence%20minister%2C%20called%20him%20at%20night%20and%20%E2%80%9Csaid%20that%20he%20had%20spoken%20to%20the%20PM%20and%20that%20it%20was%20purely%20a%20military%20decision.%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3EJo%20ucchit%20samjho%20woh%20karo%20%3C%2Fem%3E(Do%20whatever%20you%20deem%20is%20appropriate).%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CI%20had%20been%20handed%20a%20hot%20potato.%20With%20this%20carte%20blanche%2C%20the%20onus%20was%20now%20totally%20on%20me.%20I%20took%20a%20deep%20breath%20and%20sat%20silently%20for%20a%20few%20minutes.%20All%20was%20quiet%20save%20for%20the%20ticking%20of%20the%20wall%20clock%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%20He%20passed%20orders%20to%20the%20Northern%20Army%20Commander%20%E2%80%9Cto%20move%20a%20troop%20of%20our%20tanks%20right%20to%20the%20forward%20slopes%20of%20the%20Pass%20and%20depress%20their%20guns%20so%20that%20the%20PLA%20would%20be%20staring%20down%20the%20barrels%20of%20our%20guns%E2%80%9D.%20The%20Northern%20Army%20Commander%20had%20%E2%80%9Crecommended%20that%20the%20only%20way%20to%20stop%20the%20PLA%20was%20by%20opening%20up%20with%20our%20own%20medium%20artillery%2C%20which%20he%20said%20was%20ready%20and%20waiting%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fagnipath-scheme-bolt-out-of-the-blue-navy-air-force-former-army-chief-naravane-memoirs%5C%22%3EAgnipath%20Scheme%20Was%20%E2%80%98Bolt%20Out%20of%20the%20Blue%E2%80%99%20for%20Navy%20and%20Air%20Force%3A%20Former%20Army%20Chief%20Naravane%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHis%20memoirs%20are%20now%20ensnared%20in%20some%20sort%20of%20national%20security%20vetting%20process%20by%20the%20government%20and%20are%20unlikely%20to%20see%20the%20light%20of%20day.%20India%E2%80%99s%20corporate-owned%20big%20media%2C%20including%20correspondents%20covering%20national%20security%2C%20have%20let%20Naravane%E2%80%99s%20explosive%20disclosures%20sink%20without%20a%20trace.%20The%20primary%20aim%20is%20to%20prevent%20an%20embarrassment%20to%20the%20Modi%20government%20over%20its%20handling%20of%20the%20crisis%2C%20but%20the%20secondary%20goal%20seems%20to%20be%20to%20avoid%20creating%20a%20strong%20anti-China%20narrative%20in%20the%20public%20space.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENaravane%20himself%20now%20seems%20to%20have%20sensed%20the%20official%20mood.%20In%20his%20latest%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheprint.in%2Fopinion%2Findia-must-use-dialogue-to-solve-border-conflict-with-china-military-solution-not-viable%2F1914201%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ecolumn%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20he%20argued%20that%20because%20%E2%80%9CIndia%20and%20China%20are%20now%20facing%20off%20in%20Eastern%20Ladakh%20for%20the%20fourth%20successive%20winter%2C%E2%80%9D%20India%20must%20consider%20that%20the%20%E2%80%9Ctime%20is%20ripe%2C%20therefore%2C%20for%20negotiations%20to%20recommence%2C%20not%20just%20for%20the%20remaining%20friction%20points%20but%20for%20resolving%20the%20overall%20boundary%20question%E2%80%9D.%20Clearly%2C%20the%20optics%20are%20being%20built%20for%20creating%20an%20environment%20in%20which%20India%20accepts%20a%20negotiated%20solution%20that%20reinforces%20China%E2%80%99s%20aggression%20on%20the%20Ladakh%20border.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFormer%20foreign%20Secretary%20Vijay%20Gokhale%20last%20month%20published%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcarnegieindia.org%2F2023%2F12%2F15%2Fstabilizing-border-possible-way-ahead-in-post-galwan-situation-pub-91244%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Epaper%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20at%20Carnegie%20India%20where%20he%20laid%20out%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20options%20that%20might%20be%20available%20to%20India%20to%20build%20back%20a%20framework%20for%20peace%20and%20tranquility%20along%20the%20border%20areas%E2%80%9D.%20He%20further%20outlined%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20actions%20that%20India%20might%20consider%20adopting%20unilaterally%20as%20well%20as%20in%20the%20negotiations%20with%20China%20with%20the%20objective%20of%20creating%20the%20conditions%20for%20restoration%20of%20peace%20and%20tranquility%20in%20the%20border%20region%E2%80%9D.%20His%20suggestions%20are%20exhaustive%20and%20unobjectionable%20but%20the%20underlying%20premise%20is%20that%20India%20must%20accept%20the%20new%20reality%20on%20the%20China%20border%20and%20somehow%20find%20a%20way%20to%20restore%20%E2%80%9Cpeace%20and%20tranquility%E2%80%9D%20in%20the%20border%20areas.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20a%20similar%20vein%2C%20former%20Northern%20Army%20Commander%20Lt.%20Gen%20D.S.%20Hooda%20(retd.)%20has%20suggested%20in%20a%20recent%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.delhipolicygroup.org%2Fpublication%2Fpolicy-briefs%2Fstabilising-the-line-of-actual-control-need-for-new-protocols.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Epolicy%20brief%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20the%20adoption%20of%20%E2%80%9Ca%20limited%20and%20measured%20approach%20to%20breaking%20the%20impasse%20at%20the%20LAC%2C%20where%20India%20and%20China%20can%20look%20at%20calming%20the%20military%20situation%20with%20quiet%20political%20endorsement%E2%80%9D.%20Asking%20for%20jointly%20identifying%20disputed%20areas%20on%20the%20LAC%2C%20he%20suggests%20that%20%E2%80%9Ceither%20no-patrolling%20buffer%20zones%20could%20be%20established%20or%20patrolling%20patterns%20agreed%20upon%20with%20a%20specified%20periodicity%20to%20avoid%20face-offs%20between%20opposing%20troops.%20Additional%20hotlines%20and%20meeting%20points%20should%20come%20up%20along%20the%20LAC%20to%20resolve%20any%20local%20incident%20promptly%E2%80%9D.%20The%20whole%20idea%20seems%20to%20be%20rooted%20in%20a%20need%20to%20quickly%20end%20the%20crisis%2C%20even%20if%20the%20Chinese%20continue%20to%20hold%20an%20upper%20hand.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIs%20the%20sudden%20plethora%20of%20articles%20providing%20justifications%20for%20an%20Indian%20engagement%20with%20China%20to%20%E2%80%9Cresolve%E2%80%9D%20the%20border%20crisis%20a%20coincidence%3F%20Or%20is%20it%20driven%20by%20the%20political%20need%20to%20create%20a%20narrative%20where%20a%20negotiated%20settlement%20that%20rewards%20Chinese%20aggression%20on%20the%20border%20is%20seen%20as%20the%20only%20viable%20option%3F%20As%20Major%20General%20Ashok%20Mehta%20(retd.)%20recently%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tribuneindia.com%2Fnews%2Fcomment%2Fhow-ambitious-india-fares-in-catching-up-with-china-579472%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ewrote%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20the%20establishment%20is%20gripped%20by%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20fear%20of%20annoying%20China%20and%20escalating%20the%20conflict%E2%80%9D.%20He%20claimed%20that%20there%20are%20%E2%80%9Cno%20buyers%20for%20conducting%20any%20game-changing%20operation%20similar%20to%20Snow%20Leopard%20on%20land%20or%20at%20sea%20or%20exploiting%20China%E2%80%99s%20Malacca%20dilemma%E2%80%9D.%20The%20Modi%20government%20needs%20to%20shed%20%E2%80%9Cdiffidence%20and%20deference%E2%80%9D%20towards%20China.%20A%20determined%20approach%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20need%20the%20narrative%20that%20is%20being%20constructed%20now.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704951238000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F04%2F07085318%2FChina-india.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fis-lets-seek-peace-on-the-border-narrative-about-modi-governments-intent-to-appease-china%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20optics%20are%20being%20built%20for%20creating%20an%20environment%20in%20which%20India%20accepts%20an%20unfavourable%20negotiated%20solution%20that%20reinforces%20and%20rewards%20China%E2%80%99s%20aggression%20on%20the%20Ladakh%20border.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fis-lets-seek-peace-on-the-border-narra