%20to%20India%20soon%20after%20Muizzu%E2%80%99s%20inauguration%2C%20but%20it%20remained%20at%20an%20initial%20stage%20with%20the%20administration%20insisting%20on%20the%20withdrawal%20of%20the%20Indian%20defence%20personnel.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20Maldivian%20president%20has%20travelled%20to%20Turkey%2C%20the%20UAE%20and%20China%20in%20the%20last%20six%20weeks.%20Muizzu%20met%20with%20the%20Indian%20PM%20on%20the%20sidelines%20of%20the%20COP%20summit%20in%20Dubai.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDuring%20delegation%20level%20talks%2C%20the%20Chinese%20President%20Xi%20Jinping%20told%20his%20guest%20that%20China%20%E2%80%9Csupports%20the%20Maldives%20firmly%20in%20safeguarding%20its%20national%20sovereignty%2C%20independence%2C%20territorial%20integrity%20and%20national%20dignity%E2%80%9D%2C%20as%20per%20a%20readout%20from%20the%20Chinese%20foreign%20ministry.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20announcing%20the%20elevation%20of%20ties%20to%20a%20%E2%80%98Comprehensive%20Strategic%20Partnership%2C%E2%80%99%20the%20Chinese%20president%20indicated%20that%20there%20was%20a%20friendlier%20government%20in%20Mal%C3%A9%20compared%20to%20the%20previous%20regime.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fenglish.news.cn%2F20240110%2Fe3c680e411794b23a37f25b7e6d3b385%2Fc.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EUnder%20the%20new%20circumstances%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20China-Maldives%20relations%20face%20a%20historic%20opportunity%20to%20build%20on%20past%20achievements%20and%20forge%20ahead%2C%E2%80%9D%20Xi%20said%2C%20as%20quoted%20by%20state-run%20news%20agency%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EXinhua%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20the%20Chinese%20statement%2C%20Maldives%20supported%20the%20Xi-proposed%20platforms%20of%20%E2%80%9CGlobal%20Development%20Initiative%2C%20the%20Global%20Security%20Initiative%20and%20the%20Global%20Civilization%20Initiative%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpresidency.gov.mv%2FPress%2FArticle%2F29600%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20per%20a%20list%20published%20by%20the%20Maldives%20President%E2%80%99s%20Office%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%2020%20agreements%20were%20signed%20by%20the%20two%20countries%20after%20formal%20talks%20between%20India%20and%20China.%20This%20included%20an%20%E2%80%9CAction%20Plan%E2%80%9D%20for%20fostering%20Comprehensive%20Strategic%20Partnership%20over%20the%20next%20four%20years.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20also%20listed%20an%20agreement%20on%20Grant%20Assistance%2C%20but%20no%20more%20details%20were%20provided.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAdditionally%2C%20the%20list%20included%20an%20MoU%20on%20%E2%80%9CJointly%20Accelerating%20the%20Formulation%20of%20the%20Cooperation%20Plan%20on%20the%20Belt%20and%20Road%20Initiative%E2%80%9D%2C%20along%20with%20an%20agreement%20on%20disaster%20risk%20reduction.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpresidency.gov.mv%2FPress%2FArticle%2F29599%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20readout%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20of%20the%20Maldivian%20government%20stated%20that%20Muizzu%20expressed%20%E2%80%9Cgratitude%20for%20China%E2%80%99s%20significant%20role%20in%20the%20Maldives%E2%80%99%20economic%20success%20and%20for%20China%E2%80%99s%20generous%20assistance%20in%20social%20housing%2C%20higher%20education%2C%20and%20infrastructure%20development%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Maldivian%20President%20also%20called%20expanding%20tourism%20cooperation%20and%20air%20connectivity%20between%20the%20two%20countries%2C%20which%20was%20also%20echoed%20by%20the%20Chinese%20side.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20day%20earlier%20at%20an%20Investors%20Meet%2C%20Muizzu%20had%20called%20on%20China%20to%20reclaim%20its%20status%20as%20th