D%20among%20senior%20seers%20over%20the%20proposed%20consecration%20ceremony%20scheduled%20for%20January%2022%20in%20Ayodhya.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20feel%20that%20this%20places%20him%20at%20the%20forefront%20of%20the%20event%2C%20potentially%20undermining%20the%20traditional%20rituals%20dictated%20by%20the%20Sanatan%20Shastras.%20Despite%20the%20general%20excitement%20for%20the%20Ram%20Temple%20Consecration%2C%20the%20absence%20of%20Shankaracharyas%20is%20a%20point%20of%20contention%20among%20devout%20Hindus%2C%E2%80%9D%20reports%20the%20portal.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98A%20tomb%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EShankaracharya%20Swami%20Shri%20Nischalananda%20Saraswati%20of%20Purvaamnaya%20Govardhanmath%20Puri%20peeth%20has%20declined%20participation%20in%20the%20Ayodhya%20Ram%20Mandir%20Pran%20Pratishtha%20programme%2C%20as%20he%20says%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20government%E2%80%99s%20endeavour%20is%20not%20centred%20around%20constructing%20a%20%E2%80%9Csacred%20temple%E2%80%9D%20but%2C%20in%20his%20words%2C%20%E2%80%9Ca%20tomb.%E2%80%9D%20This%20characterisation%20suggests%20a%20perception%20that%20the%20project%20lacks%20the%20sanctity%20and%20reverence%20inherent%20in%20%E2%80%9Ctraditional%20temple%20construction.%E2%80%9D%20His%20decision%20not%20to%20attend%20is%20grounded%20in%20the%20principle%20of%20choosing%20not%20to%20be%20part%20of%20a%20place%20where%20due%20respect%20is%20perceived%20to%20be%20lacking.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20decision%20not%20to%20attend%20the%20event%20is%20rooted%20in%20a%20commitment%20to%20maintaining%20the%20dignity%20and%20glory%20associated%20with%20their%20position.%20The%20reluctance%20to%20participate%20is%20not%20a%20rejection%20of%20reverence%20for%20Shri%20Ram%2C%20but%20rather%20a%20principled%20stand%20against%20what%20is%20perceived%20as%20the%20opportunistic%20and%20manipulative%20politics%20of%20certain%20leaders.%20This%20stance%20emphasises%20the%20independence%20and%20moral%20integrity%20of%20the%20spiritual%20leadership%2C%20free%20from%20what%20is%20considered%20as%20the%20influence%20of%20%E2%80%9Ccrooked%E2%80%9D%20political%20figures.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98Still%20under%20construction%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EShankaracharya%20Swami%20Shri%20Bharati%20Teerth%20Ji%20of%20Sringeri%20Sharda%20Peeth%20has%20reportedly%20declined%20the%20invitation%20to%20despite%20expressing%20joy%20about%20the%20construction%20of%20the%20Ram%20temple.%20His%20reservations%20stem%20from%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20temple%20is%20still%20under%20construction.%20He%20deems%20it%20inappropriate%20to%20consecrate%20the%20divine%20in%20a%20structure%20that%20is%20not%20yet%20complete%2C%20citing%20concerns%20about%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20righteousness%20of%20such%20an%20act.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20has%20flagged%20his%20concern%20on%20the%20simultaneous%20construction%20of%20what%20is%20purported%20to%20be%20Asia%E2%80%99s%20largest%20mosque%20in%20Ayodhya.%20This%2C%20for%20him%2C%20%E2%80%9Cmarks%20an%20unfortunate%20turn%20of%20events.%E2%80%9D%20The%20dissatisfaction%20is%20further%20accentuated%20by%20a%20sense%20of%20neglect%2C%20as%20he%20claims%20that%20he%2C%20along%20with%20other%20revered%20figures%2C%20had%20presented%20evidence%20in%20court%20regarding%20the%20Ram%20Mandir.%20However%2C%20according%20to%20his%20statement%2C%20the%20Ram%20Mandir%20Trust%20has%20not%20sought%20advice%20from%20them%20or%20their%20representatives%2C%20suggesting%20a%20lack%20of%20consultation%20with%20key%20spiritual%20leaders.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20per%20the%20portal%2C%20the%20Shankaracharya%20has%20accused%20the%20Modi%20government%20of%20having%20a%20duplicitous%20character.%20He%20contends%20that%20the%20government%2C%20despite%20executing%20the%20construction%20of%20the%20Ram%20temple%2C%20is%20perceived%20%E2%80%9Cas%20exploiting%20Hindu%20sentiments%20for%20political%20gains.%E2%80%9D%20This%20assertion%20reflects%20a%20broader%20scepticism%20about%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20intentions%20and%20commitment%20to%20the%20holistic%20well-being%20of%20the%20religious%20community.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20suitable%20time%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EShankaracharya%20Shri%20Swami%20Sadanand%20Saraswati%20of%20Paschimannaya%20Dwarka%20Shardapeeth%20has%20chosen%20not%20to%20participate%20in%20the%20Ram%20Mandir%20Mahotsav%2C%20citing%20concerns%20around%20the%20timing%20of%20the%20consecration%2C%20stating%20that%20in%20the%20inauspicious%20month%20of%20Paush%2C%20according%20to%20scriptures%2C%20the%20initiation%20of%20life%20consecration%20in%20deities%20is%20deemed%20inappropriate.%20He%20proposes%20that%20a%20more%20suitable%20time%20would%20be%20Ram%20Navami%2C%20the%20auspicious%20birth%20day%20of%20Lord%20Rama.%20A%20central%20point%20of%20contention%20is%20the%20perceived%20%E2%80%9Cpoliticisation%20of%20the%20event.%E2%80%9D%20Swami%20Sadanand%20Saraswati%20suggests%20that%20politics%20is%20the%20primary%20reason%20for%20the%20consecration%20happening%20at%20this%20moment.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20anticipates%20that%20the%20election%20code%20of%20conduct%20will%20be%20in%20force%20during%20Ram%20Navami%2C%20making%20it%20less%20advantageous%20for%20BJP%20leaders%20to%20exploit%20the%20consecration%20for%20political%20gain.%20This%20perspective%20introduces%20a%20political%20dimension%20to%20the%20decision-making%20process%20around%20the%20temple%20consecration.%20Additionally%2C%20Swami%20Sadanand%20Saraswati%20questions%20the%20rationale%20behind%20consecrating%20the%20temple%20before%20its%20completion.%20Drawing%20an%20analogy%2C%20he%20notes%20that%20traditionally%2C%20one%20does%20not%20enter%20a%20house%20until%20it%20is%20fully%20formed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98Anti-%3Cem%3Edharamashashtra%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%98%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EShankaracharya%20Swami%20Shri%20Avimukteshwarananda%20Saraswati%20of%20Uttaramnaya%20Jyotirmath%20has%20decided%20not%20to%20attend%20the%20Ayodhya%20event%20on%20January%2022%2C%20citing%20specific%20concerns%2C%20which%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fits-a-ram-mandir-ramanand-tradition-to-be-followed-temple-trusts-secy-remarks-draw-criticism%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ereported%20on%20January%209%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20The%20report%20cited%20him%20as%20saying%2C%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3EHum%3C%2Fem%3E%20anti-Modi%20%3Cem%3Enahi%20hain%2C%20lekin%20hum%20anti-dharamashashtra%20bhi%20nahi%20hona%20chahte%3C%2Fem%3E%20(We%20are%20not%20anti-Modi%2C%20but%20we%20do%20not%20want%20to%20be%20anti-dharamashashtra%20either)%2C%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%20This%20portal%20says%20that%20his%20assertion%20is%20that%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20Vedas%2C%20foundational%20texts%20in%20Hinduism%2C%20contain%20a%20distinctive%20provision%20for%20the%20role%20of%20priesthood%2C%20reserving%20it%20for%20Brahmins.%20According%20to%20Vedic%20traditions%2C%20the%20priesthood%20is%20considered%20exclusive%20to%20the%20Brahmin%20caste.%20Swami%20Avimukteshwarananda%20Saraswati%20emphasises%20the%20significance%20of%20adhering%20to%20these%20established%20practices%20outlined%20in%20the%20Vedas.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20has%20criticised%20the%20appointment%20of%20a%20Shudra%20as%20a%20temple%20priest%2C%20viewing%20it%20as%20a%20departure%20from%20the%20religious%20principles%20outlined%20in%20the%20Vedas.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20portal%20writes%20that%20it%20%E2%80%9Cis%20also%20unfortunate%20that%20once%20Narendra%20Modi%20was%20seen%20at%20the%20feet%20of%20Shankaracharyas%20to%20get%20blessings%20for%20his%20political%20prosperity%2C%20who%20is%20%E2%80%98now%20playing%20an%20adharmik%20role%20to%20undermine%20the%20Sanatan%20values%20and%20dignities%E2%80%99%E2%80%9D.%20It%20says%20that%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20non-participation%20of%20Highest%20Dharma%20gurus%20of%20Hindu%20Dharma%20in%20the%20most%20awaited%20Ram%20temple%20consecration%20is%20really%20unfortunate.%20It%20is%20not%20only%20a%20religious%20setback%20but%20also%20carries%20broader%20social%20and%20political%20implications.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESringeri%20Sankaracharya%20Sri%20Bharati%20Teerth%20Mahaswamy%20Ji%20has%20conveyed%20his%20blessings%20that%20every%20Astika%20must%20take%20part%20in%20the%20most%20sacred%20and%20rare%20Prana-pratistha%20in%20Ayodhya%20on%20January%2022%20to%20get%20unbounded%20grace%20of%20Bhagavan%20Sri%20Rama.%20But%2C%20says%20the%20portal%2C%20%E2%80%9Cit%20is%20still%20not%20clear%20from%20the%20message%20whether%20Sringeri%20Shankaracharya%20will%20participate%20in%20the%20Prana-pratistha%20in%20Ayodhya%20or%20not.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704945869000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F11092938%2FGDY7syJb0AAYFyc.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Freligion%2Fsanatan-hindu-dharma-highest-guru-ram-temple%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20prominent%20pro-Hindutva%20portal%2C%20describing%20itself%20as%20adding%20'a%20new%20dimension%20to%20create%20a%20solidarity%20in%20Global%20Hindus'%20quotes%20Shankaracharyas%20critical%20of%20politicisation%2C%20not%20getting%20due%20respect%20and%20ceremony%20being%20done%20before%20time.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A6%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Freligion%2Fsanatan-hindu-dharma-highest-guru-ram-temple%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Salesforce%20refutes%20reports%20that%20it's%20imposing%20a%20hiring%20freeze%3A%20'