%2Fnorma-barzman-blacklisted-screenwriter-dies-at-103%2Farticleshow%2F106713270.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Newborn%20Baby%20Found%20Dead%20Inside%20Bag%20In%20Florida%20Dumpster%3A%20''Gut-Wrenching''%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAn%20investigation%20is%20underway%20after%20a%20newborn%20baby%20boy%20was%20found%20dead%20inside%20a%20dumpster%20in%20Florida.%20As%20per%20the%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnypost.com%2F2024%2F01%2F10%2Fnews%2Fflorida-residents-shocked-after-baby-found-dead-in-dumpster%2F%5C%22%3ENew%20York%20Post%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%C2%A0a%20construction%20worker%20found%20the%20baby's%20body%20inside%20a%20box%20near%20an%20apartment%20building%20on%20Monday%20morning.%20David%20Vazquez%2C%2021%2C%20found%20the%20baby%20at%20around%208%20a.m.%20outside%20a%20condominium%20along%20Rodman%20Street%2C%20near%20South%20Federal%20Highway%2C%20and%20notified%20his%20boss.%C2%A0Mr%20Vasquez%20said%20he%20''smelled%20a%20bad%20odour''%20at%20the%20dumpster%2C%20where%20he%20saw%20a%20blue%20grocery%20bag.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E''I%20went%20to%20open%20the%20bag.%20When%20I%20opened%20the%20bag%2C%20I%20saw%20the%20baby%20and%20it%20was%20already%20lifeless%2C''%C2%A0he%20told%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cbsnews.com%2Fmiami%2Fnews%2Fbody-of-baby-found-in-hollywood-dumpster%2F%5C%22%3ECBS%20News%20%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3Eadding%20that%20the%20infant%20looked%20like%20a%20newborn%20and%20he%20believes%20the%20bag%20was%20placed%20there%20over%20the%20weekend.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E''One%20of%20my%20job%20sites%2C%20we're%20a%20roofing%20company%2C%20we%20have%20found%20a%20child%20in%20a%20dumpster.%20It%20was%20a%20child%2C%20a%20kid%2C%20a%20human.%20My%20crew%20arrived%20at%20the%20site%20to%20start%20the%20day%20and%20I%20guess%20they%20realized%20when%20they%20were%20going%20to%20throw%20debris%20in%20the%20dumpster%20that%20they%20saw%20the%20child%20inside%2C%20so%20they%20called%20me%20and%20I'm%20calling%20you%2C%20I'm%20not%20there%20on%20site%2C%E2%80%9D%20an%20official%20with%20the%20construction%20company%20said%20in%20the%20call%20which%20was%20released%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHollywood%20Police%20Department%20officers%20rushed%20to%20the%20site%20after%20the%20call.%C2%A0When%20first%20responders%20arrived%20at%20the%20scene%2C%20they%20attempted%20to%20save%20the%20baby%20but%20it%20was%20unresponsive%20and%20was%20pronounced%20dead%20at%20the%20scene.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20incident%20has%20sent%20shockwaves%20in%20the%20neighbourhood%2C%20leaving%20people%20disturbed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20just%20gut-wrenching%20and%20I've%20been%20here%20for%2040%20years.%20I%20never%2C%20never%2C%20we've%20had%20things%20like%20this.%20I'm%20just%20like%2C%20I%20don't%20know%2C%20it's%20shocking%2C%20it's%20disgusting%2C%26quot%3B%20Eugene%20Yakymiw%20told%20%3Cem%3ECBS%20News.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt's%20unbelievable.%20It's%20like%20if%20people%20don't%20want%20a%20baby%2C%20they%20could%20have%20gave%20it%20up%20to%20the%20firemen%20or%20leave%20it%20at%20a%20hospital%2C%E2%80%9D%20Roger%20Cote%2C%20who%20also%20lives%20in%20the%20area%2C%20also%20told%20the%20outlet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHollywood%20police%20are%20now%20investigating%20how%20the%20baby%20died%20and%20who%20the%20parents%20are.%20They%20are%20specifically%20looking%20for%20anyone%20who%20might%20have%20footage%20that%20could%20help%20them%20locate%20a%20suspect.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfooter%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20you%20live%20near%20this%20area%2C%20this%20is%20the%201700%20block%20of%20Rodman%20Street%20in%20the%20city%20of%20Hollywood%2C%20and%20you%20have%20a%20Ring%20camera%20and%20you%20believe%20that%20you%20have%20some%20kind%20of%20footage%20on%20your%20Ring%20camera%20or%20your%20doorbell%20camera%2C%20please%20don't%20hesitate%20to%20call%20us%2C%E2%80%9D%20Officer%20Christian%20L