20university%20is%20more%20than%20willing%20to%20co-operate%20%5Bin%20the%20investigation%5D%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20official%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAMU%20proctor%20Wasim%20Ali%20said%20while%20he%20was%20aware%20that%20some%20former%20and%20current%20students%20of%20the%20varsity%20had%20been%20arrested%2C%20no%20state%20agency%20had%20provided%20them%20any%20official%20information.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20truth%20about%20these%20allegations%20and%20on%20what%20basis%20they%20were%20made%2C%20will%20be%20known%20through%20the%20investigation%20or%20be%20decided%20in%20court%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ali%20told%20The%20Wire.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAli%20said%20the%20arrests%20and%20the%20UP%20police%20linking%20an%20alleged%20ISIS%20module%20to%20the%20central%20university%20would%20not%20deeply%20impact%20the%20image%20of%20AMU.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%2025%2C000%20students%20enrolled%20in%20the%20university.%20Every%20year%2C%20thousands%20come%20and%20pass%20out.%20If%203-4%20of%20these%20students%2C%20most%20of%20them%20passed%20out%2C%20come%20to%20face%20such%20allegations%2C%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20think%20it%20impacts%20the%20image%20of%20the%20university.%20It%20is%20up%20to%20the%20individuals%20concerned%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Ali%20did%20feel%20that%20given%20the%20number%20of%20arrests%20made%20in%20the%20case%2C%20it%20was%20a%20%E2%80%9Cmatter%20of%20concern.%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%9COur%20syllabus%20and%20system%20are%20transparent.%20There%20is%20nothing%20in%20our%20syllabus%20that%20promotes%20such%20things.%20The%20university%20functions%20and%20provides%20education%20as%20per%20the%20constitutional%20framework%20of%20the%20country.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704940216000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Funcategorised%2Futtar-pradesh-police-arrests-9-muslim-youth-in-two-months-in-crackdown-against-isis-module-of-amu%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%22%2C%22aut