enheimer'.%20'Jawan'%20became%20the%20highest-grossing%20Hindi%20film%20ever%2C%20earning%20643%20crore%20nett%20in%20India.%20Other%20notable%20films%20on%20the%20list%20were%20'Sound%20of%20Freedom'%2C%20'John%20Wick%3A%20Chapter%204'%2C%20'Avatar%3A%20The%20Way%20of%20Water'%2C%20and%20'Everything%20Everywhere%20All%20at%20Once'.%20Sunny%20Deol's%20'Gadar%202'%20also%20made%20the%20top%2010%2C%20while%20Shah%20Rukh%20Khan's%20'Pathaan'%20concluded%20the%20list.%20Khan%20had%20a%20successful%20comeback%20with%20three%20blockbuster%20releases%20in%202023.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22As%20War%20Rages%2C%20Israel%20To%20Face%20Gaza%20Genocide%20Charges%20At%20World%20Court%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIsrael%20prepared%20to%20defend%20itself%20on%20Thursday%20at%20the%20top%20UN%20court%20against%20accusations%20of%20genocide%20in%20Gaza%2C%20as%20Prime%20Minister%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu%20publicly%20rebuffed%20for%20the%20first%20time%20calls%20by%20some%20right-wing%20ministers%20to%20permanently%20occupy%20the%20enclave.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Israel's%20war%20in%20Gaza%20continued%20to%20rage%2C%20the%20International%20Court%20of%20Justice%20in%20The%20Hague%2C%20also%20known%20as%20the%20World%20Court%2C%20was%20to%20hold%20hearings%20on%20Thursday%20and%20Friday%20in%20a%20case%20brought%20by%20South%20Africa%20in%20December%20claiming%20Israel's%20war%20against%20Hamas%20militants%20in%20Gaza%20violates%20the%201948%20Genocide%20Convention.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsraeli%20government%20spokesperson%20Eylon%20Levy%20said%20on%20Wednesday%3A%20%26quot%3BTomorrow%2C%20the%20State%20of%20Israel%20will%20appear%20before%20the%20International%20Court%20of%20Justice%20to%20dispel%20South%20Africa's%20absurd%20blood%20libel%2C%20as%20Pretoria%20gives%20political%20and%20legal%20cover%20to%20the%20Hamas%20Rapist%20Regime.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20hearings%20will%20deal%20exclusively%20with%20South%20Africa's%20request%20for%20emergency%20measures%20ordering%20Israel%20to%20suspend%20its%20military%20actions%20in%20Gaza%20while%20the%20court%20hears%20the%20merits%20of%20the%20case%20-%20a%20process%20which%20could%20take%20years.%20Colombia%20and%20Brazil%20expressed%20their%20support%20of%20South%20Africa%20late%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael%20launched%20its%20offensive%20after%20Hamas%20fighters%20carried%20out%20an%20October%207%20cross-border%20rampage%20in%20which%20Israel%20says%201%2C200%20people%20were%20killed%20and%20240%20abducted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20then%2C%20Israeli%20forces%20have%20laid%20much%20of%20Gaza%20to%20waste%2C%20and%20nearly%20all%20its%202.3%20million%20people%20have%20been%20driven%20from%20their%20homes%20at%20least%20once%2C%20causing%20a%20humanitarian%20catastrophe.%20More%20than%2023%2C000%20Palestinians%20have%20been%20killed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20eve%20of%20the%20hearings%2C%20Netanyahu%20for%20the%20first%20time%20publicly%20stated%20opposition%20to%20calls%20from%20right-wing%20members%20of%20his%20government%2C%20including%20Finance%20Minister%20Bezalel%20Smotrich%20and%20National%20Security%20Minister%20Itamar%20Ben-Gvir%2C%20for%20Palestinians%20to%20leave%20Gaza%20voluntarily%2C%20making%20way%20for%20Israelis%20to%20settle%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20stance%20has%20been%20Israel's%20official%20policy%2C%20Netanyahu's%20prior%20comments%20on%20permanent%20occupation%20of%20Gaza%20have%20been%20inconsistent%20and%20at%20times%20opaque.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20want%20to%20make%20a%20few%20points%20absolutely%20clear%3A%20Israel%20has%20no%20intention%20of%20permanently%20occupying%20Gaza%20or%20displacing%20its%20civilian%20population%2C%26quot%3B%20Netanyahu%20said%20on%20social%20media%20platform%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPotentially%20timing%20his%20comments%20ahead%20of%20the%20ICJ%20hearings%2C%20he%20added%3A%20%26quot%3BIsrael%20is%20fighting%20Hamas%20terrorists%2C%20not%20the%20Palestinian%20population%2C%20and%20we%20are%20doing%20so%20in%20full%20compliance%20with%20international%20law.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJordan%20and%20Egypt%20warned%20on%20Wednesday%20against%20any%20Israeli%20reoccupation%20of%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%20and%20appealed%20for%20uprooted%20residents%20to%20be%20allowed%20to%20return%20to%20their%20homes%20as%20Jordan's%20King%20Abdullah%20and%20Egyptian%20President%20Abdel%20Fatah%20al-Sisi%20met.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUN%20Demands%20Houthis%20Stop%20Ship%20Attacks%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20ground%20in%20Gaza%2C%20the%20fighting%20appeared%20as%20intense%20as%20ever.%20Israeli%20strikes%20in%20southern%20and%20central%20Gaza%20intensified%20on%20Wednesday%20despite%20a%20pledge%20by%20Israel%20that%20it%20would%20pull%20out%20some%20troops%20and%20shift%20to%20a%20more%20targeted%20campaign%2C%20and%20pleading%20from%20its%20ally%20Washington%20to%20reduce%20civilian%20casualties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael's%20chief%20military%20spokesperson%20Rear%20Admiral%20Daniel%20Hagari%20said%20in%20a%20televised%20briefing%20late%20on%20Wednesday%20that%20the%20military%20was%20focusing%20its%20operations%20on%20Khan%20Younis%20and%20the%20refugee%20camps%20in%20the%20centre%20of%20the%20strip.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20latest%20sign%20of%20the%20three-month-old%20war%20spreading%2C%20U.S.%20and%20British%20warships%20in%20the%20Red%20Sea%20fended%20off%20the%20biggest%20attack%20yet%20from%20Yemen's%20Houthi%20movement%2C%20which%20says%20it%20is%20acting%20to%20support%20Gaza.%20Washington%20and%20London%20said%20they%20shot%20down%2021%20drones%20and%20missiles%20aimed%20at%20shipping%20lanes.%20No%20one%20was%20hurt.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20U.N.%20Security%20Council%20late%20Wednesday%20approved%20a%20resolution%20demanding%20the%20Houthis%20immediately%20cease%20the%20shipping%20attacks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael%20had%20