of%20raw%20materials%2C%20have%20also%20been%20seized.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurther%2C%20non-genuine%20expenses%20like%20sub-contracting%20expenses%2C%20purchases%20and%20transport%20expenses%2C%20etc%20aggregating%20to%20about%20Rs%20100%20crore%20have%20also%20been%20identified%20in%20the%20seized%20evidence%20from%20the%20premises%20of%20the%20flagship%20company%2C%20as%20mentioned%20in%20the%20official%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20search%20action%20also%20resulted%20in%20the%20determination%20of%20unexplained%20transactions%20undertaken%20by%20the%20distributor%20for%20issuing%20bills%20without%20a%20genuine%20supply%20of%20goods%2C%20whereas%20such%20goods%20have%20been%20sold%20in%20the%20open%20market%20in%20cash.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThus%2C%20the%20authorised%20distributor%20facilitated%20certain%20parties%20to%20inflate%20their%20purchase%20accounts%2C%20which%20aggregated%20to%20about%20Rs%20500%20crore.%20This%20distributor%20exclusively%20sells%20products%20of%20the%20flagship%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20search%20operation%2C%20unaccounted%20cash%20exceeding%20Rs%204%20crore%20has%20been%20seized%20and%20more%20than%2025%20bank%20lockers%20have%20been%20put%20on%20restraint.%20Further%20investigations%20are%20in%20progress.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704934620000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-01%2F6kah06f8_income-tax-_625x300_06_January_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Funaccounted-sales-of-rs-1-000-crore-discovered-in-raids-against-electrical-items-manufacturer-4838924%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Income%20Tax%20department%20initiated%20search%20and%20seizure%20operations%20in%20the%20case%20of%20a%20group%20engaged%20in%20the%20manufacturing%20of%20wires%2C%20cables%20and%20other%20electrical%20items%20on%20December%2022%2C%202023%2C%20the%20agency%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20on%20Wednesday.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Funaccounted-sales-of-rs-1-000-crore-discovered-in-raids-against-electrical-items-manufacturer-4838924%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Funaccounted-sales-of-rs-1-000-crore-discovered-in-raids-against-electrical-items-manufacturer-4838924%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Funaccounted-sales-of-rs-1-000-crore-discovered-in-raids-against-electrical-items-manufacturer-4838924%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Bitcoin%20Funds%20To%20Debut%20On%20Public%20Markets%2C%20Get%20US%20Regulators'%20Approval%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EUS%20securities%20regulators%20gave%20the%20green%20light%20Wednesday%20to%20a%20group%20of%20bitcoin%20exchange-traded%20funds%2C%20a%20keenly%20anticipated%20decision%20expected%20to%20boost%20the%20cryptocurrency.%20Regulators%20approved%20proposals%20for%2011%20ETFs%20to%20list%20on%20leading%20exchanges%20including%20the%20New%20York%20Stock%20Exchange%20%26quot%3Bon%20an%20accelerated%20basis%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Securities%20and%20Exchange%20Commission%20said%20in%20a%2022-page%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EETFs%20are%20traded%20on%20public%20markets%2C%20granting%20investors%20exposure%20to%20price%20movements%20in%20asset%20prices%20without%20taking%20direct%20ownership%20of%20the%20underlying%20assets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20funds%20themselves%2C%20however%2C%20do%20invest%20in%20the%20digital%20currency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20authorization%20of%20the%20ETFs%20or%20ETPs%20(exchange-traded%20products)%20--%20which%20are%20comparable%20to%20stocks%20or%20mutual%20funds%20as%20far%20as%20accessibility%20to%20everyday%20investors%20--%20%26quot%3Brepresents%20a%20pivotal%20juncture%20for%20the%20digital%20asset%20space%2C%20signifying%20a%20movement%20towards%20mainstream%20legitimacy%20and%20acceptance%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Thomas%20Tang%2C%20vice%20president%20of%20investments%20at%20Ryze%20Labs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBitcoin%20ETFs%2C%20by%20virtue%20of%20their%20existence%20within%20a%20regulated%20framework%2C%20will%20infuse%20a%20level%20of%20institutional%20credibility%20into%20the%20realm%20of%20digital%20assets%2C%26quot%3B%20Tang%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInitially%20launched%20in%20the%201990s%2C%20ETFs%20took%20off%20in%20the%20early%202000s%20by%20investors%20looking%20for%20a%20simple%20and%20low-cost%20way%20to%20take%20bets%20on%20stock%20indices%2C%20commodities%20or%20a%20particular%20industrial%20sector.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20%246.7%20trillion%20were%20held%20globally%20in%20ETFs%20at%20the%20end%20of%202022%2C%20according%20to%20consultancy%20Oliver%20Wyman.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUntil%20Wednesday%2C%20investors%20seeking%20to%20invest%20in%20bitcoin%20had%20to%20open%20an%20account%20on%20a%20cryptocurrency%20exchange%20and%20transact%20through%20a%20traditional%20medium%20of%20exchange%2C%20such%20as%20the%20dollar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWednesday's%20action%20opens%20up%20trading%20on%20vehicles%20offered%20by%20mainstream%20financial%20houses%20such%20as%20Fidelity%20and%20BlackRock.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENear%202250%20GMT%2C%20bitcoin%20prices%20were%20up%201.4%20percent%20at%20%2446%2C576.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ERegulatory%20pivot%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnticipation%20of%20the%20SEC's%20approval%20had%20in%20recent%20weeks%20jolted%20a%20digital%20currency%20already%20known%20for%20volatility.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Tuesday%2C%20bitcoin%20prices%20reached%20a%2022-month%20high%20of%20%2447%2C914%20after%20a%20fabricated%20SEC%20post%20on%20the%20X%20platform%2C%20formerly%20Twitter%2C%20said%20the%20agency%20had%20approved%20the%20listing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20minutes%20after%20the%20false%20statement%2C%20SEC%20Chairman%20Gary%20Gensler%20took%20to%20his%20own%20X%20account%20to%20warn%20that%20the%20market%20regulator's%20account%20had%20been%20%26quot%3Bcompromised%26quot%3B%20and%20that%20an%20%26quot%3Bunauthorized%20tweet%26quot%3B%20had%20been%20posted%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20SEC%20had%20blocked%20similar%20investment%20vehicles%20in%20the%20past.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20agency%20changed%20its%20approach%20after%20a%20US%20court%20ruling%20determined%20the%20SEC%20had%20failed%20to%20adequately%20explain%20its%20reasoning%20for%20denying%20an%20ETF%20from%20Grayscale.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECiting%20the%20court%20ruling%2C%20Gensler%20concluded%20%26quot%3Bthe%20most%20sustainable%20path%20forward%20is%20to%20approve%20the%20listing%20and%20trading%20of%20these%20spot%20bitcoin%20ETP%20shares%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20released%20by%20the%20agency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGensler%20emphasized%20that%20Wednesday's%20actions%20included%20some%20key%20protections%20for%20investors%2C%20including%20disclosure%20requirements%20on%20listed%20ETFs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20products%20will%20also%20be%20listed%20on%20regulated%20exchange%2C%20which%20%26quot%3Bare%20required%20to%20have%20rules%20designed%20to%20prevent%20fraud%20and%20manipulation%2C%26quot%3B%20Gensler%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Gensler%20said%20the%20SEC%20is%20%26quot%3Bmerit%20neutral%26quot%3B%20on%20investments%2C%20he%20noted%20that%20underlying%20assets%20in%20metals%20ETFs%20have%20consumer%20and%20industrial%20uses%2C%20while%20bitcoin%20is%20%26quot%3Bin%20contrast%20bitcoin%20is%20primarily%20a%20speculative%2C%20volatile%20asset%26quot%3B%20that%20has%20been%20used%20for%20money%20laundering%20and%20other%20illicit%20activity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhile%20we%20approved%20the%20listing%20and%20trading%20of%20certain%20spot%20bitcoin%20ETP%20shares%20today%2C%20we%20did%20not%20approve%20or%20endorse%20bitcoin%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BInvestors%20should%20remain%20cautious%20about%20the%20myriad%20risks%20associated%20with%20bitcoin%20and%20products%20whose%20value%20is%20tied%20to%20crypto.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERepresentative%20Patrick%20McHenry%2C%20a%20Republican%20from%20North%20Carolina%20who%20chairs%20the%20House%20Financial%20Services%20Committee%2C%20welcomed%20the%20announcement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20pleased%20that%20investors%20and%20our%20markets%20will%20finally%20be%20afforded%20greater%20access%20to%20this%20generational%20technology%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20congressman.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704933840000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Foc389fp_bitcoin_625x300_14_December_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fbitcoin-funds-to-debut-on-public-markets-get-us-regulators-approval-4839533%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22US%20securities%20regulators%20gave%20the%20green%20light%20Wednesday%20to%20a%20group%20of%20bitcoin%20exchange-traded%20funds%2C%20a%20keenly%20anticipated%20decision%20expected%20to%20boost%20the%20cryptocurrency.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A5%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fbitcoin-funds-to-debut-on-public-markets-get-us-regulators-approval-4839533%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fbitcoin-funds-to-debut-on-public-markets-get-us-regulators-approval-4839533%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fbitcoin-funds-to-debut-on-public-markets-get-us-regulators-approval-4839533%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Five%20dead%20as%20storm%20brings%20floods%20to%20US%20north-east%22%2C%2