%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ereactive%20parent%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20who%20raged%20at%20the%20first%20sign%20of%20conflict%20or%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsigns-you-grew-up-emotionally-absent-parents-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eemotionally%20absent%20parent%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20who%20withdrew%20their%20love%2C%20%26quot%3Byou%20probably%20learned%20as%20a%20child%20that%20conflict%20is%20not%20safe%2C%26quot%3B%20Wright%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20flip%20side%2C%20if%20you%20had%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsigns-raised-by-passive-parent-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Epassive%20parent%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20who%20shut%20down%20when%20any%20uncomfortable%20feelings%20came%20up%2C%20you%20likely%20received%20the%20message%20that%20problems%20should%20be%20swallowed%20to%20keep%20the%20peace.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E5.%20You%20have%20physical%20symptoms%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Wright%2C%20the%20emotional%20and%20psychological%20symptoms%20of%20growing%20up%20in%20an%20unstable%20or%20neglectful%20family%20can%20have%20physical%20side%20effects%2C%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWright%20said%20insomnia%2C%20stress%2C%20and%20anxiety%20can%20all%20be%20linked%20to%20your%20past%20or%20current%20relationship%20with%20your%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E6.%20You're%20afraid%20of%20uncertainty%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222121%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20man%20jumps%20from%20one%20rock%20to%20another%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F659daf2b6979d7371821cc89%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221414%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EGrowing%20up%20in%20a%20dysfunctional%20family%20can%20make%20you%20uncomfortable%20with%20uncertainty%3Cp%3ESolStock%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20Wright%20said%20that%20a%20history%20of%20childhood%20abuse%20or%2