ified%20in%20a%20document%20found%20by%20troops%20in%20Gaza%20to%20be%20a%20member%20of%20Hamas's%20Gaza%20City%20Brigade%2C%20while%20Hamza%20Wael%20Dahdouh%20was%20identified%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bterrorist%26quot%3B%20belonging%20to%20Islamic%20Jihad.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20army%20statement%20included%20a%20copy%20of%20a%20document%20it%20said%20was%20a%20list%20of%20%26quot%3Boperatives%20from%20an%20electronic%20engineering%20unit%20of%20the%20Islamic%20Jihad%2C%20including%20Dahdouh%20and%20his%20military%20number%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHamza%20Wael%20Dahdouh%20and%20Mustafa%20Thuria%20were%20killed%20when%20the%20car%20they%20were%20travelling%20in%20was%20hit%20by%20two%20rockets%20on%20a%20street%20in%20Rafah%2C%20according%20to%20witnesses.%20A%20third%20journalist%20and%20the%20driver%20of%20the%20car%20were%20wounded.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMustafa%20Thuria%2C%20in%20his%2030s%2C%20had%20contributed%20for%20AFP%20since%202019%20and%20had%20also%20worked%20with%20other%20international%20media%20outlets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20and%20Hamza%20Wael%20Dahdouh%20had%20been%20tasked%20with%20filming%20the%20aftermath%20of%20a%20strike%20on%20a%20house%20in%20Rafah%20and%20their%20car%20was%20hit%20while%20they%20were%20on%20their%20way%20back%2C%20AFP%20correspondents%20said%20at%20the%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESoon%20after%20the%20strike%2C%20Al%20Jazeera%20said%20it%20%26quot%3Bstrongly%20condemns%20the%20Israeli%20occupation%20forces'%20targeting%20of%20the%20Palestinian%20journalists'%20car%26quot%3B%2C%20accusing%20Israel%20of%20%26quot%3Btargeting%26quot%3B%20journalists%20and%20%26quot%3Bviolating%20the%20principles%20of%20freedom%20of%20the%20press%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHamza's%20father%20Wael%20al-Dahdouh%20is%20Al%20Jazeera's%20Gaza%20bureau%20chief%2C%20and%20was%20recently%20wounded%20in%20a%20strike%20himself%20after%20his%20wife%20and%20two%20other%20children%20were%20killed%20in%20Israeli%20bombardment%20in%20the%20initial%20weeks%20of%20the%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESoon%20after%20Hamza%20Wael%20Dahdouh%20and%20Mustafa%20Thuria%20were%20killed%2C%20US%20Secretary%20of%20State%20Antony%20Blinken%20said%20that%20their%20deaths%20was%20an%20%26quot%3Bunimaginable%20tragedy%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20that's%20also%20been%20the%20case%20for...%20far%20too%20many%20innocent%20Palestinian%20men%2C%20women%20and%20children%2C%26quot%3B%20Blinken%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Monday%2C%20Wael's%20two%20nephews%20Ahmed%20al-Dahdouh%20and%20Muhammad%20al-Dahdouh%20were%20also%20killed%20in%20a%20strike%20when%20travelling%20in%20a%20car%20in%20Rafah%2C%20according%20to%20the%20health%20ministry%20in%20Hamas-run%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20war%20in%20Gaza%20erupted%20when%20Hamas%20militants%20rushed%20across%20Gaza's%20border%20into%20Israel%20in%20an%20unprecedented%20attack%20on%20October%207%20which%20left%20some%201%2C140%20people%20dead%2C%20mostly%20civilians%2C%20according%20to%20an%20AFP%20tally%20based%20on%20official%20Israeli%20figures.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael%20has%20vowed%20to%20eradicate%20Hamas%2C%20denounced%20as%20a%20terrorist%20group%20by%20the%20US%20and%20EU%2C%20and%20has%20kept%20up%20a%20relentless%20bombing%20of%20Gaza%2C%20which%20the%20Hamas-run%20health%20ministry%20says%20has%20killed%20at%20least%2023%2C357%20people%2C%20mostly%20civilians.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20New%20York-based%20Committee%20to%20Protect%20Journalists%20says%20at%20least%2079%20journalists%20and%20media%20professionals%2C%20the%20vast%20majority%20Palestinian%2C%20have%20been%20killed%20since%20the%20war%20began.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704926880000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Fu2kaklc_journalist-hamza-wael-dahdouh-funeral_6