%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EChris%20Christie's%20Glory%20Days%20seem%20long%20gone.%20The%20pugnacious%20former%20New%20Jersey%20governor%20boss%20had%20one%20last%20card%20to%20play%20when%20he%20ran%20for%20president%20for%20the%20second%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20one%20of%20President%20Donald%20Trump's%20most%20prominent%20early%20backers%2C%20Christie%20emerged%20from%20an%20almost%20death%20(COVID%2C%20not%20January%206%2C%20that's%20Mike%20Pence)%20and%20the%20Capitol%20riot%20as%20a%20man%20who%20had%20seen%20the%20light%20%E2%80%94%20Trump%20was%20a%20fundamental%20threat%20who%20needed%20to%20be%20stopped%2C%20Christie%20professed.%20Christie%20carried%20his%20warnings%20as%20far%20as%20a%20podcast%20hosted%20by%20former%20top%20aides%20to%20President%20Barack%20Obama.%20It%20didn't%20work.%20According%20to%20multiple%20reports%2C%20Christie%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchristie-haley-2024-presidential-campaign-exit-gop-new-hampshire-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edropped%20out%20%3C%2Fa%3Eof%20the%20race%20Wednesday%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20reality%20is%20now%20abundantly%20clear%20to%20anyone%20who%20wants%20to%20see%20it%3A%20The%20Republican%20base%20has%20little%20love%20for%20any%20GOP%20official%20who%20wants%20to%20lead%20the%20charge%20against%20the%20former%20president.%20Even%20Pence%2C%20who%20struggled%20to%20even%20describe%20how%20angry%20he%20was%20that%20Trump%20endangered%20his%20life%2C%20couldn't%20sell%20his%20candidacy.%20So%20it's%20no%20surprise%20that%20Christie's%20signature%20art%20of%20aggressiveness%20didn't%20make%20the%20product%20more%20popular.%20This%20is%20Trump's%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMinus%20jokes%20about%20Christie's%20weight%2C%20Trump%20barely%20commented%20on%20his%20former%20ally's%20candidacy.%20And%20despite%20Christie's%20repeated%20trolls%2C%20Trump%20never%20delighted%20him%20in%20agreeing%20to%20appear%20on%20the%20debate%20stage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESen.%20Mitt%20