peaker%20Explains%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EMaharashtra%20Speaker%20Rahul%20Narwekar%20today%20explained%20his%20decision%20not%20to%20disqualify%20the%20members%20of%20the%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%20camp%20--%20a%20question%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%20UBT%20chief%20had%20pointedly%20asked.%20While%20the%20naming%20of%20Bharat%20Gogawale%20as%20whip%20%26quot%3Bproper%26quot%3B%2C%20it%20is%20not%20certain%20that%20the%20whip%20to%20attend%20the%20party%20meeting%20was%20%26quot%3Badequately%20and%20properly%20served%26quot%3B%20to%20Thackeray%20faction%20MLAs%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20appears%20that%20this%20service%20is%20not%20complete.%20There%20was%20no%20evidence%20to%20show%20this%20whip%20was%20properly%20served%20upon%20the%20MLAs%20belonging%20to%20the%20Thackeray%20faction.%20Since%20this%20filter%20was%20not%20cleared%2C%20it%20was%20not%20appropriate%20for%20me%2C%20under%20the%20principles%20of%20natural%20justice%2C%20to%20hold%20them%20disqualified%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Narwekar%20told%20NDTV%20in%20an%20exclusive%20interview%2C%20declaring%20all%20the%20details%20are%20mentioned%20in%20the%20written%20version%20of%20his%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Thackray%20had%20raised%20the%20point%20today%20while%20talking%20to%20the%20media%2C%20questioning%20why%2C%20if%20their%20version%20of%20the%20constitution%20was%20not%20valid%2C%20they%20were%20not%20disqualified.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Narwekar%20--%20while%20delivering%20his%20verdict%20on%20disqualification%20petitions%20pending%20for%20since%20June%202022%20--%20had%20named%20Mr%20Shinde's%20faction%20as%20the%20%26quot%3Breal%20Shiv%20Sena%26quot%3B%2C%20basing%20his%20decision%20on%20a%201999%20version%20of%20the%20party%20constitution%20that%20is%20with%20the%20Election%20Commission.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20version%20of%20the%20constitution%20given%20by%20Mr%20Thackeray%20in%202018%20is%20%26quot%3Bnot%20on%20record%26quot%3B%2C%20Mr%20Narwekar%20had%20said.%20Going%20by%20that%20constitution%2C%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%20did%20not%20have%20the%20power%20to%20remove%20Eknath%20Shinde%20from%20Shiv%20Sena%2C%20he%20had%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20had%20also%20dismissed%20the%20petitions%20to%20disqualify%20MLAs%20from%20both%20camps%20--%20a%20move%20that%20was%20strongly%20questioned%20by%20critics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20can%20awaken%20a%20person%20who%20is%20sleeping%20but%20it%20is%20rather%20impossible%20to%20wake%20up%20a%20person%20who%20is%20pretending%20to%20sleep%2C%26quot%3B%20was%20Mr%20Narwekar's%20response.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20skipping%20a%20party%20meeting%20is%20more%20about%20dissent%20than%20violation%20of%20rules%20and%20so%20does%20not%20call%20for%20disqualification.%20The%20right%20to%20dissent%20is%20included%20in%20the%20constitutional%20right%20of%20freedom%20of%20speech%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20splitting%20in%20June%202022%2C%20the%20two%20Sena%20factions%20had%20served%20disqualification%20notices%20against%20each%20other.%20The%20list%20of%20the%20Eknath%20Shinde%20faction%20had%2014%20of%20the%2016%20MLAs%20supporting%20Uddhav%20Thackeray.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Thackeray%20faction%20had%20filed%20disqualification%20petitions%20against%2040%20MLAs%20from%20Team%20Shinde.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Narwekar%20also%20answered%20the%20criticism%20that%20he%20had%20violated%20Supreme%20Court%20orders%2C%20failing%20to%20understand%20its%20brief%20--%20a%20point%20that%20was%20also%20voiced%20by%20Mr%20Thackeray.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20courts%20had%20asked%20me%20to%20say%20which%20is%20the%20real%20political%20party%2C%20because%20the%20whip%20of%20the%20original%20political%20party%20would%20be%20applicable%20and%20should%20be%20recognised.%20That's%20what%20the%20court%20said%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Narwekar%20said.%20So%20after%20recognising%20Bharat%20Gogawale%20as%20the%20whip%2C%20it%20was%20also%20his%20job%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20whip%20was%20properly%20served%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20evening%2C%20Mr%20Thackeray%20had%20launched%20an%20all-out%20attack%20on%20Mr%20Narwekar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20(the%20Speaker)%20has%20made%20a%20thief%20the%20master%20of%20the%20House%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Thackeray%20said%2C%20voicing%20doubts%20that%20Mr%20Narwekar%20had%20any%20idea%20of%20what%20he%20was%20tasked%20with%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20has%20given%20a%20decision%20that%20exceeds%20the%20brief%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%20The%20court%20had%20given%20a%20framework%2C%20but%20he%20distorted%20it%20into%20something%20else%E2%80%A6%20He%20should%20have%20made%20laws%20against%20party%20hopping%20stricter.%20Instead%2C%20he%20was%20busy%20clearing%20a%20path%20for%20himself%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20had%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERubbishing%20the%20criticism%20directed%20at%20him%20as%20%26quot%3Bbaseless%20allegations%26quot%3B%2C%20Mr%20Narwekar%20said%20if%20someone%20believes%20his%20order%20is%20untenable%20in%20law%20or%20unjustified%2C%20they%20should%20explain%20their%20reasoning.%20%26quot%3BKindly%20bring%20out%20the%20shortcomings%20in%20that%20order%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704913440000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Fjass4cm4_rahul-nawekar-ani_625x300_11_January_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmaharashtra-assembly-sena-vs-sena-didnt-disqualify-team-thackeray-mlas-as-maharashtra-speaker-explains-4838435%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Maharashtra%20Speaker%20Rahul%20Narwekar%20today%20explained%20his%20decision%20not%20to%20disqualify%20the%20members%20of%20the%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%20camp%20--%20a%20question%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%20UBT%20chief%20had%20pointedly%20asked.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmaharashtra-assembly-sena-vs-se