011001022_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Eknath%20Shinde's%20Faction%20is%20the%20%E2%80%98Real%E2%80%99%20Shiv%20Sena%2C%20Declares%20Maharashtra%20Speaker%20Narwekar%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F10231513%2FpRahul-Narwekar.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMumbai%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20A%20year%20and%20a%20half%20after%20Eknath%20Shinde%20rebelled%20against%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%20party%20and%20took%20away%2040%20MLAs%20along%20with%20him%2C%20Maharashtra%20legislative%20assembly%20speaker%20Rahul%20Narwekar%20declared%20Shinde%E2%80%99s%20front%20to%20be%20the%20%E2%80%9Creal%20Shiv%20Sena%E2%80%9D%20on%20Wednesday%20(January%2010).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Shinde%2C%20a%20senior%20Shiv%20Sena%20leader%20considered%20to%20be%20a%20party%20loyalist%20until%20his%20rebellion%2C%20will%20get%20to%20retain%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20symbol%2C%20Narwekar%20refrained%20from%20disqualifying%20the%20MLAs%20from%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%E2%80%99s%20(UBT)%20faction.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENarwekar%E2%80%99s%20decision%2C%20which%20was%20pending%20for%20nearly%2018%20months%20and%20even%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fsc-gives-maharashtra-speaker-a-week-to-open-disqualification-proceedings-against-cm-shinde-and-other-mlas%2Farticle67321068.ece%5C%22%3Eattracted%20the%20Supreme%20Court%E2%80%99s%20ire%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20was%20on%2034%20different%20petitions%20filed%20by%20MLAs%20from%20both%20factions.%20In%20all%2C%20the%20legitimacy%20of%2054%20MLAs%20from%20both%20factions%20was%20questioned%20in%20these%20petitions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Wednesday%2C%20Narwekar%20refused%20to%20disqualify%20MLAs%20from%20either%20faction.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressing%20a%20press%20conference%20in%20Mumbai%2C%20Thackeray%20questioned%20the%20speaker%E2%80%99s%20decision%20and%20said%20that%20if%20Shinde%E2%80%99s%20faction%20is%20legitimate%2C%20the%20speaker%20should%20have%20disqualified%20his%20(Thackeray%E2%80%99s)%20group.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHowever%2C%20that%20did%20not%20happen.%20This%20is%20a%20clear%20ploy%20to%20kill%20democracy%20in%20Maharashtra%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20his%20party%20will%20challenge%20the%20speaker%E2%80%99s%20decision%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThackeray%E2%80%99s%20faction%20had%20contended%20that%20as%20the%20then-Sena%E2%80%99s%20party%20head%2C%20his%20was%20the%20final%20word.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Narwekar%20decided%20on%20Wednesday%20that%20since%20as%20many%20as%2037%20out%20of%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%2055%20elected%20members%20had%20rebelled%20against%20him%2C%20Thackeray%20could%20not%20be%20considered%20the%20party%20chief.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20speaker%20held%20that%20since%20Shinde%20had%20the%20mandate%20of%20a%20majority%20of%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20MLAs%20at%20that%20time%2C%20he%20automatically%20assumed%20the%20role%20of%20the%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3Epaksh%20pramukh%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D%20or%20the%20party%20leader%20and%20that%20Thackeray%20did%20not%20have%20the%20power%20to%20remove%20Shinde%20from%20that%20role.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Thackeray%20faction%20was%20relying%20on%20a%202018%20amendment%20to%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20constitution.%20However%2C%20as%20there%20was%20no%20organisational%20election%20held%20that%20year%20and%20the%202018%20amendment%20was%20not%20in%20the%20records%20of%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%2C%20the%20speaker%20held%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%201999%20constitution%20was%20the%20legitimate%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20in%202018%2C%20the%20party%20considered%20the%20paksh%20pramukh%20as%20its%20highest%20office%2C%20its%201999%20constitution%20said%20the%20national%20executive%20was%20the%20highest%20party%20body.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20the%201999%20rule%2C%20the%20paksh%20pramukh%20had%20to%20take%20party%20decisions%20in%20consultation%20with%20the%20national%20executive.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShinde%E2%80%99s%20exit%20from%20the%20party%20was%20a%20dramatic%20one.%20He%20had%20suddenly%20gone%20%E2%80%98incommunicado%E2%80%99%20and%20was%20later%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Frebel-maharashtra-shiv-sena-mlas-arrive-at-guwahati-received-by-bjp-mps%5C%22%3Efound%20with%2037%20MLAs%20in%20a%20hotel%20in%20Guwahati%20in%20Assam%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20BJP-ruled%20state.%20From%20here%2C%20he%20and%20fellow%20rebel%20MLAs%20moved%20to%20Gujarat%20and%20then%20to%20Goa%2C%20both%20again%20BJP%20states%2C%20before%20finally%20returning%20to%20Mumbai.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShinde%20had%20accused%20Thackeray%20of%20high-handedness%20and%20of%20losing%20touch%20with%20the%20Sena%E2%80%99s%20Hindutva%20vision.%20His%20displeasure%20with%20the%20Sena%20soon%20proved%20to%20be%20a%20political%20opportunity%2C%20with%20him%20joining%20hands%20with%20the%20BJP%20and%20also%20becoming%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20chief%20minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20front%20runner%20and%20former%20chief%20minister%20Devendra%20Fadnavis%20had%20to%20settle%20for%20the%20deputy%20chief%20minister%E2%80%99s%20position.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELater%2C%20after%20Shinde%20became%20chief%20minister%2C%20many%20Sena%20leaders%2C%20including%20those%20considered%20very%20close%20to%20the%20Thackeray%20family%2C%20joined%20his%20faction.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMonths%20later%2C%20a%20similar%20story%20played%20out%20in%20the%20Nationalist%20Congress%20Party%20(NCP)%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fajit-pawar-maharashtra-ncp-sharad-pawar%5C%22%3Ewith%20Ajit%20Pawar%20and%20many%20senior%20MLAs%20of%20the%20party%3C%2Fa%3E%20joining%20hands%20with%20Shinde%E2%80%99s%20faction%20and%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20Ajit%20Pawar%20too%20is%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20deputy%20chief%20minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20speaker%E2%80%99s%20decision%20came%20after%20several%20reminders%20and%20petitions%20by%20the%20UBT%20faction.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20since%20May%20last%20year%20been%20directing%20Narwekar%20to%20expeditiously%20decide%20on%20the%20applications%20by%20the%20two%20factions.%20The%20apex%20court%20had%20earlier%20set%20December%2031%2C%202023%20as%20the%20deadline%20for%20him%20to%20decide%20on%20the%20disqualification%20applications%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fsupreme-court-gives-maharashtra-speaker-time-till-jan-10-for-ruling-on-sena-mlas%2Farticleshow%2F106032920.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3Elater%20shifted%20it%20to%20January%2010%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20had%2C%20in%20strong%20words%2C%20expressed%20dissatisfaction%20at%20the%20speaker%E2%80%99s%20inexplicable%20delay%20in%20the%20adjudication%20of%20the%20applications.%20The%20court%20had%20said%20that%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20dignity%20of%20this%20court%E2%80%99s%20judgement%20should%20be%20maintained%E2%80%9D%2C%20legal%20news%20website%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livelaw.in%2Ftop-stories%2Fshiv-sena-mla-disqualification-eknath-shinde-uddhav-thackeray-maharashtra-speaker-decision-246382%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ELiveLaw%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Election%20Commission%20last%20year%20gave%20the%20%E2%80%98Shiv%20Sena%E2%80%99%20name%20and%20its%20%E2%80%98bow-and-arrow%E2%80%99%20symbol%20to%20the%20Shinde-led%20faction%2C%20while%20the%20one%20headed%20by%20Thackeray%20was%20called%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%20(UBT)%2C%20with%20a%20flaming%20torch%20as%20its%20symbol.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENarwekar%E2%80%99s%20decision%20today%20comes%20as%20the%20second%20jolt%20to%20Thackeray.%20The%20challenge%20before%20him%20now%20is%20to%20keep%20his%20party%20(of%2016%20MLAs)%20together%2C%20right%20before%20the%202024%20general%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20refusing%20to%20disqualify%20the%2040%20MLAs%20of%20Shinde%E2%80%99s%20faction%2C%20Narwekar%20said%20that%20as%20soon%20as%20Shinde%20and%20his%20MLAs%20walked%20out%2C%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20chief%20whip%20Sunil%20Prabhu%20had%20%E2%80%9Cno%20authority%E2%80%9D%20to%20call%20a%20meeting%20of%20the%20legislature%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Thackeray%20faction%20had%20sought%20the%20disqualification%20of%20MLAs%20from%20Shinde%E2%80%99s%20faction%20on%20the%20grounds%20that%20they%20did%20not%20attend%20the%20legislature%20party%20meeting%20called%20by%20then-chief%20whip%20Prabhu%20on%20June%2021.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20by%20then%2C%20the%20Shinde-led%20faction%20had%20passed%20a%20resolution%20appointing%20Bharatshet%20Gogawale%20as%20chief%20whip.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThackeray%E2%80%99s%20party%20MP%20Sanjay%20Raut%20called%20Narwekar%20a%20%E2%80%9Ctraitor%E2%80%9D%20and%20said%20that%20a%20%E2%80%9CMarathi%3Cem%3E%20manoos%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D%20(Marathi%20person)%20has%20backstabbed%20the%20citizens%20of%20Maharashtra.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20a%20short-lived%20victory%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShinde%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20called%20it%20a%20%E2%80%9Cpeople%E2%80%99s%20mandate%E2%80%9D%20as%20the%20majority%20of%20the%20erstwhile%20party%E2%80%99s%20MLAs%20were%20by%20his%20side.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704908940000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F10231513%2FpRahul-Narwekar.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fnarwekar-says-shindes-faction-real-shiv-sena%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Narwekar%E2%80%99s%20decision%20today%20comes%20as%20the%20second%20jolt%20to%20Thackeray%2C%20who%20faces%20the%20challenge%20of%20keeping%20his%20party%20(of%2016%20MLAs)%20together%20before%20the%202024%20general%20elections.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fnarwekar-says-shindes-faction-real-shiv-sena%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22LK%