20was%20stuck%20in%20the%20village.%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20so%20happy%20that%20I%20didn%E2%80%99t%20have%20any%20work%20then%20and%20all%20that%20I%20had%20to%20do%20was%20wake%20up%20to%20the%20beautiful%20view%20of%20the%20hills%20and%20lead%20a%20slow%20life%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAshish%20had%20understood%20that%20it%20was%20finally%20time%20for%20him%20to%20move%20to%20the%20hills%2C%20permanently.%20So%20he%20bought%20a%20small%20piece%20of%20land%20in%20Jilling%20and%20started%20working%20on%20giving%20life%20to%20his%20dream%20with%20the%20help%20of%20local%20people%20and%20his%20friend%2C%20Daya.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBeing%20an%20advocate%20for%20sustainable%20development%2C%20he%20went%20on%20to%20build%20his%20house%20using%20the%20traditional%20architectural%20methods%20of%20the%20Kumaon%20region.%20For%20instance%2C%20instead%20of%20using%20cement%2C%20he%20used%20mud%2C%20cow%20dung%2C%20repurposed%20old%20wood%2C%20rock%2C%20and%20stones%20to%20construct%20the%20house.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20did%20not%20use%20cement%20at%20all.%20We%20used%20a%20mixture%20of%20mud%2C%20%3Cem%3Ebhusa%3C%2Fem%3E%20(hay)%2C%20and%20cow%20dung%20to%20make%20the%20walls.%20Additionally%2C%20I%20also%20adopted%20age-old%20practices%20of%20%3Cem%3Elipaai%20%3C%2Fem%3E%5Bpaiting%20walls%20with%20cow%20dung%20and%20water%5D.%20This%20provides%20good%20thermal%20insulation%20and%20keeps%20the%20house%20warm%20in%20winter%20and%20cool%20in%20summer.%20We%20used%20stone%20slates%20to%20make%20slanted%20roofs%20with%20large%20sunroofs%20that%20let%20in%20light%20during%20the%20day%20and%20allow%20you%20to%20see%20the%20stars%20at%20night%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FHomestay-2-1-1704894488.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%2