ame%20in%20to%20kill%20us.%20God%20don%E2%80%99t%20let%20this%20happen.%20The%20criminals%20are%20on%20air%2C%E2%80%9D%20a%20journalist%20wrote%20to%20news%20agency%20AFP%20in%20a%20WhatsApp%20message.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJournalist%20Adriana%20Noboa%20Arregui%20in%20Quito%20told%20%3Cem%3EDW%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20she%20had%20received%20information%20that%20the%20hostages%20had%20been%20released%20and%20that%20injured%20people%20had%20been%20taken%20to%20hospital.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20haven%E2%80%99t%20had%20real%20security%20for%20the%20past%20two%20or%20three%20years%2C%E2%80%9D%20Arregui%20told%20%3Cem%3EDW%3C%2Fem%3E.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20violence%20is%20getting%20worse%20and%20since%20last%20night%2C%20it%20has%20been%20chaos%20everywhere.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArregui%20said%20the%20president%20had%20%E2%80%9Cdeclared%20war%20on%20gangs%E2%80%9D%20and%20was%20trying%20to%20regain%20control%20of%20the%20prison%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBut%20that%20is%20going%20to%20be%20hard%20because%20the%20gangs%20have%20control%20now%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20was%20originally%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fecuador-armed-intruders-take-over-tv-studio-live-on-air%2Fa-67930200%5C%22%3Epublished%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3EDW.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704898189000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F10201833%2F00.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Farmed-intruders-take-over-ecuador-tv-studio-during-live-show%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20attack%20comes%20just%20after%20the%20new%20president's%20emergency%20declaration%2C%20highlighting%20the%20country's%20escalating%20violence.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Farmed-intruders-take-over-ecuador-tv-studio-during-live-show%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Jawaharlal%20Nehru%3A%20A%20Guiding%20Force%20in%20Our%20Past%2C%20Present%2C%20and%20Future%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F14123424%2FJef_Rens_et_Jawaharlal_Nehru_-_1947.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20following%20text%20is%20Aditya%20Mukherjee%E2%80%99s%20presidential%20address%20at%20the%2082nd%20session%20of%20Indian%20History%20Congress%20(IHC)%2C%20conducted%20from%20December%2028-30%2C%202023%2C%20at%20Kakatiya%20University%2C%20in%20Warangal%2C%20Telangana.%20Mukherjee%2C%20who%20was%20earlier%20with%20the%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%20University%2C%20in%20his%20presidential%20address%2C%20spoke%20about%20the%20IHC%E2%80%99s%20role%20in%20the%20promotion%20of%20scientific%2C%20secular%20and%20anti-imperialist%20history%20over%20the%20past%2085%20years.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFriends%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20am%20thankful%20to%20the%20Executive%20Council%20of%20the%20Indian%20History%20Congress%20for%20electing%20me%20as%20the%20General%20President%20this%20year.%20I%20am%20deeply%20honoured%20to%20be%20presiding%20over%20this%20august%20body%2C%20the%20largest%20and%20most%20representative%20organisation%20of%20historians%20in%20India%20which%20was%20created%20during%20the%20heyday%20of%20the%20Indian%20national%20movement%20in%20the%20mid%20nineteen%20thirties.%20In%20conformity%20with%20the%20values%20of%20our%20national%20liberation%20struggle%2C%20symbolised%20as%20the%20%E2%80%9CIdea%20of%20India%E2%80%9D%2C%20the%20Indian%20History%20Congress%20has%20spearheaded%20the%20promotion%20of%20scientific%2C%20secular%20and%20anti-imperialist%20history%20for%20over%2085%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20all%20of%20you%20are%20aware%2C%20the%20Idea%20of%20India%20is%20deeply%20threatened%20today%20and%20the%20discipline%20of%20history%20is%20being%20mauled%20beyond%20recognition%20and%20weaponized%20to%20destroy%20the%20Idea%20of%20India%20by%20religious%20communal%20forces%2C%20which%20not%20only%20did%20not%20participate%20in%20India%E2%80%99s%20freedom%20struggle%20but%20indeed%20collaborated%20with%20imperialism.%20It%20is%20perhaps%20appropriate%20that%20on%20his%2060th%20death%20anniversary%20I%20should%20focus%20my%20address%20on%20what%20we%20can%20learn%20from%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%2C%20among%20the%20foremost%20champions%20of%20the%20Idea%20of%20India%2C%20as%20well%20as%20of%20a%20scientific%20and%20meaningful%20history.%20I%20believe%20much%20can%20be%20learnt%20from%20him%20to%20explain%20our%20present%20and%20chart%20out%20a%20vision%20of%20the%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20because%20of%20what%20Nehru%20stood%20for%20that%20he%20is%20demonized%20so%20blatantly%20by%20the%20communal%20forces%20today.%20All%20kinds%20of%20lies%20and%20abuse%20are%20spread%20about%20him%20using%20the%20massive%20propaganda%20machinery%20that%20the%20communal%20forces%20command%20today.%20Nehru%20is%20blamed%20for%20all%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20problems%2C%20from%20the%20partition%20of%20the%20country%2C%20the%20Pakistan%20problem%2C%20the%20China%20problem%2C%20the%20crisis%20in%20Indian%20agriculture%2C%20the%20Kashmir%20issue%2C%20crisis%20in%20the%20educational%20system%2C%20the%20persistence%20of%20poverty%2C%20the%20growing%20religious%20polarisation%20in%20recent%20years%2C%20amending%20the%20constitution%20to%20curb%20democracy%2C%20to%20almost%20any%20problem%20facing%20the%20country%20today.%20This%2C%20nearly%2060%20years%20after%20his%20passing%20away!%20A%20website%20called%20Dismantling%20Nehru%20with%20the%20subtitle%20%E2%80%98The%20last%20Viceroy%20of%20India%E2%80%99%20is%20on%20social%20media%20repeating%20a%20canard%20spread%20by%20the%20RSS%20since%20independence%2C%20which%20they%20thought%20was%20a%20black%20day%2C%20refusing%20to%20unfurl%20the%20national%20flag.%20A%20book%20called%2097%20Major%20Blunders%20of%20Nehru%20has%20now%20been%20expanded%20to%20Nehru%20Files%3A%20Nehru%E2%80%99s%20127%20Historic%20Blunders%20(Nehru%20Ki%20127%20Aitihasik%20Galtiyan).%20The%20list%20keeps%20growing%20as%20new%20%E2%80%98facts%E2%80%99%20are%20invented.%20He%20is%20even%20said%20to%20have%20a%20secret%20Muslim%20ancestry.%20Such%20is%20the%20hatred%20spread%20about%20him%20that%20one%20BJP%20leader%2C%20as%20reported%20in%20an%20RSS%20journal%2C%20went%20to%20the%20extent%20of%20saying%20that%20Nathuram%20Godse%20should%20have%20aimed%20his%20gun%20at%20Nehru.%20Apart%20from%20spreading%20lies%20about%20him%2C%20the%20effort%20is%20to%20also%20erase%20his%20memory%20from%20the%20minds%20of%20the%20Indian%20people.%20The%20iconic%20Nehru%20Memorial%20Museum%20and%20Library%20(NMML)%20built%20on%20the%20premises%20where%20he%20lived%20as%20the%20first%20Prime%20Minister%20of%20India%20is%20no%20more.%20Nehru%20has%20been%20dwarfed%20in%20that%20space%20which%20now%20houses%20a%20massive%20museum%20to%20all%20Prime%20Ministers%20(a%20global%20first!)%20and%20is%20called%20the%20Prime%20Ministers%E2%80%99%20Museum%20and%20Library.%20In%20Rajasthan%2C%20it%20was%20reported%20that%20textbooks%20for%20school%20children%20were%20created%20during%20the%20BJP%20regime%20in%20which%20%E2%80%9Cthere%20is%20no%20mention%20of%20Nehru%20either%20in%20the%20chapter%20(on)%20Freedom%20Movement%20or%20in%20India%20After%20Independence.%E2%80%9D%20The%20Indian%20Council%20for%20Historical%20Research%20(ICHR)%2C%20not%20to%20be%20left%20behind%20in%20pushing%20the%20BJP%20government%20initiative%2C%20recently%20put%20up%20a%20poster%20celebrating%20the%2075th%20Year%20of%20Indian%20independence%20where%20the%20pictures%20of%20many%20freedom%20fighters%20were%20put%20up%20but%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%20was%20absent%20and%20V.D.%20Savarkar%20was%20added%2C4%20a%20person%20who%20apologized%20to%20the%20British%2C%20promising%20total%20loyalty%2C%20and%20after%20his%20release%20cooperated%20with%20the%20British%20Government%20when%20the%20people%20of%20India%20were%20sacrificing%20their%20lives%20in%20the%20Quit%20India%20movement%20and%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%20spent%20nearly%20three%20years%20in%20jail%20in%20Ahmednagar%20Fort%20with%20Maulana%20Azad%2C%20Sardar%20Patel%20and%20other%20Congress%20leaders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENot%20even%20the%20British%2C%20who%20were%20the%20chief%20ally%20of%20the%20communal%20forces%2C%20demonize%20Nehru%20in%20this%20manner%2C%20and%20this%20despite%20Nehru%20spending%2030%20years%20of%20his%20life%20fighting%20the%20British%2C%20nine%20of%20those%20years%20spent%20in%20British%20jails.5%20Though%20there%20has%20been%20a%20resurgence%20of%20the%20neo-colonial%20critique%20of%20Nehru%20by%20people%20like%20Tirthankar%20Roy%2C%20Meghnad%20Desai%2C%20etc.%2C%20it%20is%20not%20as%20crass%20and%20vulgar%20as%20that%20done%20by%20communalists.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENehru%20and%20the%20Discipline%20of%20History%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20demonizing%20of%20Nehru%20and%20the%20values%20he%20stood%20for%20could%20only%20be%20done%20by%20distorting%20history%20and%20that%20is%20what%20the%20communal%20forces%20have%20done%20blatantly.%20As%20I%20am%20addressing%20a%20distinguished%20gathering%20of%20historians%2C%20I%20would%20like%20to%20begin%20with%20a%20brief%20discussion%20on%20Nehru%E2%80%99s%20own%20attitude%20to%20the%20discipline%20of%20history%20before%20moving%20on%20to%20a%20discussion%20of%20how%20Nehru%20is%20being%20wrongly%20demonized%20by%20detailing%20some%20of%20his%20actual%20historic%20contributions%20to%20the%20making%20of%20modern%20India.%20I%20do%20so%20as%20I%20believe%20that%20Nehru%2C%20from%20as%20early%20as%20the%201930s%2C%20provided%20a%20framework%2C%20partly%20demonstrated%20in%20his%20own%20historical%20writings%2C%20that%20was%20in%20sharp%20contrast%20to%20the%20colonial%20and%20communal%20framework.%20Some%20of%20the%20most%20distinguished%20scholars%20of%20the%20country%20adopted%20and%20developed%20decades%20later%2C%20the%20Nehruvian%20framework.%20Much%20can%20be%20learnt%20from%20Nehru%20in%20this%20sphere%20even%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20referring%20to%20Nehru%E2%80%99s%20outstanding%20historical%20works%2C%20Glimpses%20of%20World%20History%2C%20Autobiography%20and%20The%20Discovery%20of%20India%2C%20all%20written%20in%20British%20jails%20between%201930%20and%201944%2C%20Professor%20Irfan%20Habib%20made%20a%20very%20significant%20comparison%20with%20Gramsci%E2%80%99s%20iconic%20Prison%20Notebooks%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThese%20prison%20works%20invite%20comparison%20in%20both%20quantity%20and%20quality%20with%20the%20kind%20of%20writing%20that%20Antonio%20Gramsci%20produced%20as%20a%20communist%20prisoner%20in%20fascist%20Italy.%20There%20are%20true%20similarities%20in%20that%20both%20%E2%80%A6%20went%20to%20history%20to%20find%20answers%20to%20the%20questions%20raised%20in%20their%20minds%20as%20men%20of%20action%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Nehru%20himself%20said%20%E2%80%9CBecause%20fate%20and%20circumstances%20placed%20me%20in%20a%20position%20to%20be%20an%20actor%20in%20the%20saga%2C%20or%20the%20drama%20of%20India%2C%20if%20you%20like%2C%20in%20the%20last%20twenty%20or%20thirty%20years%20in%20common%20with%20many%20others%2C%20my%20interest%20in%20history%20became%20not%20an%20academic%20interest%20in%20things%20of%20the%20past%20%E2%80%A6%20but%20an%20intense%20personal%20interest.%20I%20wanted%20to%20understand%20those%20events%20in%20relation%20to%20today%20and%20understand%20today%20in%20relation%20to%20what%20had%20been%2C%20and%20try%20to%20peep%20into%20the%20future%E2%80%A6.%20one%20has%20to%20go%20back%20to%20(history)%20to%20understand%20the%20present%20and%20to%20try%20to%20understand%20what%20the%20future%20ought%20to%20be%E2%80%9D.%20Irfan%20Habib%20quoted%20Marx%E2%80%99s%20famous%20statement%2C%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20philosophers%20have%20only%20interpreted%20the%20world%20in%20various%20ways%2C%20the%20point%20is%20to%20change%20it%E2%80%9D%2C%20to%20argue%20that%20for%20a%20%E2%80%98man%20of%20action%E2%80%99%20like%20Nehru%2C%20history%20was%20not%20just%20a%20directionless%20descriptive%20narrative%20placed%20in%20a%20chronological%20order%20but%20a%20resource%20from%20which%20one%20sought%20to%20understand%20the%20present%20in%20order%20to%20try%20to%20shape%20the%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENehru%20urged%20historians%20to%20approach%20history%20in%20this%20manner.%20For%20example%2C%20just%20when%20India%20was%20emerging%20from%20the%20holocaust%20like%20situation%20caused%20by%20communal%20strife%20and%20the%20partition%20of%20the%20country%20on%20that%20basis%2C%20and%20the%20newly%20born%20Indian%20state%20was%20to%20embark%20on%20the%20path%20of%20building%20a%20secular%2C%20inclusive%20country%2C%20Nehru%20tells%20historians%20in%20December%201948%3A%20%E2%80%9CHistory%20shows%20us%20both%20the%20binding%20process%20and%20the%20disruptive%20process%E2%80%A6%20today%20a%20little%20more%20obviously%20%E2%80%93%20the%20binding%20or%20the%20constructive%20forces%20are%20at%20work%2C%20as%20also%20the%20disruptive%20or%20the%20fissiparous%20forces%2C%20and%20in%20any%20activity%20that%20we%20are%20indulging%20in%20we%20have%20the%20choice%20of%20laying%20emphasis%20on%20the%20binding%20and%20constructive%20aspect%20or%20the%20other%E2%80%9D.%20While%20exhorting%20the%20historians%20to%20emphasise%20the%20former%20he%20warns%2C%20true%20to%20the%20rigours%20of%20the%20discipline%20of%20history%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20must%20not%2C%20of%20course%2C%20give%20way%20to%20wishful%20thinking%20and%20emphasize%20something%20which%20we%20want%20to%20emphasize%E2%80%A6%20which%20has%20no%20relation%20to%20fact.%20However%2C%20he%20goes%20on%20to%20say%2C%20%E2%80%9CNevertheless%2C%20I%20think%20it%20is%20possible%20within%20the%20terms%20of%20scholarship%20and%20precision%20and%20truth%20to%20emphasize%20the%20binding%20and%20constructive%20aspect%20rather%20than%20the%20other%2C%20and%20I%20hope%20the%20activities%20of%20historians%20%E2%80%A6%20will%20be%20directed%20to%20that%20end%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20what%20Nehru%20himself%20did%20brilliantly%20in%20his%20classic%20work%20The%20Discovery%20of%20India%2C%20while%20the%20colonial%2Fcommunal%20approach%20was%20to%20constantly%20try%20to%20weaponize%20any%20conflict%20in%20the%20past%20to%20exacerbate%20them%20in%20the%20present.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20colonial%2Fcommunal%20interpretation%20repeatedly%20emphasized%20the%20%E2%80%98trauma%E2%80%99%20experienced%20as%20a%20result%20of%20Hindu%E2%80%93Muslim%20conflict.%20These%20theories%20of%20trauma%20were%20often%20created%20centuries%20after%20the%20so-called%20traumatic%20events.%20A%20case%20in%20point%20is%20the%20alleged%20trauma%20felt%20by%20%E2%80%98Hindus%E2%80%99%20because%20of%20the%20destruction%20of%20the%20Somanatha%20temple%20by%20a%20%E2%80%98Muslim%E2%80%99%20invader%2C%20Mahmud%2C%20the%20Sultan%20of%20Ghazni%20(now%20in%20Afghanistan)%20more%20than%20a%20thousand%20years%20ago%20in%201026.%20After%20independence%2C%20a%20demand%20was%20made%20that%20a%20grand%20temple%20be%20constructed%20at%20Somanatha.%20K.M.%20Munshi%20claimed%20in%201951%2C%20%E2%80%9C%E2%80%A6%20for%20a%20thousand%20years%20Mahmud%E2%80%99s%20destruction%20of%20the%20shrine%20has%20been%20burnt%20into%20the%20collective%20sub-conscious%20of%20the%20%5BHindu%5D%20Race%20as%20an%20unforgettable%20national%20disaster.%E2%80%9D%20In%20fact%2C%20there%20was%20no%20evidence%20of%20a%20thousand-year%20old%20trauma.%20Munshi%2C%20perhaps%20unknowingly%2C%20was%20reflecting%20the%20colonial%20perspective%20created%20in%20the%2019th%20century.%20Because%20the%20earliest%20mention%20discovered%20so%20far%20of%20%E2%80%98Hindu%20Trauma%E2%80%99%20caused%20by%20this%20%E2%80%98Muslim%E2%80%99%20invasion%20in%201026%2C%20which%20had%20to%20be%20avenged%2C%20is%20nearly%20800%20years%20later%2C%20in%201843%20when%20the%20issue%20is%20brought%20up%20in%20the%20British%20House%20of%20Commons.%20Colonial%20historiography%20since%20the%2019th%20century%20has%20used%20such%20events%20to%20evolve%20a%20notion%20of%20permanent%20confrontation%20between%20the%20Hindus%20and%20Muslims%2C%20laying%20the%20basis%20of%20the%20%E2%80%98two%20nation%E2%80%99%20theory%2C%20which%20argued%20that%20Hindus%20and%20Muslims%20constituted%20two%20distinct%20nations.%20The%20communalist%20picked%20up%20this%20theme%20and%20amplified%20it.%20The%20eminent%20historian%20Romila%20Thapar%2C%20using%20a%20multiplicity%20of%20sources%2C%20has%20convincingly%20demonstrated%20that%20no%20such%20permanent%20confrontation%20between%20Hindus%20and%20Muslims%20occurred%20historically%20as%20a%20result%20of%20the%20destruction%20of%20the%20Somanatha%20temple.%20150%20years%20after%20its%20destruction%20a%20Hindu%20king%20rebuilt%20the%20Somanatha%20temple%20without%20even%20a%20mention%20of%20Mahmud%20having%20destroyed%20it.%20250%20years%20later%20land%20was%20given%20to%20a%20Muslim%20trader%20to%20build%20a%20mosque%20on%20land%20belonging%20to%20the%20same%20temple%E2%80%99s%20estates%20with%20the%20approval%20of%20the%20local%20Hindu%20ruler%2C%20local%20merchants%20and%20priests!%20No%20signs%20of%20a%20%E2%80%98trauma%E2%80%99%20in%20the%20%E2%80%98collective%20memory%E2%80%99%20of%20Hindus%20is%20visible%20until%20it%20was%20a%20%E2%80%98memory%E2%80%99%20constructed%20much%20later%20under%20colonial%20patronage%20by%20their%20allies%2C%20the%20religious%20communal%20forces.%20Destruction%20of%20religious%20places%20was%20routinely%20done%20across%20religions%20and%20sects%20often%20to%20loot%20the%20wealth%20of%20these%20institutions%20or%20establish%20authority%20in%20ancient%20and%20medieval%20times%20and%20was%20perhaps%20treated%20as%20such.%20Nehru%20himself%20had%20a%20much%20more%20nuanced%20account%20of%20Mahmud%20Ghazni%20than%20that%20portrayed%20by%20the%20colonial%2Fcommunal%20combine%2C%20where%20he%20sees%20him%20as%20%E2%80%9Cfar%20more%20a%20warrior%20than%20man%20of%20faith%E2%80%9D%20who%20used%20his%20army%20raised%20in%20India%20under%20a%20Hindu%20general%20named%20Tilak%2C%20%E2%80%9Cagainst%20his%20own%20co-religionists%20in%20Central%20Asia%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F08%2F18111502%2FIAM-WHA-100-0566.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22851%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F08%2F18111502%2FIAM-WHA-100-0566.jpg%20851w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F08%2F18111502%2FIAM-WHA-100-0566-300x188.jpg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-614334%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22532%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EPrime%20Minister%20of%20India%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%20addresses%20parliament%20after%20Indian%20Independence%20and%20partition%201947.%20%C2%A9%20World%20History%20Archive%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20nationalist%20intelligentsia%20in%20the%20colonial%20period%20put%20forward%20a%20totally%20different%20interpretation%20of%20Indian%20history%20from%20the%20colonial%2Fcommunal%20one%2C%20where%20they%20were%20not%20trying%20to%20create%20memories%20of%20historical%20%E2%80%98trauma%E2%80%99%20in%20order%20to%20create%20differences%20in%20the%20present.%20On%20the%20contrary%20they%20drew%20on%20the%20reality%20of%20Indian%20society%20and%20how%20it%20organically%20dealt%20with%20religious%2C%20caste%20and%20other%20difference%20through%20birth%20of%20new%20religions%20like%20Buddhism%2C%20Jainism%20and%20Sikhism%20or%20movements%20spanning%20many%20centuries%20like%20the%20Sufi%20and%20Bhakti%20movements.%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%20perhaps%20best%20argued%20this%20position%20in%20his%20magisterial%20magnum%20opus%2C%20The%20Discovery%20of%20India%2C%20written%20from%20prison%20in%20the%201940s.%20The%20lessons%20that%20Nehru%20tried%20to%20draw%20from%20Indian%20history%20were%20connected%20to%20his%20imagining%20India%E2%80%99s%20future%20as%20a%20modern%20democratic%20country%20based%20on%20enlightenment%20values%2C%20%E2%80%98the%20Idea%20of%20India%E2%80%99.%20He%20focused%20on%20a%20critical%20aspect%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20civilizational%20history%3B%20an%20openness%20to%20reason%20and%20rationality%2C%20a%20questioning%20mind%20and%20acceptance%20of%20multiple%20claims%20to%20truth%2C%20a%20dialogical%20tradition%20of%20being%20in%20conversation%20and%20discussion%20with%20each%20other%2C%20the%20ability%20to%20live%20with%20difference%2C%20accommodate%2C%20adjust%2C%20resolve%20and%20transform%20rather%20than%20violently%20crush%20difference.%20Nehru%20draws%20from%20the%20Indus%20valley%20civilisation%2C%20the%20Rig%20Veda%2C%20the%20Upanishads%20the%20epics%20Ramayana%20and%20Mahabharata%2C%20the%20Gita%2C%20Buddha%2C%20A%C5%9Boka%2C%20Alauddin%20Khilji%2C%20Amir%20Khusrau%2C%20Akbar%2C%20Vivekananda%20to%20Gandhi%20to%20illustrate%20the%20above.%20He%20also%20emphasized%20how%20the%20shared%20traditions%20in%20language%2C%20music%2C%20poetry%2C%20painting%2C%20architecture%2C%20philosophy%20and%20everyday%20practice%20cutting%20across%20religion%20and%20caste%20contributed%20to%20the%20creation%20of%20a%20composite%20culture.%20While%20talking%20of%20songs%20composed%20by%20Amir%20Khusrau%20he%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20do%20not%20know%20if%20there%20is%20any%20other%20instance%20anywhere%20of%20songs%20written%20600%20years%20ago%20(in%20the%20ordinary%20spoken%20dialect%20of%20Hindi)%20maintaining%20their%20popularity%20and%20their%20mass%20appeal%20and%20being%20still%20sung%20without%20any%20change%20of%20words%E2%80%9D.%20He%20talked%20of%20the%20emergence%20of%20the%20Indian%20civilization%20that%20occurred%20over%20the%20centuries%20through%20the%20%E2%80%98absorption%E2%80%99%2C%20%E2%80%98assimilation%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98synthesis%E2%80%99%20of%20all%20the%20influences%20India%20was%20exposed%20to%20through%20trade%2C%20invasions%2C%20migration%20and%20inter%20mixing.%20From%20the%20Indus%20Valley%20civilization%20five%20thousand%20years%20ago%20to%20the%20Dravidian%2C%20Aryan-Central%20Asian%2C%20Iranian%2C%20Greek%2C%20Parthian%2C%20Bactrian%2C%20Scythian%2C%20Hun%2C%20Arab%2C%20Turk%2C%20early%20Christian%2C%20Jewish%2C%20Zoroastrian%2C%20Afghan%2C%20Mughal%2C%20etc.%2C%20all%20leaving%20their%20mark%20%E2%80%9Clike%20some%20ancient%20palimpsest%20on%20which%20layer%20upon%20layer%20of%20thought%20and%20reverie%20had%20been%20inscribed%2C%20and%20yet%20no%20succeeding%20layer%20had%20completely%20hidden%20or%20erased%20what%20had%20been%20written%20previously%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20to%20this%20organic%20process%20through%20which%20the%20Indian%20people%20had%20learnt%20to%20negotiate%20differences%20of%20multiple%20religions%2C%20languages%2C%20caste%20etc.%2C%20that%20colonialism%20came%20as%20a%20shock.%20It%20is%20as%20if%20Indian%20history%20%E2%80%98ceased%E2%80%99%2C%20to%20use%20a%20phrase%20used%20by%20the%20African%20revolutionary%2C%20Amilcar%20Cabral%2C%20for%20the%20period%20of%20colonial%20rule%20lasting%20nearly%20200%20years.%20Colonialism%20not%20only%20stopped%20the%20dynamic%20process%20of%20negotiating%20differences%20but%20actually%20froze%20or%20even%20accentuated%20these%20differences.%20And%20the%20communal%20forces%20were%20the%20chief%20instruments%20in%20their%20hands%20for%20accomplishing%20this%20task.%20The%20world%20has%20learnt%20at%20a%20very%20heavy%20cost%2C%20from%20Ireland%2C%20the%20oldest%20colony%2C%20to%20recent%20events%20in%20Palestine%20(about%20the%20Imperialist%20role%20in%20which%20Nehru%20has%20much%20to%20say)%20and%20the%20experience%20of%20large%20parts%20of%20Asia%20and%20Africa%2C%20including%20India%2C%20that%20the%20longest%20lasting%20legacy%20of%20colonialism%20has%20been%20that%20it%20left%20behind%20a%20divided%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20method%20used%20by%20the%20colonial%2Fcommunal%20forces%20to%20create%20a%20religious%20divide%2C%20of%20which%20Nehru%20was%20very%20critical%2C%20was%20the%20colonial%20periodisation%20of%20Indian%20history%2C%20done%20by%20James%20Mill%20in%20the%20early%2019th%20Century%2C%20%E2%80%9Cinto%20three%20major%20periods%3A%20Ancient%20or%20Hindu%2C%20Muslim%20and%20the%20British%20period%E2%80%9D.%20He%20thought%20%E2%80%9Cit%20is%20unscientific%20to%20divide%20history%20like%20this%E2%80%9D%20and%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThis%20division%20is%20neither%20intelligent%20nor%20correct%3B%20it%20is%20deceptive%20and%20gives%20a%20wrong%20perspective.%20It%20deals%20more%20with%20the%20superficial%20changes%20at%20the%20top%20than%20with%20the%20essential%20changes%20in%20the%20political%2C%20economic%20and%20cultural%20development%20of%20the%20Indian%20people%E2%80%9D.%20He%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20wrong%20and%20misleading%20to%20talk%20of%20a%20Muslim%20invasion%20of%20India%20or%20of%20the%20Muslim%20period%20in%20India%2C%20just%20as%20it%20would%20be%20wrong%20to%20refer%20to%20the%20coming%20of%20the%20British%20to%20India%20as%20a%20Christian%20invasion%2C%20or%20to%20call%20the%20British%20period%20in%20India%20a%20Christian%20period%E2%80%9D.%20He%20questioned%20the%20defining%20of%20a%20period%20by%20just%20the%20religion%20of%20the%20ruler%20and%20emphasized%20the%20wider%20social%20and%20economic%20and%20cultural%20factors%20which%20defined%20a%20period%20and%20also%20pointed%20out%20the%20continuities%20and%20cultural%20intermixing%20of%20people%20belonging%20to%20different%20religious%20faiths.%20Later%20historians%20have%20confirmed%20Nehru%E2%80%99s%20position%20while%20critiquing%20the%20colonial%2Fcommunal%20periodization%20of%20Indian%20history.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20Nehru%20was%20extremely%20critical%20of%20looking%20at%20history%20with%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20old%20and%20completely%20out-of-date%20approach%20of%20a%20record%20of%20doings%20of%20kings%20and%20battles%20and%20the%20like%E2%80%9D.%20He%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20whole%20conception%20of%20the%20history%20of%20a%20country%20being%20the%20names%20of%20a%20large%20number%20of%20kings%20and%20emperors%20and%20our%20learning%20them%20by%20heart%2C%20I%20suppose%2C%20is%20long%20dead.%20I%20am%20not%20quite%20sure%20whether%20in%20the%20schools%20and%20colleges%20of%20India%20it%20has%20ceased%20to%20exist%20or%20not%2C%20but%20I%20hope%20at%20any%20rate%20that%20it%20is%20dead%2C%20because%20anything%20more%20futile%20than%20children%E2%80%99s%20study%20of%20the%20record%20of%20kings%E2%80%99%20regions%20and%20battles%20I%20cannot%20imagine%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20contrary%20Nehru%2C%20anticipating%20what%20has%20now%20globally%20become%20an%20accepted%20norm%20in%20cutting%20edge%20historiography%2C%20emphasized%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20social%20aspect%20of%20history%E2%80%9D.%20The%20need%20for%20%E2%80%9Cmuch%20closer%20research%20into%20the%20daily%20lives%20of%20the%20common%20man.%20Maybe%20in%20family%20budgets%20a%20hundred%20or%20a%20thousand%20years%20ago%E2%80%A6which%20make%20us%20realize%20something%20of%20what%20the%20life%20of%20humanity%20was%20in%20the%20past%20age%E2%80%9D.%20As%20he%20put%20it%20in%20his%20characteristically%20beautiful%20prose%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20only%20then%20that%20we%20really%20clothe%20the%20dry%20bones%20of%20history%20with%20life%2C%20flesh%20and%20blood%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENehru%20was%20deeply%20aware%20of%20the%20various%20biases%20in%20history%20writing%20and%20very%20critical%20of%20the%20Eurocentric%20and%20colonial%20approaches%20which%20often%20overlapped%2C%20and%20which%20unfortunately%20exercise%20considerable%20influence%20including%20in%20the%20former%20colonies%20till%20today.%20Giving%20his%20inaugural%20address%20to%20the%20Asian%20History%20Congress%2C%20Nehru%20said%3A%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20immediate%20object%20of%20the%20History%20Congress%20should%20be%20to%20straighten%20out%20all%20the%20twists%20which%20Asian%20history%20has%20received%20at%20the%20hand%20of%20the%20Europeans.%20While%20some%20of%20them%20are%20very%20fine%20historians%2C%20their%20approach%20has%20nevertheless%20been%20based%20on%20Europe%20being%20the%20centre%20of%20the%20world%E2%80%9D.%20He%20continued%2C%20%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20case%20of%20India%2C%20a%20Western%20scholar%2C%20especially%20from%20the%20United%20Kingdom%2C%20inevitably%20tended%20to%20look%20at%20the%20history%20of%20India%20as%20if%20the%20past%20few%20thousand%20years%20were%20a%20kind%20of%20a%20preparation%20for%20the%20coming%20British%20dominion%20in%20India%E2%80%9D.%20However%2C%20Nehru%20warned%20that%20%E2%80%9Cas%20a%20reaction%20to%20that%20sometimes%20our%20own%20historians%20have%20gone%20too%20far%E2%80%A6.%20There%20is%20the%20nationalist%20history%20which%2C%20starting%20from%20a%20strong%20nationalist%20bias%2C%20praises%20everything%20that%20is%20national%20at%20the%20expense%20of%20other%20things%E2%80%9D.%20As%20early%20as%20the%201930s%2C%20reacting%20to%20the%20nationalist%20tendency%20to%20imagine%20a%20%E2%80%98Golden%20age%E2%80%99%20in%20the%20past%20which%20the%20communalists%20used%20to%20create%20a%20religious%20divide%2C%20a%20tendency%20that%20has%20become%20rampant%20today%2C%20he%20said%3A%20%E2%80%9CEverywhere%20are%20to%20be%20found%20people%20who%20consider%20their%20own%20country%20the%20best%2C%20and%20regard%20it%20as%20sacred%20soil.%20They%20only%20study%20their%20ancient%20history%20and%20award%20it%20a%20high%20place%20%E2%80%93%20it%20becomes%20Satyayug%20or%20Ramrajya%3B%20and%20the%20hope%20remains%20that%20the%20same%20may%20be%20restored%E2%80%9D.%20He%20argued%2C%20%E2%80%9CBoth%20these%20approaches%E2%80%A6the%20nationalist%20approach%20and%20imperialist%20approach%20distort%20history.%20They%20sometimes%20suppress%20history%E2%80%9D.24%20Nehru%20showed%20in%20his%20own%20writing%20in%20the%20Glimpses%20of%20World%20History%20and%20Discovery%20of%20India%20how%20one%20could%20be%20firmly%20anti-imperialist%20and%20also%20have%20pride%20in%20one%E2%80%99s%20own%20history%20%E2%80%94%20%E2%80%93%20for%20the%20genuine%20achievements%20without%20resorting%20to%20blind%20imaginary%20glorification%20of%20one%E2%80%99s%20past%20overlooking%20all%20the%20warts%20and%20blemishes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20on%20the%20subject%20of%20Eurocentric%2Fcolonial%20positions%2C%20Nehru%20very%20early%20on%20refutes%20the%20tendency%20to%20obfuscate%20the%20difference%20between%20the%20empires%20of%20the%20Ancient%20and%20medieval%20period%20and%20the%20modern%20colonial%20empires%20emerging%20with%20the%20rise%20of%20capitalism.%20A%20tendency%20which%20has%20continued%20till%20today.%20He%20says%20as%20early%20as%201933%2C%20%E2%80%9C%E2%80%A6%20There%20have%20been%20vast%20empires%20for%20thousands%20of%20years%2C%20but%20modern%20imperialism%20is%20a%20new%20concept%20developed%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%20recent%20years%E2%80%A6.%20But%20very%20few%20of%20us%20have%20understood%20its%20real%20import%20and%20often%20mistake%20it%20for%20imperialism%20of%20the%20old.%20Unless%20we%20understand%20this%20new%20imperialism%20properly%20and%20discern%20its%20roots%20and%20branches%2C%20we%20cannot%20grasp%20the%20conditions%20of%20the%20present-day%20world%20and%20cannot%20properly%20wage%20our%20battle%20for%20freedom%E2%80%9D.%20In%20fact%2C%20throughout%20the%20pages%20of%20the%20voluminous%20Glimpses%20of%20World%20History%2C%20Nehru%20maintains%20and%20highlights%20this%20clear%20distinction%20and%20explores%20the%20very%20complex%20evolution%20of%20modern%20imperialism.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENehru%20repeatedly%20questions%20the%20colonial%20characterisation%2C%20picked%20up%20by%20the%20communalists%2C%20of%20the%20medieval%20period%20when%20many%20of%20the%20rulers%20in%20India%20were%20Muslims%2C%20as%20%E2%80%98foreign%20rule%E2%80%99%2C%20clearly%20distinguishing%20it%20from%20British%20colonial%20rule%2C%20which%20he%20described%20as%20foreign%20rule.%20Lest%20one%20thinks%20it%20is%20stating%20the%20obvious%20one%20may%20point%20out%20that%20our%20current%20Prime%20Minister%20repeatedly%2C%20from%20the%20ramparts%20of%20the%20Red%20Fort%20in%20his%20Independence%20Day%20speech%2C%20his%20speech%20in%20Parliament%20as%20Prime%20Minister%20in%202014%2C%20his%20address%20to%20the%20US%20Congress%20in%202023%2C%20etc.%2C%20has%20reiterated%20the%20RSS%20position%20and%20talked%20of%201000%20years%20of%20foreign%20rule%20(sometimes%20he%20makes%20it%201200%2C%20presumably%20200%20years%20is%20of%20little%20relevance%20in%20a%20long%20history).%20With%20one%20stroke%20all%20Muslims%20rulers%20were%20declared%20as%20foreigners%20from%20whose%20alleged%20loot%20and%20%E2%80%9Cslavery%E2%80%9D%20India%20had%20to%20win%20independence!%20The%20paradox%20is%20that%20the%20forces%20which%20did%20not%20play%20a%20part%20in%20the%20actual%20struggle%20for%20freedom%20against%20British%20colonial%20rule%2C%20except%20to%20weaken%20the%20national%20movement%20against%20it%2C%20talked%20of%20freedom%20from%20a%20so%20called%20%E2%80%98Muslim%E2%80%99%20rule%20in%20the%20medieval%20period!%20Nehru%2C%20while%20critiquing%20the%20%E2%80%98Hindu%2C%20Muslim%20and%20British%20period%E2%80%99%20characterisation%20(discussed%20above)%20commented%20on%20this%20aspect%2C%20distinguishing%20the%20medieval%20period%2C%20when%20many%20rulers%20were%20Muslim%20in%20India%2C%20from%20the%20British%20period%20which%20is%20what%20he%20saw%20as%20a%20period%20of%20foreign%20rule.%20He%20said%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20so-called%20(Hindu)%20ancient%20period%20is%20vast%20and%20full%20of%20change%2C%20of%20growth%20and%20decay%2C%20and%20then%20growth%20again.%20What%20is%20called%20the%20Muslim%20or%20medieval%20period%20brought%20another%20change%2C%20and%20an%20important%20one%2C%20and%20yet%20it%20was%20more%20or%20less%20confined%20to%20the%20top%20and%20did%20not%20vitally%20affect%20the%20essential%20continuity%20of%20Indian%20life.%20The%20invaders%20who%20came%20to%20India%20from%20the%20north-west%2C%20like%20so%20many%20of%20their%20predecessors%20in%20more%20ancient%20times%2C%20became%20absorbed%20into%20India%20and%20part%20of%20her%20life.%20Their%20dynasties%20became%20Indian%20dynasties%20and%20there%20was%20a%20great%20deal%20of%20racial%20fusion%20by%20intermarriage.%20A%20deliberate%20effort%20was%20made%2C%20apart%20from%20a%20few%20exceptions%2C%20not%20to%20interfere%20with%20the%20ways%20and%20customs%20of%20the%20people.%20They%20looked%20to%20India%20as%20their%20home%20country%20and%20had%20no%20other%20affiliations.%20India%20continued%20to%20be%20an%20independent%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20coming%20of%20the%20British%20made%20a%20vital%20difference%20and%20the%20old%20system%20was%20uprooted%20in%20many%20ways.%20They%20brought%20an%20entirely%20different%20impulse%20from%20the%20west%2C%20which%20had%20slowly%20developed%20in%20Europe%E2%80%A6and%20was%20taking%20shape%20in%20the%20beginnings%20of%20the%20industrial%20revolution.%20The%20British%20remained%20outsiders%2C%20aliens%20and%20misfits%20in%20India%2C%20and%20made%20no%20attempt%20to%20be%20otherwise.%20Above%20all%2C%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%20India%E2%80%99s%20history%2C%20her%20political%20control%20was%20exercised%20from%20outside%20and%20her%20economy%20was%20centred%20in%20a%20distant%20place.%20They%20made%20India%20a%20typical%20colony%20of%20the%20modern%20age%2C%20a%20subject%20country%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%20her%20long%20history%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20few%20more%20points%20on%20Nehru%20and%20history%20writing%20which%20are%20relevant%20to%20us%20even%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20very%20early%20on%2C%20Nehru%20was%20a%20votary%20of%20looking%20at%20history%20in%20a%20global%20context%20and%20was%20an%20exponent%20of%20what%20is%20now%20fashionably%20called%20%E2%80%98connected%20histories.%E2%80%99%20He%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20old%20idea%20of%20writing%20a%20history%20of%20any%20one%20country%20has%20become%20progressively%20out%20of%20date.%20It%20is%20impossible%20today%20to%20think%20of%20the%20history%20of%20a%20country%20isolated%20from%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20world.%20The%20world%20is%20getting%20integrated.%20We%20have%20%E2%80%A6%20to%20consider%20history%20today%20in%20a%20world%20perspective%E2%80%9D.%20Globally%2C%20%E2%80%9Cevents%20are%20all%20closely%20inter-related.%20One%20event%20affects%20the%20other%20and%20if%20all%20the%20developments%20of%20world%20history%20are%20taken%20together%20then%20some%20sort%20of%20laws%20and%20causes%20emerge%20and%20we%20can%20understand%20the%20course%20and%20significance%20of%20world%20history.%20By%20knowing%20this%20some%20light%20is%20thrown%20on%20all%20events%20of%20world%20history%20and%20we%20can%20see%20our%20course%20ahead%E2%80%9D.%20Further%20he%20said%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20quite%20impossible%20today%20to%20think%20of%20current%20events%20or%20of%20history%20in%20the%20making%20in%20terms%20of%20any%20one%20nation%20or%20country%20or%20patch%20of%20territory%3B%20you%20have%20inevitably%20to%20think%20of%20the%20world%20as%20whole%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20%E2%80%98man%20of%20action%E2%80%99%2C%20one%20who%20contributed%20significantly%20to%20the%20making%20of%20history%20Nehru%20saw%20the%20need%20to%20keep%20the%20big%20picture%20in%20mind%20while%20approaching%20history.%20He%20said%20%E2%80%9CIt%20has%20been%20given%20to%20us%20in%20the%20present%20age%20to%20play%20a%20part%20in%20the%20making%20of%20history%20and%20for%20a%20person%20who%20does%20that%20it%20becomes%20an%20even%20more%20important%20thing%20to%20understand%20the%20process%20of%20history%20so%20that%20he%20might%20not%20lose%20himself%20in%20trivial%20details%20and%20forget%20the%20main%20sweep%E2%80%9D.%20He%20urged%20the%20historians%20too%20not%20to%20get%20lost%20in%20the%20details%2C%20so%20that%20they%20may%20%E2%80%9Csee%20the%20wood%20a%20little%20more%20and%20not%20be%20lost%20in%20the%20individual%20tree%E2%80%9D.%20He%20added%2C%20%E2%80%9Cany%20subject%20that%20you%20may%20investigate%E2%80%9D%20should%20%E2%80%9Cbe%20viewed%20in%20relation%20to%20a%20larger%20whole.%20Otherwise%2C%20it%20has%20no%20real%20meaning%20except%20as%20some%20odd%20incident%20which%20might%20interest%20you%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAgain%2C%20as%20a%20man%20of%20action%2C%20Nehru%20urged%20%E2%80%9Chistorians%E2%80%A6that%20they%20should%20not%20always%20write%20only%20for%20their%20brother%20historians%E2%80%A6.%20for%20the%20charmed%20circle%20of%20people%20who%20are%20interested%20in%20a%20specifically%20narrow%20aspect%E2%80%9D%20which%20%E2%80%9Closes%20all%20interest%20for%20the%20wider%20public%E2%80%9D.%20They%20should%20%E2%80%9Ctry%20to%20appeal%20to%20the%20minds%20of%20the%20larger%20public%E2%80%94the%20intelligent%20or%20semi-intelligent%20public%E2%80%9D.%20He%20did%20not%20believe%20%E2%80%9Cpopularization%20%E2%80%A6means%20a%20deviation%20from%20scholarship.%20I%20do%20not%20think%20there%20is%20any%20necessary%20conflict%20between%20real%20scholarship%20and%20a%20popular%20approach%E2%80%9D.%20He%20had%20as%20early%20as%201933%20urged%2C%20%E2%80%9Cbooks%20should%20be%20written%20not%20for%20a%20few%20scholarly%20persons%20but%20should%20be%20such%20that%20a%20person%20with%20very%20limited%20reading%E2%80%93a%20farmer%20or%20a%20labourer%20even%E2%80%94should%20be%20able%20to%20understand%20it.%20Unless%20the%20masses%20understand%20it%2C%20our%20labour%20would%20be%20in%20vain%E2%80%9D.%20Some%20of%20the%20tallest%20scholars%20in%20India%20inspired%20by%20the%20Nehruvian%20dream%20did%20try%20to%20do%20what%20he%20desired%2C%20writing%20school-texts%2C%20popular%20pamphlets%20and%20books%2C%20while%20others%2C%20often%20in%20the%20name%20of%20the%20poor%20and%20the%20subalterns%2C%20went%20into%20a%20post-modernist%20discourse%20which%20at%20least%20I%2C%20even%20after%20more%20than%20four%20decades%20of%20trying%20to%20understand%20the%20discipline%20of%20history%2C%20have%20great%20difficulty%20even%20in%20beginning%20to%20decipher.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFinally%2C%20a%20comment%20on%20how%20Nehru%20saw%20his%20role%20in%20taking%20the%20historical%20process%20forward.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20lessons%20he%20learnt%20from%20Indian%20history%20of%20the%20acceptance%20of%20the%20existence%20of%20multiple%20truths%2C%20of%20a%20non-violent%20dialogical%20tradition%2C%20of%20negotiations%20of%20truth%20claims%20and%20conflict%20and%20arriving%20at%20a%20higher%20level%20of%20synthesis%2C%20were%20greatly%20strengthened%20by%20his%20increasingly%20deeper%20understanding%20of%20Gandhiji%20and%20his%20practice.%20This%20involved%20a%20change%20in%20his%20own%20Marxist%20understanding%20which%20he%20had%20argued%20till%20the%20mid%201930s%2C%20as%20seen%20in%20the%20Autobiography%2C%20towards%20a%20more%20complex%20Gramscian%20Marxist%20understanding%20of%20how%20social%20change%20was%20to%20be%20negotiated.%20His%20more%20mature%20understanding%20was%20reflected%20in%20The%20Discovery.%20This%20shift%20has%20often%20been%20seen%20as%20Nehru%E2%80%99s%20contradictory%20and%20vacillating%20nature%2C%20his%20total%20dependence%20and%20subservience%20to%20Gandhiji%2C%20his%20giving%20in%20to%20vested%20interests%20etc.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20insightful%20work%2C%20Manash%20Firaq%20Bhattacharjee%2C%20sees%20Nehru%E2%80%99s%20doubts%2C%20his%20ambivalence%2C%20openness%20and%20engagement%20with%20apparently%20contradictory%20positions%20not%20as%20his%20weakness%20or%20vacillating%20nature%20but%20as%20his%20strength.%20He%20is%20correctly%20critical%20of%20people%20like%20Partha%20Chatterjee%20who%20dismiss%20Nehru%E2%80%99s%20absolutely%20outstanding%20work%2C%20The%20Discovery%20of%20India%2C%20as%20a%20book%20of%20%E2%80%98rambling%2C%20bristling%20with%20the%20most%20obvious%20contradictions%E2%80%99.%20(Other%20scholars%20such%20as%20the%20Eurocentric%20Marxist%2C%20Perry%20Anderson%20also%20shockingly%20rubbish%20Nehru%E2%80%99s%20Discovery%20calling%20it%20%E2%80%9Ca%20steam%20bath%20of%20Schw%C3%A4rmereii%20(over%20enthusiastic%20and%20sentimental)%E2%80%9D%20with%20a%20%E2%80%9CBarbara%20Cartland%20Streak%E2%80%9D!)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Bhattacharjee%20argues%20in%20elegant%20prose%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20idea%20of%20liberty%20needs%20to%20be%20reconciled%20with%20the%20presence%20of%20contradictions.%20No%20idea%20or%20truth-claim%20can%20justify%20the%20sacrifice%20of%20human%20lives.%20It%20would%20mean%20the%20barbarism%20of%20truth.%20Ethics%20provokes%20us%20to%20think%20of%20freedom%20without%20violence.%3Cbr%3E%5CnNehru%20did%20not%20sit%20on%20horseback%20with%20sword%20in%20hand%2C%20and%20rush%20towards%20the%20windmills%20of%20history%20thinking%20they%20were%20giants%20he%20had%20to%20exterminate.%20He%20did%20not%20hallucinate%20from%20the%20desire%20to%20rid%20the%20world%20of%20all%20its%20ills%20and%20create%20a%20gigantic%20prison%20in%20the%20name%20of%20paradise%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20where%20Nehru%20learnt%20from%20Gandhiji.%20He%20accepted%20Gandhiji%E2%80%99s%20position%20that%20however%20good%20the%20end%20the%20means%20had%20to%20be%20ethical%20and%20non%20violent.%20For%20Gandhiji%2C%20his%20deep%20conviction%20on%20non-violence%20did%20not%20emerge%20from%20the%20fact%20that%20it%20was%20a%20brilliant%20tactic%20to%20fight%20the%20British%2C%20which%20of%20course%20it%20was%2C%20but%20from%20his%20philosophical%20position%20that%20nobody%20could%20make%20the%20claim%20of%20having%20arrived%20at%20%E2%80%98transcendental%20truth%E2%80%99%20or%20absolute%20truth.%20His%20belief%20in%20the%20possibility%20of%20multiple%20truths%20and%20multiple%20paths%20to%20the%20seeking%20of%20truth%20would%20not%20allow%20for%20violence%20against%20anyone.%20The%20Enlightenment%20project%20emerging%20from%20Europe%20often%20faltered%20on%20this%20ground%2C%20where%20the%20notion%20of%20possessing%20the%20ultimate%20truth%20justified%20mass%20killings%20by%20revolutionary%20movements%20(in%20the%20name%20of%20democracy%20and%20the%20people)%20thus%20negating%20a%20critical%20aspect%20of%20democracy%2C%20every%20human%20being%E2%80%99s%20right%20to%20differ.%20Gandhiji%20saw%20this%20weakness%20in%20the%20French%20and%20the%20Russian%20Revolution%20as%20compared%20to%20India%E2%80%99s%20struggle%20for%20freedom.%20Attention%20must%20be%20drawn%20here%20to%20Tadd%20Graham%20Fern%C3%A9e%E2%80%99s%20work%2C%20where%20he%20compares%20the%20European%20Enlightenment%20project%20with%20the%20Indian%2C%20Turkish%20and%20Iranian%20efforts%20at%20transition%20to%20modernity%2C%20with%20a%20focus%20on%20the%20Indian%20National%20Movement%20under%20Gandhiji%E2%80%99s%20leadership%20with%20its%20%E2%80%98Ethic%20of%20Reconciliation%20as%20Mass%20Movement%E2%80%99%20as%20well%20as%20the%20%E2%80%98Nehruvian%20effort%20after%20independence%E2%80%99%20at%20drawing%20on%20this%20heritage%2C%20towards%20an%20%E2%80%98Ethic%20of%20Reconciliation%20in%20Nation%20Making%E2%80%99.%20His%20conclusion%20is%20that%20the%20Indian%20experiment%20at%20transition%20to%20modernity%20without%20violence%20remained%20much%20truer%20to%20the%20Enlightenment%20objectives.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBhattacharjee%20has%20done%20us%20a%20favour%20by%20quoting%20extensively%20from%20Octavio%20Paz%2C%20the%20great%20Mexican%20poet%2C%20thinker%2C%20diplomat%20and%20Nobel%20Laureate%2C%20who%20was%20also%20Mexican%20ambassador%20to%20India%20in%20Nehru%E2%80%99s%20time%2C%20showing%20how%20he%20very%20sensitively%20comprehended%20what%20Nehru%20had%20%E2%80%98discovered%E2%80%99%20for%20himself%20from%20Indian%20tradition%20and%20Gandhiji%2C%20and%20very%20importantly%2C%20brilliantly%20interpreted%20Nehru%20and%20his%20supposed%20contradictions.%20It%20is%20well%20worth%20repeating%20them%20here%2C%20if%20for%20no%20other%20reason%20but%20to%20show%20how%20great%20contemporaries%20of%20Nehru%20saw%20him%20in%20contrast%20to%20scholars%20whom%20I%20would%20characterise%20as%20Eurocentric%20if%20not%20colonial%20and%20of%20course%2C%20the%20communal%2C%20fake%20%E2%80%98nationalists%E2%80%99%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20speech%20delivered%20in%201966%2C%20Paz%20says%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20remarkable%20that%20Nehru%2C%20in%20spite%20of%20his%20mainly%20being%20a%20political%20leader%2C%20did%20not%20fall%20into%20the%20temptation%20of%20suppressing%20the%20contradictions%20of%20history%20by%20brute%20force%20or%20with%20a%20verbal%20tour%20de%20pass%C3%A9%20(sleight%20of%20hand).%20%5BIt%5D%20is%20unique%20in%20our%20world%20of%20fanatical%20Manicheans%20(those%20who%20see%20things%20only%20in%20black%20and%20white)%20and%20hangmen%20masked%20as%20philosophers%20of%20history.%20He%20did%20not%20pretend%20to%20embody%20either%20the%20supreme%20good%20or%20the%20absolute%20truth%20but%20human%20liberty%3A%20man%20and%20his%20contradictions%E2%80%A6.%20He%20was%20faithful%20to%20his%20contradictions%20and%20for%20this%20very%20reason%20he%20neither%20killed%20others%20nor%20mutilated%20himself%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAgain%2C%20he%20says%20very%20profoundly%20and%20with%20a%20deep%20understanding%20of%20Nehru%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20contrast%20to%20the%20majority%20of%20the%20political%20leaders%20of%20this%20century.%20Nehru%20did%20not%20believe%20that%20he%20had%20the%20key%20to%20history%20in%20his%20hands.%20Because%20of%20this%20he%20did%20not%20stain%20his%20country%20nor%20the%20world%20with%20blood.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENehru%20tried%20to%20move%20towards%20his%20goal%2C%20what%20he%20thought%20was%20his%20historic%20role%20with%20this%20sensibility.%20This%20meant%20following%20a%20path%20which%20could%20be%20slower%2C%20but%20took%20people%20along%20and%20did%20not%20resort%20to%20violence%20and%20brute%20force%20as%20many%20of%20his%20contemporaries%20trying%20the%20same%20transformation%20did.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F08%2F14193717%2FScreenshot-2022-08-14-at-7.37.12-PM.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22851%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F08%2F14193717%2FScreenshot-2022-08-14-at-7.37.12-PM.png%20851w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F08%2F14193717%2FScreenshot-2022-08-14-at-7.37.12-PM-300x139.png%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-613737%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22393%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EJawaharlal%20Nehru%20delivers%20his%20%E2%80%98Tryst%20with%20Destiny%E2%80%99%20speech%2C%20on%20the%20eve%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20independence.%20Photo%3A%20Wikipedia%2FFair%20Use%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENehru%20and%20the%20Idea%20of%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20may%20ask%20ourselves%20the%20question%20that%20if%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%20was%20such%20an%20evil%20and%20incompetent%20person%20as%20the%20communal%2Fcolonial%20right%20makes%20him%20out%20to%20be%2C%20why%20did%20the%20father%20of%20the%20nation%2C%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%2C%20choose%20him%20as%20his%20successor%20and%20not%20his%20other%20brilliant%20comrades%20like%20C.%20Rajagopalachari%20or%20Sardar%20Patel%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20speech%20at%20the%20AICC%20meeting%20at%20Wardha%20on%2015%20June%201942%20Gandhiji%20declared%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9C%E2%80%A6Somebody%20suggested%20that%20Pandit%20Jawaharlal%20and%20I%20were%20estranged.%20This%20is%20baseless%E2%80%A6.%20You%20cannot%20divide%20water%20by%20repeatedly%20striking%20it%20with%20a%20stick.%20It%20is%20just%20as%20difficult%20to%20divide%20us.%20I%20have%20always%20said%20that%20not%20Rajaji%2C%20nor%20Sardar%20Vallabhbhai%20but%20Jawahar%20will%20be%20my%20successor%E2%80%A6.%20When%20I%20am%20gone%E2%80%A6he%20will%20speak%20my%20language%20too%E2%80%A6.%20Even%20if%20this%20does%20not%20happen%2C%20I%20would%20at%20least%20die%20with%20this%20faith%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhy%20did%20Gandhiji%20have%20such%20tremendous%20faith%20in%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%3F%20One%20can%20surmise%20at%20least%20two%20reasons.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFirst%2C%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%20quintessentially%20represented%20and%20fought%20for%20all%20the%20core%20values%20of%20the%20Indian%20freedom%20struggle%20which%20have%20in%20short%20been%20called%20%E2%80%98The%20Idea%20of%20India%E2%80%99.%20These%20core%20values%20were%20in%20brief%3A%201)%20Sovereignty%2C%20i.e.%2C%20India%20will%20be%20independent%20and%20self-reliant%2C%20and%20oppose%20imperialist%20domination%20globally%3B%202)%20Democracy%2C%20i.e.%2C%20India%20will%20be%20a%20democratic%20country%20with%20adult%20franchise%20and%20with%20equal%20rights%20to%20all%20citizens%2C%20irrespective%20of%20their%20caste%2C%20class%2C%20language%2C%20gender%2C%20region%20or%20ethnicity%3B%203)%20Secularism%2C%20i.e.%2C%20people%20belonging%20to%20different%20religious%20faiths%20will%20have%20equal%20rights%20in%20the%20country.%20India%20will%20not%20be%20a%20majoritarian%20Hindu%20state.%20Secularism%20and%20democracy%20were%20seen%20as%20coterminous%2C%20one%20could%20not%20exist%20without%20the%20other.%20The%20term%20secular-democracy%20was%20often%20used%20conjointly%2C%20just%20as%20communalism%20was%20with%20loyalism%3B%204)%20Pro-poor%20orientation.%20Beginning%20from%20the%20early%20nationalists%20like%20Dadabhai%20Naoroji%20whose%20book%20was%20titled%20%E2%80%98Poverty%20and%20Un-British%20Rule%20in%20India%E2%80%99%20to%20Gandhiji%20turning%20the%20face%20of%20the%20country%20towards%20the%20poor%2C%20the%20Daridranarayan%2C%20to%20the%20revolutionaries%2C%20socialists%20and%20communists%20%E2%80%94%20all%20were%20agreed%20on%20a%20pro-poor%20orientation%20even%20if%20there%20was%20no%20consensus%20on%20socialism%20or%20communism.%205)%20Modern%20scientific%20outlook%20was%20to%20be%20propagated%20(what%20Nehru%20called%20the%20scientific%20temper)%2C%20overcoming%20obscurantism%20and%20blind%20faith.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20must%20be%20noted%20that%20there%20was%20a%20consensus%20among%20the%20entire%20spectrum%20of%20the%20Indian%20national%20movement%20on%20these%20core%20values%20whatever%20may%20have%20been%20their%20other%20differences.%20From%20the%20early%20nationalists%20like%20Naoroji%2C%20Ranade%20and%20Gokhale%2C%20to%20Tilak%20and%20C.R.%20Das%2C%20to%20Bhagat%20Singh%20and%20other%20revolutionaries%2C%20to%20Gandhiji%2C%20Nehru%2C%20Patel%2C%20Subhash%20Bose%2C%20the%20socialists%20like%20Acharya%20Narendra%20Dev%20and%20Jaiprakash%20Narain%20and%20communists%20like%20EMS%20Namboodiripad%2C%20Harkishan%20Singh%20Surjeet%20and%20P.C.%20Joshi%2C%20all%20agreed%20on%20the%20above%20core%20values%20of%20the%20idea%20of%20India.%20Only%20the%20loyalists%20and%20the%20communalists%20of%20all%20hues%20were%20opposed%20to%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENot%20only%20did%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%20fight%20for%20these%20values%20during%20the%20freedom%20struggle%20but%20he%20played%20a%20stellar%20role%20in%20implementing%20these%20ideas%20in%20the%20new%20born%20state%20after%20independence.%20Gandhiji%20perhaps%20anticipated%20this%20capacity%20of%20Nehru%20in%20choosing%20him%20as%20his%20successor.%20In%20fact%2C%20the%20burden%20of%20implementing%20these%20ideas%20fell%20largely%20on%20Nehru%E2%80%99s%20shoulders%20with%20the%20Mahatma%20being%20murdered%20by%20a%20Hindu%20communalist%20within%20six%20months%20of%20India%20gaining%20Independence%20and%20Sardar%20Patel%20passing%20away%20in%201950.%20Nehru%20performed%20this%20task%20with%20great%20%C3%A9lan%20and%20imagination%20as%20India%E2%80%99s%20first%20Prime%20Minister%20for%20about%2017%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20on%20Nehru%E2%80%99s%20role%20after%20Independence%20in%20implementing%20the%20five%20core%20values%20of%20the%20%E2%80%98Idea%20of%20India%E2%80%99%20that%20I%20will%20focus%20on%20today.%20It%20is%20necessary%20to%20do%20so%20as%20each%20element%20of%20the%20Idea%20of%20India%20is%20deeply%20threatened%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20we%20evaluate%20Nehru%E2%80%99s%20role%20in%20implementing%20the%20Idea%20of%20India%20after%20independence%2C%20we%20must%20remind%20ourselves%20of%20what%20economists%20call%20the%20%E2%80%98initial%20conditions%E2%80%99%20from%20which%20he%20had%20to%20start%2C%20to%20get%20an%20idea%20of%20the%20gigantic%20task%20ahead%20of%20him%20at%20independence.%20The%20poet%20Rabindranath%20Tagore%2C%20shortly%20before%20his%20death%2C%20had%20graphically%20anticipated%20the%20condition%20of%20India%20at%20the%20end%20of%20British%20rule.%20He%20said%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20wheels%20of%20fate%20will%20someday%20compel%20the%20English%20to%20give%20up%20their%20Indian%20empire.%20What%20kind%20of%20India%20will%20they%20leave%20behind%2C%20what%20stark%20misery%3F%20When%20the%20stream%20of%20their%20centuries%E2%80%99%20administration%20runs%20dry%20at%20last%2C%20what%20a%20waste%20of%20mud%20and%20filth%20will%20they%20leave%20behind%20them.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%E2%80%98mud%20and%20filth%20left%20behind%E2%80%99%20was%20a%20famine-ridden%20country%20(three%20million%20perished%20in%20a%20man-made%20famine%20just%20four%20years%20before%20independence)%2C%20where%20per%20capita%20income%20and%20foodgrains%20output%20was%20actually%20shrinking%20annually%20for%20the%20past%20three%20decades%20before%20independence%2C%20where%20average%20life%20expectancy%20at%20independence%20was%20a%20shocking%20low%20of%20about%2030%20years%2C%2084%20per%20cent%20of%20all%20Indians%20and%2092%20per%20cent%20women%20were%20illiterate.%20On%20top%20of%20all%20this%2C%20the%20British%20left%20the%20country%20deeply%20divided%20on%20religious%20lines%2C%20with%20millions%20dead%20and%20rendered%20homeless%20in%20a%20communal%20carnage%20that%20happened%20under%20colonial%20tutelage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20a%20gigantic%20task%20indeed%20to%20lift%20India%20out%20of%20this%20misery%20following%20the%20path%20laid%20down%20by%20our%20freedom%20fighters%20in%20their%20imagination%20of%20independent%20India.%20It%20is%20to%20Nehru%E2%80%99s%20credit%20that%20he%20evolved%20a%20multi-pronged%20strategy%20to%20lift%20India%20out%20of%20this%20morass%2C%20which%20in%20fact%20became%20an%20example%20for%20numerous%20other%20countries%20which%20gained%20independence%20from%20colonial%20rule.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20will%20seek%20to%20outline%20how%20Nehru%20undertook%20this%20stupendous%20and%20in%20many%20respects%20historically%20unique%20task%20of%20creating%20a%20modern%20democratic%20nation%20state%20in%20a%20plural%20society%20left%20deeply%20divided%20through%20the%20active%20collusion%20of%20the%20colonial%20state%3B%20of%20promoting%20modern%20industrialization%20within%20the%20parameters%20of%20democracy%20in%20a%20backward%20and%20colonially%20structured%20economy%3B%20of%20finding%20the%20balance%20between%20growth%20and%20equity%20in%20an%20impoverished%2C%20famine-ridden%20country%3B%20of%20empowering%20the%20people%20and%20yet%20expecting%20them%20to%20tighten%20their%20belt%20for%20the%20sake%20of%20the%20nation%20as%20a%20whole%3B%20of%20promoting%20the%20highest%20level%20of%20scientific%20education%2C%20a%20field%20left%20barren%20by%20colonialism%3B%20in%20short%2C%20of%20un-structuring%20colonialism%20and%20bringing%20in%20rapid%20economic%20development%20but%20doing%20it%20consensually%2C%20without%20the%20use%20of%20force%2C%20keeping%20what%20has%20been%20called%20the%20%E2%80%9CNehruvian%20consensus%E2%80%9D%20intact%20in%20the%20critical%20formative%20years%20of%20the%20nation.%20A%20Herculean%20effort%20was%20needed%20to%20achieve%20this%20complex%20task%20and%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%20rose%20to%20the%20occasion%20putting%20everything%20he%20had%20into%20this%20effort%2C%20in%20the%20process%20leaving%20behind%20a%20legacy%20not%20only%20for%20the%20Indian%20people%20but%20for%20all%20the%20peoples%20of%20the%20world%20oppressed%20by%20colonialism%20who%20were%20striving%20to%20liberate%20themselves%20of%20their%20past%2C%20but%20in%20a%20humane%20and%20democratic%20manner.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Communal%20Challenge%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20secular%20vision%20of%20the%20Idea%20of%20India%20was%20severely%20threatened%20at%20the%20point%20of%20the%20very%20birth%20of%20the%20independent%20Indian%20nation%20state%2C%20as%20it%20is%20threatened%20today.%20Much%20can%20be%20learnt%20from%20how%20this%20threat%20was%20dealt%20with%20by%20our%20nationalist%20leaders.%20The%20communal%20challenge%20in%20my%20opinion%20being%20the%20most%20important%20challenge%20before%20our%20country%20today%2C%20I%20shall%20discuss%20this%20aspect%20in%20somewhat%20greater%20detail%20than%20the%20other%20aspects%20of%20the%20Idea%20of%20India%20that%20are%20being%20challenged.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20period%201946%20to%201952%2C%20from%20the%20time%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%20took%20over%20as%20the%20head%20of%20the%20Interim%20government%20till%20he%2C%20as%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20led%20independent%20India%20into%20its%20first%20general%20election%2C%20was%20the%20phase%20when%20the%20secular%20%E2%80%98Idea%20of%20India%E2%80%99%20was%20tested%20against%20the%20most%20overwhelming%20odds.%20Independence%20was%20accompanied%20by%20the%20partition%20of%20the%20country%20and%20widespread%20religious%20communal%20violence.%20It%20was%20a%20holocaust-like%20situation%20where%20an%20estimated%20500%2C000%20were%20killed%20and%20millions%20were%20turned%20homeless%20(nearly%206%20million%20refugees%20poured%20into%20India)%20in%20a%20spate%20of%20communal%20hatred%20and%20violence.%20The%20result%20was%20one%20of%20the%20largest%20transfers%20of%20populations%20in%20human%20history%20in%20a%20short%20span%20of%20just%20a%20few%20years.%20In%20the%20midst%20of%20all%20this%2C%20the%20tallest%20leader%20of%20the%20fledgling%20Indian%20nation%2C%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%2C%20the%20Father%20of%20the%20nation%2C%20was%20felled%20by%20an%20assassin%E2%80%99s%20bullet%2C%20an%20assassin%20who%20was%20put%20up%20to%20challenge%20the%20very%20%E2%80%98Idea%20of%20India%E2%80%99%20the%20Mahatma%20had%20lived%20and%20died%20for.%20In%20this%20atmosphere%20of%20hatred%20and%20violence%2C%20guiding%20India%20to%20its%20first%20democratic%20general%20election%20based%20on%20complete%20adult%20franchise%20appeared%20to%20be%20a%20nearly%20impossible%20task.%20But%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%20took%20the%20challenge%20head%20on%20and%20with%20indomitable%20energy%20saw%20India%20through%20its%20worst%20ever%20crisis%20at%20its%20very%20moment%20of%20birth%20as%20a%20new%20nation.%20It%20was%2C%20in%20the%20words%20of%20an%20Indian%20historian%20in%20a%20recent%20study%2C%20his%20%E2%80%9Cfinest%20hour%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20spiral%20of%20religious%20sectarian%20violence%20engulfed%20India%20in%20the%20run-up%20to%20Independence%20and%20Partition.%20It%20began%20with%20the%20Great%20Calcutta%20Killings%20as%20a%20result%20of%20Muslim%20League%E2%80%99s%20call%20for%20Direct%20Action%20in%20August%201946%2C%20barely%20a%20month%20before%20the%20Interim%20Government%20led%20by%20Nehru%20was%20set%20up%20in%20September%20by%20the%20British%20as%20a%20prelude%20to%20the%20handing%20over%20of%20power.%20The%20very%20next%20month%2C%20in%20October%2C%20large%20scale%20violence%20erupted%20in%20Noakhali%2C%20a%20remote%20district%20of%20Bengal%20with%20the%20Muslim%20League%20government%20that%20ruled%20the%20province%20doing%20little%20to%20stop%20it.%20As%20a%20reaction%20to%20the%20violence%20against%20Hindus%20in%20Calcutta%20and%20Noakhali%2C%20large%20scale%20violence%20against%20Muslims%20broke%20out%20in%20neighbouring%20Bihar%2C%20spreading%20like%20wildfire%2C%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%20rural%20areas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGandhiji%20immediately%20rushed%20to%20the%20villages%20of%20Noakhali%20on%206%20November%201946%20to%20take%20on%20the%20most%20difficult%20task%20of%20trying%20to%20contain%20communal%20violence%20with%20a%20hostile%20Muslim%20League%20government%20in%20power%20in%20the%20province.%20At%20a%20time%20when%20perhaps%20one%20of%20the%20most%20important%20events%20of%20world%20history%2C%20the%20preparation%20for%20transfer%20of%20power%20from%20the%20British%20Empire%20to%20a%20free%20India%2C%20a%20transfer%20which%20was%20followed%20by%20colonial%20empires%20collapsing%20in%20most%20parts%20of%20the%20world%2C%20the%20top%20leader%20of%20the%20Indian%20national%20movement%20which%20ousted%20the%20British%2C%20spent%20four%20months%2C%20till%204%20March%201947%2C%20walking%20on%20village%20paths%20and%20sleeping%20in%20huts%20in%20hamlets%20in%20this%20virtually%20unreachable%2C%20remote%20corner%20of%20India.%20This%20was%20the%20time%20when%20the%20complex%20negotiations%20for%20the%20transfer%20of%20power%20were%20under%20way!%20This%20showed%20the%20utmost%20importance%20Gandhiji%20placed%20on%20fighting%20communalism.%20Nehru%20on%20his%20part%20rushed%20to%20Bihar%2C%20and%20between%204%20to%209%20November%201946%2C%20along%20with%20virtually%20the%20entire%20top%20leadership%20of%20the%20Congress%20Sardar%20Patel%2C%20Rajendra%20Prasad%2C%20Maulana%20Azad%2C%20Acharya%20Kripalani%2C%20Jayaprakash%20Narayan%2C%20Anugraha%20Narain%20Sinha%20and%20many%20others%20toured%20the%20affected%20areas%2C%20determined%20to%20stop%20the%20violence%20immediately.%20%E2%80%9COne%20by%20one%2C%20he%20(Nehru)%20brandished%20all%20the%20weapons%20in%20his%20armoury%2C%20the%20coercive%20power%20of%20the%20state%2C%20the%20prestige%20and%20ideals%20of%20the%20freedom%20struggle%2C%20the%20prestige%20and%20reverence%20for%20Gandhiji%2C%20his%20own%20personal%20prestige%2C%20and%20much%20else%E2%80%9D%20to%20bring%20things%20under%20control.%20He%20put%20his%20own%20life%20at%20stake%20and%20declared%20immediately%20on%20reaching%20Bihar%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20will%20stand%20in%20the%20way%20of%20Hindu-Muslim%20riots.%20Members%20of%20both%20the%20communities%20will%20have%20to%20tread%20over%20my%20dead%20body%20before%20they%20can%20strike%20at%20each%20other%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20the%208th%20of%20November%20things%20were%20under%20control%20in%20Bihar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndependence%20came%20with%20hundreds%20of%20thousands%20of%20refugees%20pouring%20into%20East%20Punjab%20and%20Delhi%20and%20large-scale%20violence%20ensued%20in%20this%20region.%20On%20his%20Independence%20Day%20speech%20from%20the%20Ramparts%20of%20the%20Red%20Fort%20in%20Delhi%20on%2016th%20August%201947%2C%20Nehru%20made%20it%20clear%20that%20communal%20strife%20will%20not%20be%20tolerated%20and%20that%20India%20will%20be%20a%20secular%20state%20and%20not%20the%20mirror%20image%20of%20Pakistan%2C%20a%20Hindu%20state.%20He%20declared%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20first%20charge%20of%20the%20Government%20will%20be%20to%20establish%20and%20maintain%20peace%20and%20tranquillity%20in%20the%20land%20and%20to%20ruthlessly%20suppress%20communal%20strife%E2%80%A6.%20It%20is%20wrong%20to%20suggest%20that%20in%20this%20country%20there%20would%20be%20the%20rule%20of%20a%20particular%20religion%20or%20sect.%20All%20who%20owe%20allegiance%20to%20the%20flag%20will%20enjoy%20equal%20rights%20of%20citizenship%2C%20irrespective%20of%20caste%20and%20creed%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20very%20next%20day%20he%20was%20in%20Punjab%20and%20in%20the%20first%20few%20weeks%20after%20independence%20he%20was%20more%20in%20Punjab%20than%20in%20Delhi.%20Again%2C%20in%20a%20broadcast%20to%20the%20nation%20on%20the%2019th%20of%20August%201947%2C%20he%20asserted%20in%20no%20uncertain%20terms%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20state%20is%20not%20a%20communal%20state%20but%20a%20democratic%20state%20in%20which%20every%20citizen%20has%20equal%20rights.%20The%20Government%20is%20determined%20to%20protect%20these%20rights%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBarely%20had%20the%20communal%20situation%20come%20under%20control%20that%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%20was%20assassinated.%20Nehru%20was%20very%20clear%20that%20%E2%80%9Cthis%20assassination%20was%20not%20the%20act%20of%20just%20one%20individual%20or%20even%20a%20small%20group%E2%80%A6%20behind%20him%20lay%20a%20widespread%20organization%E2%80%9D%20and%20he%20made%20it%20clear%20that%20the%20organization%20he%20was%20referring%20to%20was%20the%20RSS.%20In%20fact%20he%20saw%20it%20as%20an%20effort%20to%20change%20the%20very%20nature%20of%20the%20Indian%20state%20by%20seizing%20power.%20In%20his%20letter%20to%20the%20Chief%20Ministers%20on%205%20February%201948%20he%20did%20not%20mince%20his%20words%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20would%20appear%20that%20a%20deliberate%20coup%20d%E2%80%99etat%20was%20planned%20involving%20the%20killing%20of%20several%20persons%20and%20the%20promotion%20of%20general%20disorder%20to%20enable%20the%20particular%20group%20concerned%20to%20seize%20power.%20The%20conspiracy%20appears%20to%20have%20been%20a%20fairly%20widespread%20one%2C%20spreading%20to%20some%20of%20the%20states%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20a%20threat%20to%20the%20very%20%E2%80%98idea%20of%20India%E2%80%99%20as%20a%20secular%20country%20and%20Nehru%20was%20not%20about%20to%20let%20it%20succeed.%20With%20the%20full%20support%20of%20his%20Home%20Minister%20and%20Deputy%20Prime%20Minister%20Sardar%20Patel%2C%20he%20banned%20the%20RSS%20and%20put%2025%2C000%20of%20its%20activists%20in%20jail.%20Even%20when%20the%20ban%20on%20the%20RSS%20was%20removed%20in%20July%201949%2C%20after%20it%20gave%20written%20assurances%20that%20henceforth%20it%20would%20function%20only%20as%20a%20cultural%20organization%20and%20have%20nothing%20to%20do%20with%20politics%2C%20he%20warned%20the%20chief%20ministers%20of%20the%20fascist%20nature%20of%20the%20RSS%20and%20the%20threat%20of%20their%20renewing%20their%20activities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENehru%E2%80%99s%20commitment%20to%20the%20secular%20ideal%20and%20his%20prescient%20understanding%20of%20the%20grave%20nature%20of%20the%20threat%20from%20the%20communal%20fascist%20forces%20is%20evident%20from%20the%20manner%20in%20which%20he%20converted%20the%20first%20general%20elections%20of%201951%E2%80%9352%20into%20a%20virtual%20referendum%20on%20what%20was%20to%20be%20the%20nature%20of%20the%20Indian%20state.%20Was%20it%20going%20to%20be%20a%20%E2%80%98Hindu%20Rashtra%E2%80%99%2C%20a%20mirror%20image%20of%20%E2%80%98Muslim%20Pakistan%E2%80%99%2C%20or%20a%20secular-democratic%20Indian%20state%3F%20He%20made%20the%20fight%20against%20the%20communal%20political%20groups%20his%20central%20objective%20and%20campaigned%20relentlessly%20for%20realizing%20the%20secular%20vision%20of%20the%20Indian%20national%20movement.%20%E2%80%9CHe%20travelled%20nearly%2040%2C000%20kilometers%20and%20addressed%20an%20estimated%20thirty-five%20million%20people%20or%20one-tenth%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20population.%20The%20result%20was%20that%20in%20a%20peaceful%20fair%20election%20held%20within%20years%20of%20the%20holocaust%20like%20situation%20and%20extreme%20arousal%20of%20communal%20frenzy%2C%20the%20communal%20parties%2C%20the%20Hindu%20Mahasabha%2C%20the%20newly%20formed%20Jana%20Sangh%2C%20and%20the%20Ram%20Rajya%20Parishad%20won%20between%20them%20only%2010%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20in%20a%20house%20of%20489%2C%20and%20polled%20less%20than%20six%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20vote%E2%80%9D.%20It%20was%20a%20stunning%20achievement%20and%20a%20fitting%20tribute%20to%20the%20Indian%20national%20movement.%20Communalism%20was%20pushed%20back%20for%20decades.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%20that%2075%20years%20later%20we%20are%20again%20in%20a%20similar%20situation%20and%20are%20bewildered%20regarding%20how%20to%20combat%20the%20communal%20threat%20to%20the%20survival%20of%20secular%20democracy%20in%20India%2C%20let%20us%20look%20back%20and%20see%20what%20our%20tallest%20leaders%2C%20Gandhiji%20and%20Nehru%2C%20did%20in%20a%20similar%20situation.%20Their%20frontal%20attack%20on%20the%20communal%20forces%20and%20the%20vision%20they%20represented%2C%20treating%20it%20as%20the%20topmost%20priority%20to%20save%20the%20Idea%20of%20India%3B%20their%20standing%20openly%20and%20bravely%20with%20the%20minorities%20in%20independent%20India%2C%20the%20Muslims%20particularly%2C%20as%20they%20were%20the%20chief%20targets%20of%20the%20communalists%3B%20their%20refusal%20to%20compromise%20on%20this%20question%20for%20short%20term%20electoral%20gains%20to%20be%20garnered%20from%20an%20already%20communalised%20people%2C%20as%20happens%20today%3B%20their%20understanding%20that%20without%20secularism%20there%20could%20not%20be%20any%20democracy%20in%20India%20to%20the%20detriment%20of%20the%20entire%20Indian%20people%2C%20are%20some%20of%20the%20lessons%20we%20can%20learn.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20several%20other%20lessons%20we%20can%20learn%20from%20Nehru%20who%20was%20among%20the%20first%20in%20India%20to%20evolve%20a%20complex%20and%20scientific%20understanding%20of%20communalism%2C%20which%20had%20to%20be%20the%20first%20step%20if%20one%20wished%20to%20combat%20it.%20As%20he%20put%20it%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20oft%20repeated%20appeal%20for%20Hindu-Muslim%20unity%2C%20useful%20as%20it%20no%20doubt%20is%2C%20seemed%20to%20me%20singularly%20inane%2C%20unless%20some%20effort%20was%20made%20to%20understand%20the%20causes%20of%20the%20disunity%E2%80%9D.%20In%20a%20section%20called%20%E2%80%98Communalism%20and%20Reaction%E2%80%99%20in%20his%20Autobiography%20written%20during1934%E2%80%93%2035%20and%20in%20several%20other%20writings%20and%20speeches%20which%20I%20shall%20cite%20separately%2C%20Nehru%20explores%20the%20issue%20of%20communalism%20with%20great%20complexity.%20I%20will%20briefly%20highlight%20some%20of%20the%20important%20generalisations%20he%20made%20from%20which%20we%20can%20learn%20even%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStudying%20the%20rise%20of%20communalism%20in%20India%2C%20Nehru%20is%20very%20clear%20that%20it%20was%20a%20modern%20phenomenon%2C%20not%20a%20left%20over%20the%20medieval%20past%3B%20it%20did%20not%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20originate%20with%20the%20arrival%20of%20Islam%20in%20India.%20He%20saw%20communalism%20clearly%20as%20a%20product%20of%20the%20colonial%20period%20with%20active%20connivance%20of%20the%20colonial%20state%3B%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20British%20Government%20%E2%80%A6%20throws%20its%20sheltering%20wings%20over%20a%20useful%20ally%E2%80%9D.%20In%20fact%20he%20traces%20the%20origin%20and%20growth%20of%20communalism%20with%20amazing%20finesse%20anticipating%20what%20was%20confirmed%20by%20much%20scholarly%20work%20that%20has%20emerged%20since.%20He%20traces%20the%20role%20of%20British%20policy%20%E2%80%9Csince%20the%20rising%20of%201857%20%E2%80%A6%20of%20preventing%20the%20Hindu%20and%20Muslim%20from%20acting%20together%2C%20and%20of%20playing%20off%20one%20community%20against%20the%20other%E2%80%9D.%20He%20shows%20how%20a%20number%20of%20factors%20such%20as%20the%20initial%20heavy%20discrimination%20by%20the%20British%20against%20Muslims%20after%20the%201857%20uprising%2C%20seeing%20them%20as%20more%20dangerous%2C%20the%20lagging%20behind%20of%20Muslims%20(as%20compared%20to%20Hindus)%20in%20modern%20education%2C%20in%20social%20reform%2C%20in%20evolving%20a%20modern%20intelligentsia%20and%20a%20Muslim%20bourgeoisie%20and%20particularly%20lagging%20behind%20in%20government%20employment%2C%20created%20a%20fertile%20ground%20for%20the%20evolution%20of%20a%20certain%20kind%20of%20Muslim%20politics.%20A%20politics%2C%20much%20aided%20by%20the%20colonial%20government%2C%20where%20an%20elite%2C%20princely%2C%20landed%20section%20of%20the%20Muslims%20led%20by%20Syed%20Ahmad%20Khan%2C%20Aga%20Khan%2C%20etc.%2C%20offered%20loyalty%20to%20the%20colonial%20government%20and%20opposition%20to%20the%20democratic%20urges%20of%20the%20emerging%20Indian%20national%20movement%20against%20the%20colonial%20government.%20In%20return%20the%20colonial%20government%20granted%20%E2%80%98favours%E2%80%99%20to%20the%20%E2%80%98Muslims%E2%80%99%20as%20a%20community.%20These%20seeds%20of%20communalism%20sown%20by%20British%20connivance%20were%20to%20grow%20among%20other%20communities%20over%20time.%20He%20saw%20that%20while%20the%20communalist%2C%20whether%20Hindu%20or%20Muslim%2C%20spoke%20in%20the%20name%20of%20the%20community%2C%20it%20actually%20did%20not%20represent%20the%20masses%20of%20any%20community%20but%20was%20backed%20by%20the%20vested%20interests%2C%20the%20feudal%20aristocracy%2C%20landlords%2C%20princes%20and%20moneylenders%20who%20feared%20the%20political%20changes%20which%20Indian%20nationalism%20ushered%20in%2C%20and%20supported%20the%20government.%20In%20regions%20where%20different%20economic%20categories%20or%20classes%20belonged%20to%20different%20religions%2C%20the%20economic%20conflict%20%E2%80%9Cwas%20given%20a%20communal%20colouring%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20independence%2C%20in%201952%2C%20Nehru%20added%20the%20capitalists%20among%20the%20vested%20interests%20supporting%20communal%20formations.%20He%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9Cbehind%20the%20fa%C3%A7ade%20of%20religion%2C%20vested%20interests%2C%20particularly%20the%20Zamindars%20and%20the%20capitalists%2C%20were%20fighting%20against%20the%20economic%20policies%20of%20the%20Congress%E2%80%9D.%20Till%20independence%20the%20capitalists%20had%2C%20by%20and%20large%2C%20aligned%20with%20the%20national%20movement%20and%20not%20the%20communal%20loyalists.%20With%20land%20reforms%20pushed%20vigorously%20after%20independence%20by%20Nehru%2C%20overtime%20the%20back%20of%20the%20Zamindari%20forces%20was%20broken.%20As%20Nehru%20said%20in%20October%201951%2C%20%E2%80%9Cjagirdari%20and%20zamindari%20system%20must%20go%20from%20India%E2%80%A6.The%20Hindu%20Mahasabha%2C%20Rashtriya%20Swayamsevak%20Sevak%20Sangh%20or%20the%20Jan%20Sangh%20may%20thrive%20on%20the%20funds%20they%20get%20from%20them%20but%20there%20is%20no%20power%20in%20the%20world%20which%20can%20perpetuate%20the%20system%E2%80%9D.%20Today%20we%20witness%20the%20crony%20capitalists%20performing%20this%20role%20of%20backing%20communal%20forces%20through%20funds%20and%20control%20over%20media%20on%20an%20infinitely%20larger%20scale.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENehru%20perceptively%20argued%20that%20communalists%20had%20nothing%20to%20do%20with%20religion%20or%20with%20culture%20and%20were%20%E2%80%9Csingularly%20devoid%20of%20all%20ethics%20and%20morality%E2%80%9D%20though%20%E2%80%9Cthey%20talk%20bravely%20of%20past%20culture%E2%80%9D.%20He%20also%20noted%20that%20though%20the%20communalists%20%E2%80%9Ccall%E2%80%A6themselves%20non-political%E2%80%9D%20they%20%E2%80%9Cas%20a%20matter%20fact%20function%20politically%20and%20their%20demands%20are%20political%E2%80%9D.%20Only%20their%20politics%20was%20reactionary%20and%20anti-national.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENehru%20had%20realised%20very%20early%20on%20that%20his%20hope%20that%20with%20the%20British%20gone%20communalism%20would%20disappear%20proved%20to%20be%20unfounded.%20In%20the%201930s%2C%20he%20had%20argued%3A%20%E2%80%9CCommunalism%20is%20essentially%20a%20hunt%20for%20favour%20from%20a%20third%20party%20%E2%80%94%20the%20foreign%20power%E2%80%A6.%20Delete%20the%20foreign%20power%20and%20communal%20arguments%20and%20demands%20fall%20to%20the%20ground%E2%80%9D.%20As%20we%20saw%20above%2C%20following%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20assassination%2C%20the%20RSS%20was%20banned%20and%20around%2025%2C000%20RSS%20activists%20were%20put%20in%20jail.%20However%2C%20once%20the%20ban%20was%20lifted%2C%20roughly%20a%20year%20and%20a%20half%20later%2C%20in%20July%201949%2C%20and%20prisoners%20released%2C%20the%20RSS%20resumed%20its%20ideological%20offensive.%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%20repeatedly%20warned%20against%20the%20dangerous%20implications%20of%20this.%20In%20his%20letters%20to%20the%20Chief%20Ministers%20of%20provinces%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20whole%20mentality%20of%20the%20R.S.S.%20is%20a%20fascist%20mentality.%20Therefore%2C%20their%20activities%20have%20to%20be%20closely%20watched%E2%80%9D.%20He%20was%20very%20clear%20and%20repeatedly%20said%20that%20there%20was%20no%20space%20for%20complacency%20after%20the%20spectacular%20defeat%20of%20the%20communal%20forces%20in%20the%20first%20general%20election.%20Writing%20to%20the%20Presidents%20of%20the%20Provincial%20Congress%20Committees%2C%20he%20said%20in%201952%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COne%20good%20thing%20that%20has%20emerged%20from%20these%20elections%20is%20our%20straight%20fight%20and%20success%20against%20communalism.%20That%20success%20is%20significant%20and%20heartening.%20But%20it%20is%20by%20no%20means%20a%20complete%20success%20and%20we%20have%20to%20be%20wary%20about%20this%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENehru%20thought%20that%20the%20first%20election%20taught%20another%20significant%20lesson%20that%20there%20was%20no%20percentage%20in%20compromising%20with%20communalism.%20A%20very%20important%20lesson%20in%20today%E2%80%99s%20context%20in%20India.%20He%20said%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20seen%20at%20last%20that%20we%20need%20not%20be%20afraid%20of%20communalism%20and%20we%20need%20not%20compromise%20with%20it%20as%20many%20Congressman%20did%20for%20fear%20of%20consequences.%20Where%20we%20fight%20it%20in%20a%20straight%20and%20honest%20way%2C%20we%20win.%20Where%20we%20compromise%20with%20it%2C%20we%20lose%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20early%20as%20the%201930s%2C%20Nehru%20had%20rejected%20the%20warning%20by%20friends%20that%20his%20highly%20critical%20%E2%80%9Cattitude%20towards%20communal%20organisations%20will%20result%20in%20antagonizing%20many%20people%20against%E2%80%9D%20him.%20He%20said%20%E2%80%9Cin%20politics%20people%20are%20very%20careful%20of%20what%20they%20say%20and%20do%20not%20say%20lest%20they%20offend%20some%20group%20or%20individual%20and%20lose%20support%E2%80%9D%20but%20then%20he%20was%20%E2%80%9Cyet%20to%20learn%20the%20ways%20of%20politicians%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Cremain%20a%20silent%20witness%E2%80%9D%20when%20the%20nation%20was%20in%20danger.%20He%20therefore%20refused%20to%20compromise%20and%20outright%20condemned%20the%20communal%20organisations.%20An%20AICC%20resolution%20drafted%20by%20him%20in%20March%201952%20read%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20AICC%20expresses%20its%20deep%20gratification%20at%20the%20overwhelming%20response%20of%20the%20electorate%E2%80%9D%20to%20the%20Congress%20policy%20of%20opposing%20communalism.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20response%2C%20however%2C%20must%20not%20lead%20Congressman%E2%80%A6to%20think%20that%20the%20danger%20from%20communal%20tendencies%20is%20wholly%20over.%20Communal%20and%20separatist%20tendencies%20still%20exist%20%E2%80%A6and%20have%20to%20be%20constantly%20watched%20and%20combated%2C%20whether%20they%20are%20Hindu%2C%20Muslim%2C%20Sikh%20or%20other%E2%80%A6.the%20AICC%20declares%20that%20there%20should%20be%20no%20alliance%2C%20cooperation%20or%20understanding%2C%20explicit%20or%20implicit%2C%20between%20the%20Congress%20and%20any%20organization%20which%20is%20essentially%20communal%20in%20character%20or%20working%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20decades%20following%20Nehru%20this%20advice%20was%20unfortunately%20forgotten.%20In%20a%20society%20already%20communalized%20to%20a%20considerable%20extent%2C%20the%20logic%20of%20electoral%20politics%20led%20even%20secular%20parties%20of%20all%20hues%2C%20to%20compromise%20and%20resort%2C%20in%20varying%20degrees%2C%20to%20short%20cuts%20to%20popular%20mobilization%2C%20by%20appealing%20to%20or%20allying%20with%20parties%20that%20appealed%20to%20the%20existing%20communal%20consciousness%20rather%20than%20attempting%20the%20relatively%20difficult%20and%20long-term%20task%20of%20altering%20that%20consciousness.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENehru%20led%20by%20example%20in%20combating%20the%20communal%20forces%20by%20both%20constantly%20critiquing%20communal%20ideology%20and%20using%20state%20power%20when%20needed%20to%20do%20so.%20He%20declared%20on%20Gandhiji%E2%80%99s%20birth%20anniversary%20on%202%20October%201951%3A%20%E2%80%9Cno%20quarter%20would%20be%20given%E2%80%9D%20to%20the%20communal%20forces%20and%20%E2%80%9Cas%20far%20as%20he%20was%20concerned%2C%20he%20would%20fight%20communalism%20till%20the%20last%20breath%20of%20his%20life%20both%20inside%20and%20if%20need%20be%20outside%20the%20Government%E2%80%9D.%20Hearing%20of%20the%20communalists%20talk%20of%20Hindu%20Rashtra%20in%20Delhi%20and%20threaten%20the%20Muslims%20to%20vacate%20their%20houses%20for%20the%20incoming%20refugees%20and%20asking%20them%20to%20go%20to%20Pakistan%2C%20Nehru%20warned%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9Cif%20any%20person%20raises%20his%20hand%20against%20another%20person%20on%20basis%20of%20religion%2C%20all%20the%20resources%20at%20the%20command%20of%20the%20Government%20will%20be%20used%20to%20put%20him%20down%20with%20an%20iron%20hand%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAware%20of%20the%20critical%20role%20played%20by%20the%20police%20officials%20and%20the%20district%20administration%20in%20preventing%20or%20abetting%20communal%20disturbances%20including%20riots%2C%20Nehru%20asked%20his%20chief%20ministers%20not%20to%20accept%20any%20excuses%20%E2%80%9Cand%20put%20a%20black%20mark%20in%20the%20record%20of%20every%20district%20officer%20when%20a%20communal%20incident%20takes%20place%20and%20to%20inform%20him%20of%20this%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECommunal%20ideology%20also%20had%20to%20be%20combatted.%20Nehru%20no%20longer%20believed%2C%20as%20he%20did%20in%20the%201930s%2C%20that%20once%20the%20real%20economic%20issues%20were%20brought%20before%20the%20masses%2C%20the%20%E2%80%9Ccommunal%20problem%20will%20fade%20into%20the%20background%20for%20the%20masses%20will%20be%20far%20more%20interested%20in%20filling%20their%20hungry%20stomachs%E2%80%A6%E2%80%9D%20He%20argued%20in%20October%201951%2C%20%E2%80%9Cwe%20must%20put%20an%20end%20to%20both%20conscious%20and%20unconscious%20communal%20thought%20in%20India.%20There%20can%20be%20no%20compromise%20with%20that%E2%80%A6.Only%20then%20can%20we%20realise%20true%20freedom%20and%20make%20progress%E2%80%9D.%20He%20added%2C%20%E2%80%9Cno%20amount%20of%20economic%20policies%20and%20development%20projects%20would%20be%20of%20any%20use%20if%20the%20people%20were%20divided%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20India%E2%80%99s%20recent%20history%20shows%2C%20the%20hope%20that%20economic%20development%20or%20growth%20of%20economistic%20class%20struggles%20would%20by%20itself%20lead%20to%20the%20erosion%20of%20communalism%2C%20has%20been%20repeatedly%20belied.%20Communalism%20has%20often%20spread%20in%20economically%20developed%20areas%20and%20people%20suffering%20from%20hunger%20have%20often%20turned%20to%20communalism%20and%20communal%20parties%20and%20not%20necessarily%20class%20struggle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEmphasising%20the%20critical%20importance%20of%20an%20ideological%20battle%20to%20challenge%20the%20communal%20onslaught%2C%20Nehru%20tells%20his%20chief%20ministers%20shortly%20after%20independence%2C%20when%20the%20RSS%20threat%20was%20still%20very%20strong%3A%20%E2%80%9CThose%20who%20are%20impelled%20by%20a%20faith%20in%20a%20cause%20can%20seldom%20be%20crushed%20by%20superior%20force.%20They%20can%20only%20be%20defeated%20by%20higher%20idealism%20as%20well%20as%20a%20vision%20and%20a%20capacity%20to%20work%20for%20the%20cause%20that%20represents%20these%20objectives%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENehru%20spoke%20very%20strongly%20against%20the%20spreading%20of%20hate%20ideology%20and%20advocated%20strong%20measures%20against%20it%20even%20if%20it%20involved%20curbing%20the%20freedom%20of%20the%20press.%20While%20he%20believed%20that%20%E2%80%9Cevery%20human%20being%20has%20the%20right%20to%20express%20his%20opinion%20even%20if%20it%20is%20a%20criticism%20against%20me%E2%80%9D%20and%20did%20not%20%E2%80%9Clike%20the%20idea%20of%20suppressing%20freedom%20of%20expression%20of%20newspapers%2C%20even%20if%20their%20views%20are%20wrong%E2%80%9D%2C%20yet%20he%20made%20an%20exception.%20In%20a%20long%20speech%20delivered%20from%20the%20Ramlila%20Ground%20in%20Delhi%20on%2023%20September%201956%2C%20shortly%20before%20the%20second%20general%20election%2C%20Nehru%20talked%20of%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20Hindu%20Mahasabha%2C%20Jana%20Sangh%2C%20Rashtriya%20Swayamsevak%20Sangh%20and%20the%20Muslim%20organisations%20which%20have%20now%20taken%20the%20place%20of%20the%20Muslim%20League%20and%20if%20it%20is%20possible%20for%20such%20a%20thing%20to%20happen%2C%20are%20even%20worse%20than%20the%20Muslim%20League%E2%80%9D%20who%20%E2%80%9Crake%20up%20religious%20emotions%20and%20incite%20trouble%E2%80%9D.%20In%20this%20context%20he%20said%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20have%20been%20deeply%20perturbed%E2%80%A6by%20the%20way%20some%20newspapers%20incite%20violence%20and%20spread%20false%20rumours%20and%20outright%20lies.%20Therefore%20I%20have%20reached%20the%20conclusion%20that%20the%20newspapers%20which%20spread%20communal%20hatred%20and%20violence%20should%20be%20controlled.%20I%20am%20all%20in%20favour%20of%20freedom%20of%20every%20kind%20but%20if%20that%20freedom%20means%20rioting%20and%20inflaming%20the%20people%20or%20snatching%20away%20the%20others%E2%80%99%20freedom%20or%20spreading%20hatred%2C%20then%20they%20should%20be%20prevented%20by%20law%20and%20dealt%20with%20strictly%E2%80%A6.%20We%20shall%20not%20allow%20communal%20violence%20or%20hatred%20to%20be%20spread%2C%20whether%20it%20is%20the%20Hindus%2C%20Muslims%20or%20Sikhs%20or%20Christians%20who%20indulge%20in%20such%20activities%E2%80%A6.%20I%20am%20going%20to%20suggest%20to%20my%20%E2%80%A6Home%20Minister%2C%20Shri%20Govind%20Ballabh%20Pant%E2%80%A6a%20law%20be%20passed%20as%20soon%20as%20possible%20because%20this%20situation%20cannot%20be%20tolerated%20any%20longer%20that%20the%20newspapers%20should%20deliberately%20spread%20lies%20and%20rumours%20and%20create%20enmity%20and%20make%20money%20out%20of%20all%20this%2C%20instead%20of%20being%20punished.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20a%20contrast%20between%20Nehru%20as%20Prime%20Minister%20taking%20such%20a%20stand%20and%20the%20current%20situation%20where%20the%20press%20and%20the%20visual%20media%20is%20playing%20a%20much%20worse%20role%20and%20the%20police%20and%20administration%20often%20colluding%20with%20the%20communal%20forces%20under%20the%20benign%20gaze%20of%20the%20state%20if%20not%20its%20active%20encouragement!%20In%20fact%20perhaps%20the%20most%20important%20factor%20in%20the%20survival%20and%20reassertion%20of%20the%20communal%20forces%20in%20India%20was%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20secular%20forces%20failed%20to%20undertake%20any%20sustained%20ideological%20work%20to%20combat%20communal%20ideology%2C%20nor%20were%20they%20able%20to%20use%20state%20power%20to%20firmly%20contain%20the%20communal%20forces.%20The%20Hindu%20communalists%20led%20by%20the%20RSS%20as%20well%20as%20minority%20Sikh%20and%20Muslim%20communalists%20continued%20their%20propaganda%2C%20including%20in%20the%20education%20system.%20Claiming%20to%20be%20only%20a%20%E2%80%98cultural%E2%80%99%20organisation%2C%20the%20RSS%20continued%20spreading%20their%20divisive%20hate%20ideology%2C%20proving%20Nehru%E2%80%99s%20belief%20right%20that%20the%20communalists%20say%20one%20thing%20but%20do%20the%20opposite%20in%20practice.%20The%20divisive%20hate%20ideology%20was%20spread%20through%20propaganda%20in%20the%20RSS%20shakhas%2C%20rumours%2C%20newspapers%2C%20pamphlets%20and%20through%20a%20network%20of%20educational%20institutions%20called%20the%20Saraswati%20Shishu%20Mandirs%2C%20the%20first%20of%20which%20was%20started%20in%201952%20in%20the%20presence%20of%20the%20RSS%20Chief%20M.S.%20Golwalkar.%20(The%20RSS%20presence%20in%20this%20sensitive%20sphere%20has%20grown%20phenomenally%20in%20the%20decades%20after%20Nehru%2C%20particularly%20when%20it%20had%20access%20to%20state%20power%20such%20as%20during%201977%E2%80%9379%2C%201999%E2%80%932004%20and%202014%20onwards%2C%20with%20its%20organization%20looking%20after%20education%2C%20the%20Vidya%20Bharati%2C%20in%20its%20official%20website%20claiming%20that%20in%202022%E2%80%9323%20it%20had%2012%2C065%20formal%20schools%20with%2031%2C58%2C658%20students%20and%207%2C797%20non-formal%20schools%20with%201%2C88%2C%20334%20students.%20It%20also%20claimed%20a%20reach%20in%2092%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20districts%20in%20India!)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENothing%20substantial%20was%20done%20by%20secular%20political%20parties%20to%20counter%20such%20harmful%20propaganda%20through%20either%20state%20action%20or%20sustained%20anti%20communal%20ideological%20work%20at%20the%20ground%20level.%20The%20honourable%20exception%20was%20the%20effort%20made%20in%20the%201960s%20through%20the%20NCERT%20to%20bring%20to%20our%20school%20children%20scientific%20and%20secular%20texts%20free%20from%20communal%20and%20colonial%20prejudices.%20The%20tallest%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20historians80%20and%20other%20social%20scientists%20were%20persuaded%20to%20write%20textbooks%20for%20school%20children%2C%20which%20remained%20popular%20for%20decades%20thereafter%20for%20their%20outstanding%20quality.%20However%2C%20even%20this%20effort%20was%20gradually%20snuffed%20out%20by%20the%20growing%20communal%20forces%2C%20using%20state%20power%20whenever%20they%20got%20access%20to%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUltimately%2C%20during%20the%20NDA%20regime%20led%20by%20the%20BJP%20(1999%E2%80%932004)%2C%20these%20texts%20were%20removed%20and%20replaced%20with%20another%20set%20of%20books.%20Such%20was%20the%20poor%20quality%20of%20the%20books%20and%20the%20communal%20bias%20in%20them%20that%20the%20Indian%20History%20Congress%20was%20constrained%20to%20bring%20out%20a%20book%20in%202003%20called%20History%20in%20the%20New%20NCERT%20Textbooks%3A%20A%20Report%20and%20an%20Index%20of%20Errors.%20The%20report%20concluded%3A%20%E2%80%9COften%20the%20errors%20are%20apparently%20mere%20products%20of%20ignorance%3B%20but%20as%20often%20they%20stem%20from%20an%20anxiety%20to%20present%20History%20with%20a%20very%20strong%20chauvinistic%20and%20communal%20bias.%20The%20textbooks%20draw%20heavily%20on%20the%20kind%20of%20propaganda%20that%20the%20so%20called%20Sangh%20Parivar%20publications%20have%20been%20projecting%20for%20quite%20some%20time%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMore%20shocking%20was%20what%20happened%20after%20the%20communal%20forces%2C%20particularly%20after%201999%2C%20acquired%20state%20power%20at%20the%20national%20level%20to%20rapidly%20spread%20communalism%20through%20the%20education%20system%20and%20other%20means%20which%20led%20to%20one%20of%20the%20worst%20pogroms%20in%20Indian%20history%20since%20independence%2C%20(Gujarat%2C%202002).%20The%20secular%20forces%20led%20by%20the%20Congress%20came%20back%20to%20power%20with%20the%20slogan%20of%20secularizing%20education%2C%20of%20%E2%80%98de-Talibanising%E2%80%99%20education%2C%20and%20in%20the%20ten%20long%20years%20that%20they%20were%20in%20power%20from%202004%20to%202014%2C%20unfortunately%20not%20enough%20was%20done%20on%20this%20front.%20The%20NCERT%20textbooks%20brought%20out%20during%20the%20BJP%20regime%20(1999%E2%80%932004)%20were%20replaced%20with%20secular%20and%20scientific%20texts%20written%20by%20a%20wide%20range%20of%20eminent%20scholars%20from%20all%20over%20the%20country.%20However%2C%20no%20effort%20was%20made%20to%20prevent%20virulently%20communal%20texts%20such%20as%20those%20brought%20out%20by%20the%20RSS%20from%20being%20continued%20to%20be%20taught%20in%20large%20number%20of%20RSS%20schools.%20Their%20record%20in%20being%20able%20to%20use%20state%20power%20to%20bring%20to%20book%20those%20complicit%20in%20the%20Gujarat%20tragedy%20was%20equally%20dismal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20few%20more%20important%20lessons%20to%20be%20learnt%20from%20Nehru%20on%20the%20issue%20of%20communalism.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENehru%20since%20the%201930s%20made%20a%20subtle%20distinction%20between%20minority%20and%20majority%20communalism.%20Nehru%20was%20empathetic%20to%20the%20minority%20condition%20and%20their%20fears%20when%20he%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CHonest%20communalism%20is%20fear%3B%20false%20communalism%20is%20reaction.%20To%20some%20extent%20this%20fear%20is%20justified%2C%20or%20is%20at%20least%20understandable%2C%20in%20a%20minority%20community.%20We%20see%20this%20fear%20overshadowing%20the%20communal%20sky%20in%20India%20as%20a%20whole%20so%20far%20as%20Muslims%20are%20concerned%3B%20we%20see%20it%20as%20an%20equally%20potent%20force%20in%20the%20Punjab%20and%20Sind%20so%20far%20as%20the%20Hindus%20are%20concerned%2C%20and%20in%20the%20Punjab%2C%20the%20Sikhs%E2%80%9D.%20The%20colonial%20state%20he%20said%20stoked%20these%20fears%20and%20pulled%20the%20minority%20communalists%20towards%20loyalism.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20criticising%20minority%20communalism%2C%20Nehru%20felt%20that%20there%20was%20the%20need%20to%20allay%20the%20fears%20of%20the%20minority%20by%20the%20majority%20rather%20than%20exacerbate%20these%20fears.%20%E2%80%9CA%20special%20responsibility%20does%20attach%20to%20the%20Hindus%20in%20India%20both%20because%20they%20are%20the%20majority%20community%20and%20because%20economically%20and%20educationally%20they%20are%20more%20advanced%E2%80%9D.%20The%20founding%20fathers%20of%20the%20Indian%20national%20movement%20and%20that%20of%20the%20Indian%20National%20Congress%20since%20its%20inception%20had%20adopted%20this%20approach.%20The%20Hindu%20communalists%20then%2C%20as%20they%20do%20now%2C%20saw%20this%20as%20a%20policy%20of%20%E2%80%98appeasement%E2%80%99%20of%20the%20minorities%20and%20adopted%20a%20stance%20which%20worsened%20matters.%20As%20Nehru%20put%20it%3A%20%E2%80%9CThe%20(Hindu)%20Mahasabha%2C%20instead%20of%20discharging%20that%20responsibility%2C%20has%20acted%20in%20a%20manner%20which%20has%20undoubtedly%20increased%20the%20communalism%20of%20the%20Muslims%20and%20made%20them%20distrust%20the%20Hindus%20all%20the%20more.%20The%20only%20way%20it%20has%20tried%20to%20meet%20their%20communalism%20is%20by%20its%20own%20variety%20of%20communalism%E2%80%9D.%20Nehru%20then%20goes%20on%20to%20make%20the%20classic%20statement%20which%20should%20be%20the%20mantra%20of%20all%20secularists%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COne%20communalism%20does%20not%20end%20the%20other%3B%20each%20feeds%20on%20the%20other%20and%20both%20fatten%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%20he%20also%20pointed%20out%20very%20early%20in%20the%201930s%20the%20phenomenon%20that%20while%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20Hindu%20and%20the%20Muslim%20communalists%20attack%20each%20other%20in%20public%20they%20cooperate%20in%20the%20Assembly%20and%20elsewhere%20in%20helping%20Government%20to%20pass%20reactionary%20measures.%E2%80%9D%20This%20phenomenon%20has%20continued%20over%20the%20decades%20till%20today.%20After%20all%20the%20chief%20enemy%20of%20the%20communal%20forces%20is%20the%20secular%20forces%20as%20they%20question%20their%20raison%20d%E2%80%99etre%20while%20the%20communalism%20of%20the%20other%20helps%20them%20grow%20even%20more%20or%20%E2%80%9Cfatten%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20understanding%20the%20%E2%80%98fears%E2%80%99%20that%20help%20the%20growth%20of%20minority%20communalism%2C%20it%20did%20not%20lead%20Nehru%20to%20be%20soft%20towards%2C%20leave%20alone%20support%2C%20minority%20communalism.%20When%20he%20was%20%E2%80%9Cchided%20for%20not%20blaming%20Muslim%20communalists%E2%80%9D%20while%20making%20a%20strong%20critique%20of%20Hindu%20communalism%20of%20the%20Hindu%20Sabha%20in%20a%20speech%20delivered%20at%20the%20Banaras%20Hindu%20University%20on%2012%20November%201933%2C%20at%20the%20invitation%20of%20the%20Vice%20Chancellor%2C%20Madan%20Mohan%20Malaviya%20(who%20incidentally%20was%20one%20of%20the%20early%20leaders%20of%20the%20Sabha)%2C%20Nehru%20made%20a%20very%20important%20point%3A%20the%20need%20to%20critique%20the%20communalism%20of%20the%20audience%20one%20is%20addressing.%20He%20said%20%E2%80%9Cit%20would%20have%20been%20entirely%20out%20of%20place%20for%20me%2C%20speaking%20to%20a%20Hindu%20audience%2C%20to%20draw%20attention%20to%20Muslim%20communalists%20and%20reactionaries.%20It%20would%20have%20been%20preaching%20to%20the%20converted%20as%20the%20average%20Hindu%20is%20well%20aware%20of%20them.%20It%20is%20far%20more%20difficult%20to%20see%20one%E2%80%99s%20own%20fault%20than%20to%20see%20the%20failing%20of%20others%E2%80%9D.86%20The%20critiquing%20of%20communalism%20of%20the%20other%20community%20than%20the%20one%20being%20addressed%20is%20easy%20and%20can%20even%20amount%20to%20pandering%20to%20the%20communalism%20of%20the%20audience.%20An%20important%20lesson%20even%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENehru%2C%20in%20fact%2C%20was%20as%20critical%20of%20minority%20communalism%20as%20of%20majority%20communalism%3B%20he%20believed%20that%20%E2%80%9Cthere%20is%20no%20essential%20difference%20between%20the%20two%E2%80%9D.%20He%20had%20no%20hesitation%20in%20describing%20Muslim%20League%20leaders%20and%20Muslim%20communalists%20as%20loyalists%2C%20%E2%80%9Cdefinitely%20anti-national%20and%20political%20reactionaries%20of%20the%20worst%20kind%E2%80%9D.%20A%20lesson%20to%20be%20learnt%20here%20as%20there%20has%20been%20a%20tendency%20in%20the%20years%20after%20independence%20of%20certain%20secular%20forces%20to%20exhibit%20a%20softness%20towards%20minority%20communalism%2C%20or%20towards%20parties%20that%20took%20support%20of%20minority%20communalists%2C%20often%20on%20the%20plea%20that%20they%20were%20relatively%20backward%20or%20were%20being%20discriminated%20against%20by%20the%20majority%20community.%20This%20tendency%20was%20exhibited%20even%20by%20sections%20of%20the%20Left.%20This%20was%20a%20major%20factor%20in%20enabling%20the%20majority%20communalists%20to%20extend%20their%20influence.%20A%20heavy%20price%20was%20paid%20for%20ignoring%20the%20sage%20advice%20given%20by%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%20referred%20to%20earlier%2C%20that%20%E2%80%9Cone%20communalism%20does%20not%20end%20the%20other%3B%20each%20feeds%20on%20the%20other%20and%20both%20fatten%E2%80%9D.%20Softness%20towards%20minority%20communalism%20made%20the%20growth%20of%20majority%20communalism%20much%20easier.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInterestingly%2C%20in%20contrast%20to%20the%20Hindu%20communal%20critique%20of%20Nehru%20being%20soft%20on%20minority%20communalism%20and%20appeasing%20them%2C%20Nehru%20and%20the%20Indian%20nationalist%20leadership%20was%20also%20accused%20of%20the%20opposite.%20Somewhat%20in%20line%20with%20the%20colonial%20position%2C%20they%20were%20accused%20of%20not%20being%20sensitive%20to%20and%20accommodating%20minority%2FMuslim%20demands%2C%20such%20as%20the%20separate%20electorates%2C%20and%20hence%20pushing%20the%20country%20towards%20a%20bloody%20partition.%20This%20old%20view%20has%20been%20repeated%20recently%2C%20by%20some%20Eurocentric%20Marxists%20like%20Perry%20Anderson%2C89%20and%20surprisingly%20by%20an%20admirer%20and%20fine%20scholar%20of%20Nehru%20in%20many%20other%20aspects%2C%20Manash%20Firaq%20Bhattacharjee%2C%20whom%20I%20have%20referred%20to%20appreciatively%20above.%20He%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20possibility%20that%20the%20fear%20of%20the%20minority%20against%20majoritarianism%20may%20be%20real%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20occur%20to%20Nehru%E2%80%9D.%20Also%2C%20he%20sees%20the%20nationalist%20critique%20of%20minority%20identity%20politics%20in%20a%20%E2%80%9Ccommunal%2Fnational%20binary%E2%80%9D%20as%20problematic%20and%20says%20it%20has%20%E2%80%9Can%20anti-minoritarian%20streak%20%E2%80%A6%20that%20can%20be%20termed%20secular%20majoritarianism%E2%80%9D.%20He%20says%20%E2%80%9CTo%20pit%20communalism%20against%20nationalism%20is%20a%20Nehruvian%20error%E2%80%9D.%20Bhattacharjee%20grossly%20misreads%20the%20ideology%20and%20the%20actual%20history%20of%20Indian%20national%20movement%20when%20he%20sees%20the%20nationalists%20as%20seeing%20only%20minority%20identity%20politics%20as%20%E2%80%98communal%E2%80%99%2C%20emerging%20%E2%80%9Csurreptitiously%E2%80%9D%20from%20a%20%E2%80%9Cmajoritarian%20reluctance%20to%20share%20power%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20tallest%20leaders%20of%20the%20Indian%20national%20movement%20led%20by%20Gandhiji%20and%20Nehru%20put%20their%20lives%20at%20stake%20to%20protect%20minority%20rights%2C%20enable%20the%20religious%20minorities%20to%20have%20equal%20citizenship%20rights%20in%20the%20Indian%20republic%2C%20but%20refused%20to%20do%20so%20by%20pandering%20to%20minority%20identity%20politics%20as%20it%20would%20stand%20against%20the%20whole%20republican%20idea%20of%20citizenship.%20It%20is%20an%20absolute%20canard%20to%20describe%20the%20Indian%20nationalist%20position%20as%20%E2%80%9Csecular%20majoritarianism%E2%80%9D%20with%20%E2%80%9Can%20anti-minoritarian%20streak%20(since%20the%20late%201920s)%E2%80%9D%2C%20as%20Bhattacharjee%20does.%20The%20national%20movement%20was%20correct%20in%20erecting%20a%20%E2%80%9Ccommunal%2Fnational%E2%80%9D%20binary.%20Communal%20politics%20by%20definition%20broke%20up%20the%20%E2%80%98nation%E2%80%99%20in%20a%20multi-religious%20country.%20That%20is%20why%20the%20colonial%20state%20constantly%20encouraged%20and%20supported%20communalism%20of%20all%20varieties%20and%20it%20is%20a%20historical%20fact%20that%20the%20communal%20forces%20who%20did%20politics%20of%20religious%20identity%2C%20whether%20they%20be%20of%20minority%20or%20majority%2C%20allied%20with%20the%20colonial%20state%20and%20saw%20the%20Congress%20which%20spoke%20of%20a%20nation%20where%20religion%20would%20not%20determine%20politics%20as%20the%20chief%20enemy.%20Empowering%20politics%20based%20on%20religion%20was%20the%20colonial%20project%20and%20could%20not%20be%20that%20of%20the%20nationalists%20and%20ought%20not%20be%20that%20of%20such%20a%20fine%20scholar%20of%20Nehru%20as%20Bhattacharjee%2C%20or%20Eurocentric%20Marxists%20like%20Perry%20Anderson.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20completely%20missing%20Nehru%E2%80%99s%20subtle%20understanding%20of%20minority%20fears%20while%20opposing%20minority%20communalism%20(discussed%20above)%2C%20the%20portrayal%20of%20Nehru%20as%20%E2%80%98Majoritarian%E2%80%99%20is%20a%20total%20travesty.%20The%20Hindu%20majoritarians%20would%20not%20have%20wished%20him%20dead%20if%20it%20were%20so.%20In%20fact%20a%20more%20ardent%20critic%20of%20majoritarian%2C%20Hindu%20communalism%20in%20India%20would%20be%20difficult%20to%20find.%20In%201933%20he%20said%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20policy%20of%20the%20Hindu%20Mahasabha%E2%80%A6is%20one%20of%20cooperation%20with%20the%20foreign%20government%20so%20that%2C%20by%20abasing%20themselves%20before%20it%2C%20might%20get%20a%20few%20crumbs.%20This%20is%20a%20betrayal%20of%20the%20freedom%20struggle%2C%20denial%20of%20every%20vestige%20of%20nationalism%2C%20suppressive%20of%20every%20manly%20instinct%20in%20the%20Hindus%20%E2%80%A6.%20Anything%20more%20degrading%2C%20reactionary%2C%20anti-national%2C%20anti-progressive%20and%20harmful%20than%20the%20policy%20of%20the%20Hindu%20Mahasabha%20is%20difficult%20to%20imagine%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20much%20for%20Nehru%E2%80%99s%20so%20called%20%E2%80%98secular%20majoritarian%E2%80%99%20streak.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20also%20to%20be%20noted%20that%20Nehru%20was%20also%20among%20the%20first%20to%20emphasize%20that%20majority%20communalism%20easily%20%E2%80%9Cmasquerades%20under%20a%20nationalist%20cloak%E2%80%9D.%20Minority%20communalism%20on%20the%20other%20hand%20%E2%80%9Cgrew%20and%20fed%20itself%20%E2%80%A6on%20separatism%E2%80%9D.%20He%20said%20%E2%80%9CIt%20must%20be%20remembered%20that%20the%20communalism%20of%20a%20majority%20community%20must%20of%20necessity%20bear%20a%20closer%20resemblance%20to%20nationalism%20than%20the%20communalism%20of%20the%20minority%E2%80%A6.%20%E2%80%98Hindu%20Nationalism%E2%80%99%E2%80%A6is%20but%20another%20name%20for%20communalism%E2%80%9D.%20Nehru%2C%20therefore%2C%20categorically%20reiterates%20that%20Hindu%20communal%20organisations%20may%20call%20themselves%20nationalist%20but%20are%20in%20reality%20%E2%80%9Canti-national%20and%20reactionary%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20current%20type%20of%20masculine%2C%20aggressive%2C%20alpha-male%20nationalism%20that%20is%20being%20paraded%20around%20by%20the%20Hindutva%20forces%20was%20squarely%20characterised%20by%20Nehru%20and%20the%20Indian%20national%20movement%20as%20%E2%80%98anti%20national%E2%80%99.%20It%20is%20important%20to%20remind%20ourselves%20of%20this%20as%20there%20has%20been%20a%20gradual%20ceding%20of%20the%20nationalist%20space%20by%20the%20secular%20forces%20which%20has%20contributed%20a%20great%20deal%20to%20enabling%20communalists%2C%20who%20were%20pro-colonial%20and%20thereby%20played%20an%20anti-national%20role%20when%20the%20Indian%20people%20were%20struggling%20for%20freedom%2C%20to%20successfully%20masquerade%20today%20as%20the%20real%20nationalists%20and%20garner%20the%20tremendous%20mass%20appeal%20that%20the%20nationalist%20sentiment%20commands.%20The%20very%20acceptance%20of%20the%20self-description%20of%20the%20majority%20communalists%20as%20%E2%80%98Hindu%20Nationalists%E2%80%99%20was%20a%20grave%20error.%20During%20the%20entire%20national%20movement%20for%20independence%2C%20they%20were%20called%20communalists%2C%20not%20Hindu%20nationalists%2C%20as%20it%20was%20so%20obviously%20a%20contradiction%20in%20terms%3B%20by%20restricting%20nation%20to%20the%20Hindus%2C%20the%20others%20were%20left%20out%2C%20thus%20dividing%20the%20nation%20itself.%20But%20the%20phrase%20gained%20currency%20among%20foreign%20journalists%2C%20commentators%20and%20academics%20writing%20for%20foreign%20audiences%20unfamiliar%20with%20the%20meaning%20of%20the%20term%20%E2%80%98communalism%E2%80%99%20as%20used%20in%20the%20Indian%20context%20and%20is%20now%20unfortunately%20routinely%20used%20by%20Indian%20analysts%20and%20journalists.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20secular%20forces%20have%20made%20it%20easier%20for%20the%20communalists%20to%20occupy%20the%20nationalist%20space%20by%20themselves%20neglecting%2C%20critiquing%20and%20even%20ridiculing%2C%20the%20national%20liberation%20struggle%20and%20its%20tallest%20leaders.%20The%20condemning%20of%20Gandhiji%2C%20Nehru%2C%20Patel%2C%20Tilak%2C%20Aurobindo%20as%20communal%20or%20semi-communal%2C%20with%20a%20%E2%80%98majoritarian%E2%80%99%20streak%2C%20the%20branding%20of%20the%20national%20movement%20as%20bourgeois%2C%20and%20its%20leaders%20as%20agents%20of%20the%20bourgeoise%20if%20not%20of%20imperialism%20itself%2C%20or%20as%20upper%20caste%20leaders%20fighting%20for%20their%20prescriptive%20groups%20rather%20than%20representing%20the%20people%20of%20the%20country%2C%20etc.%2C%20was%20done%20by%20secular%20ideologues%2C%20including%20from%20the%20Left%2C%20such%20as%20most%20recently%20by%20Perry%20Anderson.%20The%20need%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20was%20to%20first%20own%20up%20the%20ancestry%20and%20the%20great%20legacy%20of%20the%20Indian%20national%20movement%2C%20one%20of%20the%20most%20powerful%20national%20liberation%20struggles%20in%20the%20world%2C%20and%20then%2C%20standing%20on%20its%20shoulder%2C%20build%20upon%20it%20by%20making%20advances%2C%20going%20beyond%20the%20breakthroughs%20made%20by%20that%20struggle.%20Its%20rejection%20simply%20made%20it%20easy%20for%20the%20communalists%20to%20appropriate%20its%20legacy.%20Witness%20the%20attempt%20to%20appropriate%20Gandhi%2C%20Patel%2C%20Tilak%2C%20Aurobindo%2C%20Bhagat%20Singh%2C%20Subhash%20Bose%2C%20etc.%2C%20by%20the%20majoritarian%20communal%20forces%20while%20each%20one%20of%20them%20were%20deeply%20secular.%20Nehru%20was%20spared%20this%20ignominy%2C%20perhaps%20as%20he%20was%20seen%20as%20too%20sharp%20a%20critic%20of%20communalism%20to%20be%20appropriated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFinally%2C%20a%20major%20contribution%20of%20Nehru%20was%20to%20repeatedly%20warn%20of%20the%20fascist%20nature%20of%20communalism.%20As%20Bipan%20Chandra%20wrote%3A%20%E2%80%9CNehru%20was%E2%80%A6the%20first%20to%20see%20communalism%20as%20a%20form%20of%20fascism.%20Before%201947%2C%20he%20saw%20the%20close%20resemblance%20between%20the%20post-1937%20Muslim%20League%20and%20fascism%20both%20in%20terms%20of%20methods%2C%20techniques%20of%20hatred%20and%20violence%2C%20organization%20and%20style%20of%20leadership%20and%20in%20terms%20of%20language%20and%20ideology.%20After%201947%2C%20he%20began%20to%20apply%20this%20understanding%20to%20Hindu%20and%20Sikh%20communalism%2C%20especially%20to%20the%20Rashtriya%20Swayamsevak%20Sangh%20(RSS)%E2%80%9D.%20In%20December%201947%2C%20a%20few%20months%20before%20the%20assassination%20of%20the%20Mahatma%2C%20Nehru%20as%20Prime%20Minister%20warned%20the%20Chief%20Ministers%3A%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20a%20great%20deal%20of%20evidence%20to%20show%20the%20RSS%20is%20an%20organization%20which%20is%20in%20the%20nature%20of%20a%20private%20army%20and%20which%20is%20definitely%20proceeding%20on%20the%20strictest%20Nazi%20lines%2C%20even%20following%20the%20technique%20of%20organization%E2%80%9D.%20Even%20after%20the%20ban%20on%20the%20RSS%20following%20Gandhiji%E2%80%99s%20murder%20was%20lifted%2C%20in%201949%2C%20following%20a%20written%20assurance%20that%20they%20would%20not%20engage%20in%20politics%20and%20remain%20only%20a%20cultural%20organization%2C%20Nehru%20warned%20the%20Chief%20Ministers%3A%20%E2%80%9CReports%20reach%20us%20that%20the%20RSS%20is%20again%20resuming%20some%20of%20its%20activities%E2%80%A6.%20But%20it%20must%20always%20be%20remembered%20that%20the%20whole%20mentality%20of%20the%20RSS%20is%20a%20fascist%20mentality.%20Therefore%2C%20their%20activities%20have%20to%20be%20closely%20watched%E2%80%9D.%20He%20warned%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CCommunalism%20bears%20a%20striking%20resemblance%20to%20the%20various%20forms%20of%20fascism%20that%20we%20have%20seen%20in%20other%20counties.%20It%20is%20in%20fact%20the%20Indian%20version%20of%20fascism%E2%80%A6.%20It%20plays%20upon%20the%20basest%20instincts%20of%20man.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20another%20occasion%20he%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CCommunalism%20was%20diametrically%20opposed%20to%20democracy%20and%20usually%20relied%20on%20Nazi%20and%20Fascist%20methods%E2%80%9D.%20In%20a%20public%20speech%20in%20Delhi%20on%202%20October%201951%2C%20while%20warning%20against%20the%20various%20aspects%20of%20communalism%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9Ccommunalism%E2%80%A6.I%20call%20it%20by%20another%20name%E2%80%94fascism%E2%80%9D%2C%20by%20following%20this%20path%20%E2%80%9Cultimately%20the%20result%20would%20be%20similar%20to%20what%20happened%20to%20Hitler%20and%20fascism%20in%20Europe.%20I%20do%20not%20want%20India%20to%20follow%20that%20terrible%20path%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20all%20these%20early%20warnings%20what%20we%20are%20witnessing%20is%20the%20playing%20out%20of%20the%20fascist%20threat%20in%20India.%20Having%20acquired%20governmental%20power%20with%20an%20absolute%20majority%2C%20the%20Hindu%20communalists%20find%20that%20India%20is%20still%20not%20a%20Hindu%20state%20or%20Hindu%20Rashtra.%20The%20effort%20therefore%20now%20is%20to%20change%20the%20character%20of%20the%20Indian%20state%20from%20a%20secular%20state%20to%20a%20Hindu%20state.%20This%20involves%20not%20only%20acquiring%20governmental%20power%2C%20but%20also%20changing%20the%20character%20of%20all%20the%20state%20apparatuses%20and%20changing%20the%20mindset%20of%20the%20people%2C%20of%20civil%20society%20at%20large.%20All%20of%20them%20had%20to%20be%20communalized.%20This%20in%20turn%20involved%20control%20over%20the%20bureaucracy%2C%20police%2C%20judiciary%2C%20media%2C%20the%20education%20system%20and%20containment%20of%20free%20speech%20and%20civil%20liberties.%20It%20also%20involved%20the%20withdrawal%20of%20the%20civil%20rights%20of%20the%20religious%20minorities%20and%20shutting%20out%20their%20voices%20as%20well%20as%20of%20those%20who%20tried%20to%20speak%20up%20for%20them.%20All%20this%20could%20not%20be%20achieved%20without%20use%20of%20coercion%20and%20force%20and%20even%20violence.%20The%20regime%20therefore%20began%20to%20take%20on%20a%20fascist%20character%2C%20or%20as%20Prabhat%20Patnaik%20put%20it%20%E2%80%9CFascism%20arrives%20in%20camouflage%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20very%20recent%20article%20for%20The%20Guardian%2C%20Jason%20Stanley%2C%20philosopher%20at%20Yale%20University%20and%20the%20author%20of%20the%20celebrated%20work%2C%20How%20Fascism%20Works%2C104%20makes%20a%20scathing%20critique%20of%20the%20current%20situation%20in%20India.%20A%20brief%20extract%20is%20in%20order%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20hallmarks%20of%20fascism%20are%20everywhere.%20School%20textbooks%20are%20being%20rewritten%20to%20reinforce%20the%20fake%20history%20behind%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20Hindu%20nationalist%20agenda.%20Topics%20like%20the%20theory%20of%20evolution%20and%20the%20periodic%20table%20have%20been%20replaced%20with%20traditional%20Hindu%20theories%2C%20and%20academics%20have%20been%20silenced%20for%20calling%20out%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20election%20malpractices.%20The%20government%20has%20weaponized%20education%20in%20the%20manner%20typical%20of%20fascist%20regimes%20%E2%80%A6.%20There%20are%20other%20clear%20indications%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20slide%20towards%20fascism.%20On%20press%20freedom%2C%20India%20ranks%20161st%20out%20of%20180%20countries%2C%20sandwiched%20between%20Venezuela%20(at%20159)%20and%20Russia%20(at%20164)%E2%80%A6.%20India%E2%80%99s%20minorities%20face%20lynchings%20and%20the%20bulldozing%20of%20their%20homes%2C%20among%20other%20abuses.%20Ten%20percent%20of%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20Muslims%20live%20in%20India%2C%20over%20200%20million%20in%20all%3B%20as%20Gregory%20Stanton%2C%20the%20founder%20and%20director%20of%20Genocide%20Watch%2C%20has%20warned%20in%20a%20US%20congressional%20briefing%2C%20we%20are%20seeing%20in%20India%20the%20beginning%20of%20what%20would%20be%20by%20far%20the%20largest%20genocide%20in%20history%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bulldozer%20appears%20to%20have%20become%20the%20frightening%20imagery%20as%20well%20as%20the%20reality%20of%20punishing%20the%20minorities.%20The%20most%20recent%20%E2%80%98bulldozing%E2%80%99%20of%20the%20minorities%20was%20done%20right%20next%20to%20the%20capital%2C%20Delhi%2C%20in%20August%202023%2C%20following%20a%20deliberately%20provoked%20conflict%20in%20the%20Mewat%20region.%20The%20Punjab%20and%20Haryana%20High%20Court%20was%20constrained%20to%20take%20suo%20moto%20action%20intervening%20against%20the%20reported%20targeted%20bulldozing%20of%20properties%20of%20the%20Muslim%20minority%20saying%20the%20issue%20arises%20%E2%80%9Cwhether%20the%20buildings%20belonging%20to%20a%20particular%20community%20are%20being%20brought%20down%20under%20the%20guise%20of%20law%20and%20order%20problem%20and%20an%20exercise%20of%20ethnic%20cleansing%20is%20being%20conducted%20by%20the%20state%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFaced%20with%20a%20similar%20communal%20upheaval%2C%20Nehru%20had%20some%20advice%20for%20the%20way%20ahead%20from%20which%20we%20may%20learn.%20A%20winning%20of%20an%20election%2C%20arrest%20of%20a%20few%20and%20banning%20of%20certain%20organisations%20may%20be%20a%20first%20step%20ahead%20but%20was%20not%20going%20to%20be%20enough.%20Addressing%20lakhs%20of%20people%20shortly%20after%20the%20murder%20of%20the%20Mahatma%20by%20a%20communalist%2C%20he%20said%3A%20%E2%80%9CThe%20Government%20have%20arrested%20some%20persons%20and%20put%20them%20in%20jails%20and%20have%20declared%20two%20or%20three%20organisations%20unlawful.%20If%20by%20these%20actions%20%E2%80%A6it%20is%20thought%20that%20the%20whole%20thing%20is%20over%20then%20people%20are%20mistaken.%20We%20have%20to%20uproot%20this%20despicable%20communalism.%20It%20must%20be%20obliterated%20from%20this%20land%20so%20that%20it%20may%20not%20take%20roots%20again.%20This%20poison%20has%20%E2%80%A6%20permeated%20the%20land%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20poison%20had%20to%20be%20fought%2C%20as%20we%20saw%20above%2C%20not%20only%20with%20%E2%80%9Csuperior%20force%E2%80%9D%20but%20a%20%E2%80%9Chigher%20idealism%E2%80%9D.%20The%20%E2%80%98higher%20idealism%E2%80%99%20Nehru%20and%20the%20leaders%20of%20his%20time%20offered%20was%20a%20humane%2C%20inclusive%20nationalism%20and%20socialism.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBuilding%20Democracy%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20threat%20to%20Indian%20democracy%20posed%20by%20communalism%2C%20or%20by%20%E2%80%98communal%20fascism%E2%80%99%2C%20as%20Amartya%20Sen%2C%20perhaps%20first%2C%20described%20it%2C%20is%20now%20perceived%20globally.%20Michelguglielmo%20Torri%2C%20arguably%20the%20foremost%20Italian%20scholar%20on%20India%2C%20has%20outlined%20the%20rapid%20growth%20in%20recent%20years%20of%20the%20forces%20trying%20to%20transform%20India%E2%80%99s%20secular%20democracy%20into%20a%20Hindu%20State%20(Rashtra)%20and%20the%20repressive%20authoritarian%20manner%20in%20which%20it%20is%20being%20done%2C%20leading%20to%20a%20situation%20where%20he%20says%20India%20can%20no%20longer%20be%20called%20a%20full%20democracy.%20In%20fact%2C%20international%20bodies%20such%20as%20the%20V-Dem%20Institute%20of%20Sweden%2C%20the%20US-based%20Freedom%20House%2C%20and%20The%20Economist%E2%80%99s%20EIU%20(Economist%20Intelligence%20Unit)%2C%20which%20produces%20the%20Democracy%20Index%2C%20are%20no%20longer%20accepting%20India%20as%20a%20full%20democracy.%20%E2%80%98A%20democratic%20backsliding%E2%80%99%20is%20said%20to%20be%20occurring%20and%20India%20is%20being%20variously%20described%20as%20%E2%80%98a%20partially%20free%20democracy%E2%80%99%2C%20%E2%80%98a%20flawed%20democracy%E2%80%99%20or%20even%20%E2%80%98an%20electoral%20autocracy%E2%80%99.%20The%20downgrading%20was%20based%20on%20what%20was%20perceived%20as%20the%20current%20regime%20promoting%20anti-minority%20feeling%20and%20legislation%2C%20the%20violation%20of%20human%20rights%20with%20%E2%80%98the%20diminishing%20of%20freedom%20of%20expression%2C%20the%20media%20and%20civil%20society%20hav(ing)%20gone%20the%20furthest%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHow%20far%20we%20have%20moved%20from%20Nehru%E2%80%99s%20dream%3F%20What%20can%20we%20learn%20from%20Nehru%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%2C%20democracy%20and%20civil%20liberties%20were%20absolute%20values%2C%20which%20could%20not%20be%20compromised%20for%20any%20goal%2C%20however%20laudable%2C%20be%20it%20planning%2C%20economic%20development%20or%20social%20justice.%20This%20impacted%20critically%20on%20how%20these%20other%20goals%20were%20sought%20to%20be%20achieved.%20%E2%80%9CI%20would%20not%E2%80%9D%2C%20declared%20Nehru%2C%20%E2%80%9Cgive%20up%20the%20democratic%20system%20for%20anything%E2%80%9D.%20In%20this%20he%20was%20reflecting%20faith%20in%20a%20non-negotiable%20core%20of%20the%20Indian%20national%20movement%2C%20democracy%20and%20civil%20liberties%2C%20best%20expressed%20by%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%20in%20his%20inimitable%20idiom%3A%20%E2%80%9CCivil%20liberty%20consistent%20with%20the%20observance%20of%20non-violence%20%E2%80%A6%20is%20the%20foundation%20of%20freedom.%20There%20is%20no%20room%20there%20for%20dilution%20or%20compromise.%20It%20is%20the%20water%20of%20life.%20I%20have%20never%20heard%20of%20water%20being%20diluted%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%201931%20Karachi%20Resolution%20of%20the%20Congress%2C%20which%20formed%20the%20basic%20kernel%20of%20the%20future%20Constitution%20of%20India%2C%20and%20was%20drafted%20by%20Nehru%20and%20moved%20by%20Gandhiji%2C%20had%20as%20its%20first%20item%3A%20%E2%80%9CEvery%20citizen%20of%20India%20has%20the%20right%20to%20free%20expression%20of%20opinion%2C%20the%20right%20of%20free%20association%20and%20combination%2C%20and%20the%20right%20to%20assemble%20peacefully%20and%20without%20arms%E2%80%9D.%20Nehru%20was%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20strongest%20force%20behind%20founding%20the%20Indian%20Civil%20Liberties%20Union%20in%201936%20as%20a%20non-party%2C%20non-sectarian%20organisation%E2%80%9D.%20Nehru%20persuaded%20Rabindranath%20Tagore%20to%20become%20the%20Honorary%20President%20of%20the%20Indian%20Civil%20Liberties%20Union%20and%20Sarojini%20Naidu%20as%20the%20functioning%20chairperson%2C%20and%20actively%20encouraged%20the%20formation%20of%20several%20such%20unions%20in%20the%20provinces.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFreedom%20of%20the%20press%20was%20an%20essential%20aspect%20of%20civil%20liberties.%20Defining%20what%20he%20meant%20by%20the%20freedom%20of%20the%20press%2C%20Nehru%20said%20in%201940%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%98The%20freedom%20of%20the%20press%20does%20not%20consist%20in%20our%20permitting%20such%20things%20as%20we%20like%20to%20appear.%20Even%20a%20tyrant%20is%20agreeable%20to%20this%20kind%20of%20freedom.%20Civil%20liberty%20and%20freedom%20of%20press%20consist%20in%20our%20permitting%20what%20we%20do%20not%20like%2C%20in%20our%20putting%20up%20with%20criticism%20of%20ourselves%E2%80%A6%E2%80%99%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENehru%E2%80%99s%20commitment%20to%20a%20free%20press%20was%20absolute%20and%20remained%20as%20strong%20when%20he%20was%20in%20government%20as%20it%20was%20when%20he%20was%20leading%20the%20struggle%20against%20the%20colonial%20state.%20No%20cartoonist%20had%20to%20go%20to%20jail%20in%20his%20times%2C%20nor%20did%20stand-up%20comedians%20or%20journalists%20before%20they%20performed%20or%20were%20yet%20to%20write%20a%20story!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20seeing%20democracy%20and%20civil%20liberties%20as%20essential%20values%20in%20themselves%2C%20Nehru%20strongly%20believed%20that%20a%20country%20as%20diverse%20as%20India%20could%20be%20held%20together%20only%20by%20a%20non-violent%2C%20democratic%20way%20of%20life%2C%20and%20not%20by%20force%20or%20coercion.%20Only%20a%20democratic%20structure%20that%20gave%20space%20to%20various%20linguistic%2C%20religious%2C%20cultural%2C%20political%2C%20and%20socio-economic%20trends%20to%20express%20themselves%20could%20hold%20India%20together.%20Almost%20as%20if%20anticipating%20the%20danger%20faced%20by%20the%20nation%20today%2C%20he%20said%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20too%20large%20a%20country%20with%20too%20many%20legitimate%20diversities%20to%20permit%20any%20so-called%20%E2%80%98strong%20man%E2%80%99%20to%20trample%20over%20people%20and%20their%20ideas%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20careful%20not%20to%20allow%20himself%20to%20fall%20prey%20to%20populism%20or%20plebiscitary%2Fmajoritarian%20democracy%20at%20a%20time%20when%20he%2C%20after%20Gandhiji%E2%80%99s%20and%20Patel%E2%80%99s%20death%2C%20towered%20over%20the%20Indian%20political%20spectrum%20and%20could%20easily%20smother%20opposition%20to%20himself%20and%20his%20policies.%20He%20correctly%20saw%20that%20the%20heart%20of%20democracy%20lay%20in%20respecting%20difference%20of%20opinion%2C%20even%20if%20it%20be%20that%20of%20a%20minority.%20He%20said%20on%202%20June%201950%2C%20before%20the%20first%20general%20elections%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20am%20not%20afraid%20of%20the%20opposition%20in%20this%20country%20and%20I%20do%20not%20mind%20if%20opposition%20groups%20grow%20up%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20some%20theory%2C%20practice%20or%20constructive%20theme.%20I%20do%20not%20want%20India%20to%20be%20a%20country%20in%20which%20millions%20of%20people%20say%20%E2%80%9Cyes%E2%80%9D%20to%20one%20man%2C%20I%20want%20a%20strong%20opposition%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20telling%20example%20of%20Nehru%20respecting%20opposition%20and%20his%20conviction%20that%20India%20should%20not%20countenance%20any%20tendency%20towards%20the%20emergence%20of%20a%20%E2%80%98dictator%E2%80%99%20or%20any%20one%20%E2%80%98strong%20man%E2%80%99%2C%20was%20a%20critique%20he%20wrote%20of%20himself%20under%20a%20pseudonym%20at%20a%20time%20when%20he%20was%20at%20the%20peak%20of%20his%20popularity.%20It%20was%20as%20if%20he%20was%20warning%20himself%20and%20the%20Indian%20people%20at%20large%20against%20any%20such%20tendency%20emerging%20in%20himself%20and%20in%20Indian%20politics!%20Elected%20President%20of%20the%20Indian%20National%20Congress%20for%20two%20consecutive%20years%2C%20he%20wrote%20an%20article%20(using%20the%20pseudonym%20Chanakya)%20titled%20%E2%80%98Rashtrapati%E2%80%99%20or%20%E2%80%98President%E2%80%99%20in%20a%20popular%20journal%20in%20October%201937%2C%20warning%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMen%20like%20Jawaharlal%20with%20all%20their%20capacity%20for%20great%20and%20good%20work%2C%20are%20unsafe%20in%20a%20democracy%E2%80%A6.%20A%20little%20twist%20and%20Jawaharlal%20might%20turn%20a%20dictator%20sweeping%20aside%20the%20paraphernalia%20of%20a%20slow-%20moving%20democracy.%20He%20might%20still%20use%20the%20language%20and%20slogan%20of%20democracy%20and%20socialism%2C%20but%20we%20all%20know%20how%20fascism%20has%20fattened%20on%20this%20language%E2%80%A6.%20He%20has%20all%20the%20makings%20of%20a%20dictator%20in%20him%E2%80%94%20vast%20popularity%2C%20a%20strong%20will%20directed%20to%20a%20well-defined%20purpose%2C%20energy%2C%20pride%2C%20organisational%20capacity%2C%20ability%2C%20hardness%20and%20with%20all%20his%20love%20of%20the%20crowd%2C%20an%20intolerance%20of%20others%20and%20a%20certain%20contempt%20for%20the%20weak%20and%20the%20inefficient%E2%80%A6.%20His%20over-mastering%20desire%20to%20get%20things%20done%2C%20to%20sweep%20away%20what%20he%20dislikes%20and%20build%20anew%2C%20will%20hardly%20brook%20for%20long%20the%20slow%20process%20of%20democracy%E2%80%A6.%20Caesarism%20is%20always%20at%20the%20door%2C%20and%20is%20it%20not%20possible%20that%20Jawaharlal%20might%20fancy%20himself%20as%20a%20Caesar%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENehru%20was%20warning%20himself%20and%20his%20people%20against%20any%20compromises%20with%20democracy%20and%20civil%20liberties.%20While%20he%20succeeded%20in%20great%20measure%20in%20himself%20sticking%20scrupulously%20to%20the%20democratic%20path%20and%20in%20making%20the%20democratic%20path%20a%20part%20of%20the%20common%20sense%20of%20the%20Indian%20people%2C%20the%20dangers%20he%20was%20alluding%20to%20have%20not%20lost%20their%20salience%20for%20India%20today%2C%20sixty%20years%20after%20the%20end%20of%20the%20Nehru%20era.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20unfortunately%2C%20%E2%80%98Mukti%E2%80%99%20(deliverance)%20from%20any%20opposition%20is%20declared%20as%20the%20goal%3B%20Congress%20mukt%2C%20%E2%80%98Lutyens%20Delhi%E2%80%99%20mukt%2C%20Left-liberal%20mukt%2C%20andolanjeevi%2Fparjeevi%20(agitationists%2Fparasites)%20mukt%2C%20independently%20thinking%20universities%20like%20JNU%20mukt%2C%20NGOs%20mukt%2C%20Amnesty%20International%20India%20mukt%2C%20Human%20Rights%20Organisations%20mukt%2C%20are%20some%20examples%20of%20what%20%E2%80%98Bharat%E2%80%99%20must%20be%20mukt%20of!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20nurturing%20a%20robust%20opposition%20through%20a%20free%20expression%20of%20ideas%20through%20an%20independent%20media%2C%20Nehru%20also%20paid%20a%20great%20deal%20of%20attention%20to%20other%20critical%20institutions%20of%20a%20functional%20democracy%2C%20such%20as%20the%20parliament.%20The%20respect%20he%20gave%20to%20the%20parliament%20and%20parliamentary%20practice%20and%20code%20of%20conduct%2C%20right%20up%20to%20his%20death%2C%20was%20legendary%20and%20could%20be%20an%20abject%20lesson%20to%20our%20present%20parliamentarians.%20He%20took%20great%20care%20to%20institutionalize%20the%20cabinet%20system%20of%20government.%20Not%20only%20did%20he%20not%20usurp%20all%20powers%20to%20himself%2C%20he%20refused%20to%20give%20in%20to%20the%20tendency%20among%20many%20of%20his%20colleagues%20to%20leave%20important%20policy%20decisions%20to%20him.%20C.D.%20Deshmukh%2C%20who%20was%20Finance%20Minister%20in%20Nehru%E2%80%99s%20cabinet%20from%201950%E2%80%9356%2C%20recorded%20in%20his%20autobiography%20that%20%E2%80%9CNehru%20as%20head%20of%20the%20cabinet%20was%20gentle%2C%20considerate%20and%20democratic%2C%20never%20forcing%20a%20decision%20on%20his%20colleagues%E2%80%A6%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENehru%20was%20very%20careful%20in%20trying%20to%20build%20democratic%20institutions%20with%20as%20little%20interference%20of%20the%20state%20as%20was%20possible%20whether%20it%20be%20the%20judiciary%2C%20bureaucracy%20and%20other%20institutions.%20This%20was%20particularly%20true%20of%20academic%20institutions%20with%20which%20all%20of%20us%20here%20are%20particularly%20involved.%20He%20said%20in%20December%201947%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CA%20university%20stands%20for%20humanism.%20For%20tolerance%2C%20for%20reason%2C%20for%20the%20adventure%20of%20ideas%20and%20the%20search%20for%20truth%20%E2%80%A6%20If%20universities%20discharge%20their%20duty%20adequately%2C%20then%20it%20is%20well%20with%20the%20nation%20and%20the%20people.%20But%20if%20the%20temple%20of%20learning%20itself%20becomes%20a%20home%20of%20narrow%20bigotry%20and%20petty%20objectives%2C%20how%2C%20then%2C%20will%20a%20nation%20prosper%20or%20a%20people%20grow%20in%20stature%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20of%20the%20finest%20institutions%20were%20created%20and%20nurtured%20in%20his%20time.%20Unfortunately%2C%20many%20of%20these%20institutions%2C%20like%20my%20university%2C%20JNU%2C%20are%20struggling%20to%20survive%20the%20current%20assault%20on%20them%20where%20%E2%80%98the%20adventure%20of%20ideas%E2%80%99%20and%20dissent%20is%20suppressed%2C%20often%20brutally.%20Students%20are%20beaten%20up%2C%20arrested%20and%20put%20in%20jail%20for%20years%20and%20even%20denied%20bail%2C%20faculty%20is%20intimidated%20and%20efforts%20are%20made%20to%20alter%20syllabi%20to%20suit%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20communal%20bias.%20The%20%E2%80%98temple%20of%20learning%20%E2%80%98%20is%20indeed%20becoming%20a%20%E2%80%98home%20for%20narrow%20bigotry.%E2%80%99%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlmost%20all%20the%20institutions%20of%20democracy%20so%20carefully%20nurtured%20by%20Nehru%20are%20under%20threat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20984px)%2061vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2045vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F11%2F12133508%2FPrime_Minister_Jawaharlal_Nehru_addressing_a_public_meeting_in_Kashmir.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22746%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F11%2F12133508%2FPrime_Minister_Jawaharlal_Nehru_addressing_a_public_meeting_in_Kashmir.jpg%20746w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F11%2F12133508%2FPrime_Minister_Jawaharlal_Nehru_addressing_a_public_meeting_in_Kashmir-300x151.jpg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-628240%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22376%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EJawaharlal%20Nehru%20in%20Kashmir%20in%20May%201948.%20Photo%3A%20Photo%20Division%2C%20MIB%2C%20Public%20domain%2C%20via%20Wikimedia%20Commons%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EEconomic%20Development%20with%20Democracy%20and%20Sovereignty%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20maintenance%20of%20sovereignty%20and%20democracy%20with%20civil%20liberties%20were%20two%20non-negotiables%20bequeathed%20to%20independent%20India%20by%20the%20Indian%20national%20movement%2C%20then%20all%20efforts%20at%20post-colonial%20transformation%20in%20India%20had%20to%20occur%20within%20these%20parameters.%20However%2C%20never%20before%20in%20history%20was%20the%20process%20of%20transition%20to%20industrialism%20or%20the%20process%20of%20primitive%20accumulation%20of%20capital%20accomplished%20along%20with%20democracy.%20The%20Nehruvian%20attempt%20at%20industrial%20transformation%20with%20democracy%20was%20thus%20a%20unique%20attempt.%20Nehru%20was%20deeply%20conscious%20of%20this%20and%20often%20spoke%20about%20it%20being%20an%20uncharted%20path%2C%20%E2%80%9Cunique%20in%20history%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20non-negotiable%20commitment%20to%20democracy%20meant%20that%20the%20necessary%20%E2%80%98surplus%E2%80%99%20required%20for%20investment%20in%20order%20to%20facilitate%20the%20transition%20to%20industrialism%20could%20not%20be%20raised%20forcibly%20on%20the%20backs%20of%20the%20Indian%20working%20class%20and%20peasantry%20or%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20colonial%20surplus%20appropriation%20as%20happened%20in%20other%20countries%20in%20the%20past.%20Nehruvian%20state%20intervention%20and%20planning%20was%20to%20be%20consensual%20and%20not%20a%20command%20performance.%20The%20path%20of%20extracting%20surplus%20out%20of%20agriculture%20through%20%E2%80%98expropriatory%E2%80%99%20land%20tax%20or%20forced%20collectivization%3B%20of%20forcing%20surplus%20out%20of%20labour%20though%20slavery%2C%20indentured%20labour%20and%20in%20the%20absence%20of%20organized%20trade%20union%20rights%20or%20of%20forcing%20surplus%20out%20of%20the%20people%20of%20other%20countries%20through%20collection%20of%20tribute%20from%20colonies%2C%20was%20not%20open%20to%20India.%20While%2C%20during%20colonial%20rule%2C%20the%20Indian%20peasant%20often%20ended%20up%20handing%20over%20more%20than%20half%20of%20his%20gross%20produce%20as%20land%20tax%20and%20rent%2C%20after%20independence%20a%20democratic%20regime%20based%20on%20popular%20will%20meant%20that%20not%20only%20was%20there%20no%20tax%2C%20or%20surplus%20extraction%20through%20other%20forms%20from%20agriculture%20(on%20which%20an%20overwhelming%20majority%20of%20the%20Indian%20people%20were%20dependent)%2C%20but%20a%20net%20transfer%20of%20income%20to%20agriculture%20occurred%20through%20state%20subsidies.%20Also%2C%20trade%20union%20rights%20to%20the%20working%20class%20were%20guaranteed%20from%20the%20very%20beginning%20and%20were%20exercised%20vigorously.%20Of%20course%2C%20the%20question%20of%20appropriating%20colonial%20tribute%20from%20other%20countries%20did%20not%20even%20arise.%20In%20fact%2C%20even%20after%20Indian%20independence%2C%20Nehru%20remained%20a%20relentless%20champion%20of%20liberation%20movements%20against%20imperialist%20domination%20in%20other%20parts%20of%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimilarly%2C%20the%20non-negotiable%20commitment%20to%20sovereignty%20meant%20that%20the%20transition%20to%20modernity%20could%20not%20be%20accomplished%20with%20foreign%20aid%2C%20foreign%20capital%20or%20foreign%20intervention%20in%20any%20manner%20that%20would%20make%20India%20a%20junior%20partner%20of%20any%20advanced%20country%2C%20however%20powerful%20it%20may%20be.%20The%20imperative%20of%20maintaining%20sovereignty%20was%20a%20natural%20pointer%20towards%20the%20Nehruvian%20non-alignment%20policy%20in%20the%20post-World%20War%20II%20Cold%20War%20situation%20where%20the%20world%20was%20divided%20into%20two%20power%20blocs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E(a)%20Industrial%20Transformation%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENehru%20and%20the%20early%20Indian%20planners%20had%20correctly%20understood%20that%20political%20independence%20was%20of%20little%20value%20if%20it%20could%20not%20be%20used%20to%20acquire%20first%20economic%20and%20then%20intellectual%20independence.%20In%20a%20special%20letter%20to%20the%20Chief%20Ministers%20in%201949%20he%20warned%20them%2C%20%E2%80%9Cin%20any%20real%20sense%20of%20the%20word%20this%20fight%20for%20freedom%20is%20not%20over%2C%20though%20we%20may%20be%20politically%20free.%20It%20is%20not%20over%20in%20the%20economic%20sense%E2%80%A6%E2%80%9D%20At%20independence%2C%20because%20of%20the%20colonial%20structuring%20of%20the%20Indian%20economy%2C%20India%20was%20almost%20completely%20dependent%20on%20the%20advanced%20world%20for%20capital%20goods%20and%20technology%20for%20making%20any%20investment.%20It%20produced%20virtually%20no%20capital%20goods.%20In%201950%2C%20India%20met%20nearly%2090%20per%20cent%20of%20its%20needs%20of%20machines%20and%20even%20machine%20tools%20through%20imports.%20This%20meant%20that%20despite%20political%20independence%2C%20it%20was%20completely%20dependent%20on%20the%20advanced%20countries%20for%20achieving%20any%20economic%20growth%20though%20investment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20a%20neo-colonial%20type%20situation%2C%20which%20needed%20immediate%20remedy.%20And%20this%20is%20what%20the%20famous%20Nehru-Mahalanobis%20strategy%20tried%20to%20reverse%20by%20adopting%20a%20heavy%20industry%20or%20capital-goods%20industry%20based%20industrialization.%20During%20the%20first%20three%20Five%20Year%20plans%20(1951%E2%80%9365)%2C%20industry%20in%20India%20grew%20at%207.1%20per%20cent%20per%20annum.%20This%20was%20a%20far%20cry%20from%20the%20de-industrialization%20process%20of%20the%2019th%20century%20and%20the%20slow%20industrial%20growth%20between%201914%E2%80%9347.%20More%20important%2C%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20three-fold%20increase%20in%20aggregate%20index%20of%20industrial%20production%20between%201951%20and%201969%20was%20the%20result%20of%20a%2070%20per%20cent%20increase%20in%20consumer%20goods%20industries%2C%20a%20quadrupling%20of%20the%20intermediate%20goods%20production%20and%20a%20ten-fold%20increase%20in%20the%20output%20of%20capital%20goods%E2%80%9D.%20This%20pattern%20of%20industrial%20development%20led%20to%20a%20structural%20transformation%20of%20the%20colonial%20legacy.%20From%20a%20situation%20where%2C%20to%20make%20any%20capital%20investment%20in%20India%2C%20virtually%20the%20entire%20equipment%20(90%20per%20cent)%20had%20to%20be%20imported%2C%20the%20share%20of%20imported%20equipment%20in%20the%20total%20fixed%20investment%20in%20the%20form%20of%20equipment%20had%20come%20down%20to%2043%20per%20cent%20in%201960%20and%20a%20mere%209%20per%20cent%20in%201974%2C%20whereas%20the%20value%20of%20the%20fixed%20investment%20in%20India%20increased%20by%20about%20two%20and%20a%20half%20times%20over%20the%20period%20(1960%E2%80%9374).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20a%20major%20achievement%20towards%20self-reliance%20and%20it%20considerably%20increased%20India%E2%80%99s%20autonomy%20from%20the%20advanced%20countries%20in%20determining%20her%20own%20rate%20of%20capital%20accumulation%20or%20growth.%20It%20thus%20created%20the%20key%20condition%20for%20non-alignment%20or%20relative%20independence%20from%20both%20the%20power%20blocs.%20In%20my%20understanding%20no%20amount%20of%20diplomatic%20finesse%20could%20achieve%20and%20sustain%20the%20objective%20of%20non-alignment%20without%20the%20economic%20basis%20of%20relative%20autonomy%20having%20been%20created.%20It%20was%20this%20un-structuring%20of%20the%20colonial%20structure%20which%20was%20to%20later%20enable%20India%20to%20participate%20in%20the%20globalization%20process%20with%20considerable%20advantage%20to%20itself.%20The%20policy%20of%20non-alignment%20in%20other%20words%20was%20as%20much%20a%20function%20of%20the%20strategy%20of%20economic%20development%20chosen%20by%20India%2C%20as%20it%20was%20a%20product%20of%20the%20Indian%20national%20movement%E2%80%99s%20commitment%20to%20world%20peace%20and%20sovereignty%20of%20nation%20states.%20Conversely%2C%20non-alignment%20became%20a%20viable%20strategy%20only%20as%20India%20began%20to%20gain%20economic%20sovereignty.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20India%20at%20independence%20did%20not%20have%20a%20sufficiently%20large%20indigenous%20private%20sector%20to%20take%20on%20the%20massive%20task%20of%20developing%20capital%20goods%20industries%2C%20the%20only%20other%20option%20was%20to%20develop%20it%20through%20the%20public%20sector.%20The%20option%20of%20basing%20the%20development%20of%20this%20sector%20on%20foreign%20capital%20did%20not%20arise%20as%20the%20Nehruvian%20consensus%20was%20that%20sovereignty%20would%20be%20achieved%20only%20if%20its%20industrial%20development%20was%20primarily%20built%20indigenously%20and%20was%20not%20based%20on%20foreign%20capital.%20The%20public%20sector%20was%20clearly%20seen%2C%20by%20a%20wide%20spectrum%20of%20opinion%2C%20which%20included%20the%20capitalists%20and%20the%20Left%2C%20as%20the%20alternative%20to%20foreign%20capital%20domination.%20The%20public%20sector%20soon%20transformed%20the%20industrial%20and%20infrastructural%20landscape%20in%20India.%20In%20Nehru%E2%80%99s%20time%20four%20major%20steel%20plants%20at%20Rourkela%2C%20Bhilai%2C%20Durgapur%20and%20Bokaro%20came%20up%20in%20the%20public%20sector.%20Large%20number%20of%20capital%20goods%20industries%2C%20infrastructure%20projects%20and%20other%20areas%20requiring%20large%20investments%2C%20which%20the%20Indian%20private%20sector%20could%20not%20have%20developed%20at%20that%20time%2C%20were%20started%20in%20the%20public%20sector.%20To%20list%20just%20a%20few%2C%20Indian%20Telephone%20Industries%2C%20Bhakra%20Dam%2C%20Damodar%20valley%20Corporation%20and%20the%20Hirakud%20Dam%20were%20started%20in%201947%E2%80%931948%20itself%3B%20Hindustan%20Machine%20Tools%20(HMT)%2C%20Bharat%20Heavy%20Electricals%20Limited%2C%20Hindustan%20Shipyard%2C%20Bharat%20Petroleum%2C%20Heavy%20Engineering%20Corporation%2C%20Indian%20Oil%20Corporation%2C%20Hindustan%20Antibiotics%2C%20Hindustan%20Insecticides%2C%20Nagarjuna%20Sagar%20Dam%2C%20National%20Mineral%20Development%20Corporation%20were%20started%20in%20the%201950s%20and%20National%20Building%20and%20Construction%20Corporation%2C%20Indian%20Drugs%20and%20Pharmaceuticals%20Limited%2C%20Fertiliser%20Corporation%20of%20India%2C%20Shipping%20Corporation%20of%20India%2C%20Hindustan%20Aeronautics%20Limited%2C%20Bharat%20Earth%20Movers%20were%20started%20in%20the%20early%201960s.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20important%20to%20point%20out%20that%20these%20public%20sector%20undertakings%20were%20not%20loss%20making%20%E2%80%98white%20elephants%E2%80%99%20acting%20as%20a%20drag%20on%20national%20resources%20in%20Nehru%E2%80%99s%20time%2C%20which%20some%20of%20them%20did%20become%20in%20later%20decades.%20On%20the%20contrary%20they%20contributed%20to%20resource%20mobilisation%20in%20India%20apart%20from%20creating%20a%20self-reliance%20in%20critical%20areas.%20The%20Public%20Sector%20savings%20were%20throughout%20the%20Nehruvian%20period%201950%E2%80%9351%20to%201964%E2%80%9365%20considerably%20higher%20than%20the%20private%20corporate%20sector.129%20Nehru%20could%20proudly%20announce%20while%20inaugurating%20the%20second%20HMT%20factory%20in%201961%20that%20%E2%80%9Cthis%20factory%20has%20been%20made%20out%20of%20the%20profits%20or%20the%20surplus%20of%20the%20older%20Hindustan%20Machine%20Tools%20factory%E2%80%9D.%20Today%E2%80%99s%20neo-liberals%20who%20push%20for%20indiscriminate%20privatisation%20totally%20ignore%20this%20aspect.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20reducing%20dependence%20on%20foreign%20capital%20and%20technology%20for%20making%20indigenous%20investment%20was%20one%20way%20of%20gaining%20and%20keeping%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20sovereignty%20intact%2C%20other%20strategies%20were%20adopted%20as%20well.%20India%20undertook%20a%20deliberate%20strategy%20of%20diversifying%20its%20foreign%20trade%20so%20that%20her%20dependence%20on%20any%20one%20country%20or%20bloc%20of%20countries%20was%20reduced.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20the%20geographical%20concentration%20index%20(GCI)%20of%20trade%20with%20foreign%20countries%20declined%20sharply.%20GCI%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20exports%20declined%20from%200.69%20in%201947%20to%200.22%20in%201975.%20There%20was%20a%20similar%20decline%20in%20GCI%20in%20the%20case%20of%20imports.%20Significantly%2C%20the%20result%20of%20the%20declining%20GCI%20was%20that%20the%20share%20of%20the%20metropolitan%20countries%20of%20the%20West%2C%20which%20earlier%20dominated%20India%E2%80%99s%20trade%2C%20declined%20sharply.%20For%20example%2C%20the%20share%20of%20UK%20and%20USA%20in%20India%E2%80%99s%20exports%2C%20which%20was%2045%20per%20cent%20in%201947%2C%20fell%20by%20more%20than%20half%20and%20by%201977%20it%20was%20only%2020%20per%20cent.%20This%20was%20partly%20achieved%20by%20the%20increase%20in%20India%E2%80%99s%20trade%20with%20the%20Socialist%20bloc%20(which%20bailed%20out%20India%20at%20a%20time%20when%20she%20was%20extremely%20short%20of%20foreign%20exchange%20by%20allowing%20barter%20and%20Rupee%20trade)%20and%20other%20underdeveloped%20countries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20recent%20years%2C%20however%2C%20there%20has%20been%20a%20growing%20tendency%2C%20particularly%20among%20neo-colonial%20scholars%20like%20Tirthankar%20Roy%20and%20Meghnad%20Desai%2C%20to%20dismiss%20or%20run%20down%20the%20economic%20achievements%20of%20the%20Nehruvian%20era.%20Looking%20back%20from%20the%20vantage%20point%20of%20the%20high%20growth%20rates%20since%20the%20economic%20reforms%20of%201991%2C%20the%20Nehru%20years%20are%20described%20as%20the%20wasted%20opportunity.%20The%20strategy%20of%20trying%20to%20reverse%20the%20colonial%20structuring%20of%20the%20Indian%20economy%20through%20a%20mixed%20economy%20with%20a%20substantial%20public%20sector%20and%20an%20inward%20oriented%2C%20import%20substituting%20self%20reliant%20growth%2C%20which%20involved%20protecting%20the%20fledgling%20domestic%20industry%2C%20was%20seen%20as%20the%20main%20problem.%20As%20Meghnad%20Desai%20put%20it%2C%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20first%2040%20years%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20independence%20were%20wasted%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20assessment%20is%20completely%20a-historical.%20It%20is%20oblivious%20of%20the%20massive%20increase%20in%20all%20indicators%20of%20growth%2C%20per%20capita%20GDP%2C%20industry%2C%20agriculture%2C%20savings%2C%20investment%20or%20domestic%20capital%20formation%20that%20occurred%20in%20the%20Nehruvian%20period%20as%20compared%20the%20to%20the%20colonial%20times.%20Also%20it%20ignores%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20growth%20parameters%20in%20Nehru%E2%80%99s%20time%20compared%20extremely%20favourably%20when%20compared%20to%20other%20countries%20of%20the%20world%20at%20the%20same%20stage%20of%20development%20including%20UK%2C%20USA%2C%20France%2C%20China%20and%20Japan.%20Further%2C%20this%20assessment%20ignores%20the%20global%20structural%20context.%20If%20the%20post%201991%20strategy%20was%20adopted%20in%20the%201950s%2C%20India%20would%20surely%20have%20headed%20towards%20becoming%20a%20%E2%80%98banana%20republic%E2%80%99.%20Conversely%2C%20it%20would%20not%20make%20any%20sense%20to%20have%20the%201950s%20economic%20strategy%20in%20the%201990s%20when%20the%20nature%20of%20the%20global%20economy%2C%20including%20the%20Indian%20economy%2C%20had%20undergone%20fundamental%20changes.%20The%20Nehruvian%20era%20created%20the%20conditions%20for%20the%20future%20opening%20up%20and%20growth%20by%20%E2%80%98un%20structuring%E2%80%99%20many%20aspects%20of%20the%20inherited%20colonial%20structure.%20Other%20post%20colonial%20countries%20too%20required%20this%20period%20of%2030%20to%2040%20years%20of%20un%20structuring%20before%20opening%20up.%20China%20needed%20the%20Maoist%20phase%20before%20Deng%E2%80%99s%20opening%20up%20in%20the%20late%201970s%20was%20possible.%20Today%E2%80%99s%20India%20is%20possible%20because%20of%20the%20base%20laid%20in%20the%20early%20decades%20after%20independence%20and%20has%20not%20emerged%20despite%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E(b)%20Agricultural%20Transformation%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20canard%20spread%20about%20Nehru%20is%20his%20supposed%20neglect%20of%20agriculture%20while%20focusing%20on%20industrial%20development.%20Nehru%20was%20acutely%20aware%20of%20the%20complementarity%20of%20agricultural%20and%20industrial%20growth.%20Also%2C%20India%E2%80%99s%20food%20security%20was%20an%20area%20of%20great%20concern%20because%20the%20maintenance%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20sovereignty%20and%20ability%20to%20stay%20non-aligned%20and%20the%20welfare%20of%20the%20vast%20masses%20of%20India%20was%20involved.%20Indian%20agriculture%20had%20stagnated%20and%20even%20declined%20under%20colonial%20rule%20and%20at%20independence%20India%20was%20faced%20with%20acute%20food%20shortage%20and%20famine%20conditions%20in%20many%20areas.%2014%20million%20tonnes%20of%20food%20had%20to%20be%20imported%20between%201946%20and%201953.%20There%20could%20be%20no%20sovereignty%20if%20India%20was%20dependent%20on%20food%20aid%20for%20its%20very%20survival.%20Indian%20agriculture%20needed%20to%20be%20revolutionized%20and%20Nehru%20took%20up%20the%20task%20on%20a%20war%20footing.%20As%20Nehru%20clearly%20stated%20in%20parliament%20on%2015%20December%201952%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20certainly%20attach%20importance%20to%20industry%2C%20but%20in%20the%20present%20context%20we%20attach%20far%20greater%20importance%20to%20agriculture%20and%20food%20and%20matters%20pertaining%20to%20agriculture.%20If%20our%20agricultural%20foundation%20is%20not%20strong%20then%20the%20industry%20we%20seek%20to%20build%20will%20not%20have%20a%20strong%20basis%20either.%20Apart%20from%20that%2C%20the%20situation%20in%20the%20country%20today%20is%20such%20that%20if%20our%20food%20front%20cracks%20up%2C%20everything%20else%20will%20crack%20up%20too.%20Therefore%20we%20dare%20not%20weaken%20our%20food%20front.%20If%20our%20agriculture%20becomes%20strongly%20entrenched%2C%20as%20we%20hope%20it%20will%2C%20then%20it%20will%20be%20relatively%20easy%20for%20us%20to%20progress%20more%20rapidly%20on%20the%20industrial%20front%2C%20whereas%20if%20we%20concentrate%20only%20on%20industrial%20development%20and%20leave%20agriculture%20in%20a%20weak%20condition%20we%20shall%20ultimately%20be%20weakening%20industry.%20That%20is%20why%20primary%20attention%20has%20been%20given%20to%20agriculture%20and%20food%20and%20that%2C%20I%20think%2C%20is%20essential%20in%20country%20like%20India%20at%20the%20present%20moment%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENehru%20pushed%20through%20the%20extremely%20difficult%20task%20of%20land%20reforms%20in%20India%20within%20a%20democratic%20framework%2C%20basing%20himself%20on%20the%20long%20and%20powerful%20heritage%20of%20the%20national%20and%20peasant%20movements.%20A%20remarkable%20achievement%20in%20contrast%20to%20the%20forced%20land%20reforms%20achieved%20in%20Soviet%20Union%20or%20China%20costing%20millions%20of%20lives%20or%20the%20land%20reforms%20of%20Japan%20under%20an%20army%20of%20occupation.%20By%201957%20the%20back%20of%20the%20over%20150%20years%20old%20Zamindari%20system%20was%20broken.%20Cooperative%20and%20institutional%20credit%20considerably%20weakened%20the%20stranglehold%20of%20the%20moneylender.%20Loans%20advanced%20by%20such%20institutions%20increased%20by%20more%20than%20fifteen%20times%2C%20rising%20from%20Rs.%200.23%20billion%20in%201950%E2%80%9351%20to%20Rs.3.65%20billion%20in%201965%E2%80%9366.%20Such%20institutional%20reforms%20were%20combined%20with%20major%20investments%20in%20scientific%20agricultural%20research%2C%20irrigation%20and%20electric%20power%20projects.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENehru%20made%20no%20false%20dichotomy%20between%20agriculture%20and%20industry.%20Keenly%20aware%20that%20an%20agrarian%20transformation%20was%20not%20possible%20without%20an%20industrial%20and%20infrastructural%20transformation%2C%20i.e.%2C%20without%20electricity%2C%20tractors%2C%20pumps%2C%20chemical%20fertilizers%2C%20etc.%2C%20he%20pushed%20for%20industrial%20transformation%20simultaneously%20with%20the%20agricultural%20reforms.%20Electricity%20generation%2C%20for%20example%2C%20increased%20by%20over%201300%20per%20cent%20under%20his%20guidance%20between%201950%20and%201965.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20combination%20of%20institutional%20changes%20(land%20reforms)%20and%20massive%20state%20sponsored%20technological%20change%20transformed%20Indian%20agriculture%20rapidly.%20During%20the%20first%20three%20plans%20(leaving%20out%201965%E2%80%9366%2C%20a%20drought%20year)%2C%20Indian%20agriculture%20grew%20at%20an%20annual%20rate%20of%20over%203%20per%20cent%2C%20a%20growth%20rate%20more%20than%20eight%20times%20the%20annual%20growth%20rate%20of%200.37%20per%20cent%20achieved%20during%20the%20half%20century%20(1891%E2%80%931946)%20of%20the%20last%20phase%20of%20colonialism%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAttempts%20are%20sometimes%20made%20to%20contrast%20Nehru%20with%20his%20successor%20Lal%20Bahadur%20Shastri%2C%20the%20latter%20in%20his%20all%20too%20brief%20tenure%20being%20credited%20with%20the%20ushering%20in%20of%20the%20Green%20Revolution%20strategy.%20The%20reality%20is%20somewhat%20different.%20It%20is%20clear%20that%20by%20the%20late%20fifties%20and%20early%20sixties%2C%20as%20the%20benefits%20from%20the%20land%20reforms%20that%20could%20be%20carried%20out%20in%20Indian%20conditions%20had%20begun%20to%20peak%20and%20the%20possibilities%20of%20agricultural%20growth%20based%20on%20extension%20of%20agriculture%2C%20i.e.%2C%20bringing%20more%20area%20into%20cultivation%2C%20were%20also%20reaching%20their%20limit%2C%20Nehru%E2%80%99s%20focus%20inevitably%20shifted%20further%20towards%20technological%20solutions.%20Even%20the%20New%20Agricultural%20Strategy%2C%20associated%20with%20the%20Green%20Revolution%2C%20of%20picking%20out%20select%20areas%20with%20certain%20natural%20advantages%20for%20intensive%20development%20with%20a%20package%20programme%20(the%20IADP%20or%20the%20Intensive%20Agricultural%20Districts%20Programme)%20was%20launched%20in%2015%20districts%2C%20one%20for%20each%20state%2C%20on%20an%20experimental%20basis%20during%20the%20Third%20Plan%20in%20Nehru%E2%80%99s%20lifetime%E2%80%94a%20practice%20which%20was%20to%20be%20generalised%20on%20a%20large%20scale%20a%20few%20years%20later.%20As%20one%20of%20the%20major%20scholars%20of%20the%20Green%20Revolution%2C%20G.S.%20Bhalla%2C%20put%20it%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20qualitative%20technological%20transformation%20in%20India%E2%80%94the%20Green%20Revolution%20%E2%80%A6came%20about%20not%20during%20his%20lifetime%20but%20soon%20after%20his%20death.%20But%20the%20foundations%20for%20the%20technological%20development%20were%20laid%20during%20Nehru%E2%80%99s%20time%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENehru%20thus%20not%20only%20brought%20about%20major%20institutional%20reforms%20(land%20reforms)%20in%20Indian%20agriculture%20he%20also%20laid%20the%20foundations%20for%20the%20technological%20reforms%2C%20the%20basis%20of%20the%20%E2%80%98Green%20Revolution%E2%80%99%2C%20which%20made%20India%20food%20surplus%20in%20a%20remarkably%20short%20period.%20No%20wonder%2C%20Daniel%20Thorner%2C%20one%20of%20the%20keenest%20observers%20of%20Indian%20agriculture%20since%20independence%2C%20noted%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20sometimes%20said%20that%20the%20(initial)%20five-year%20plans%20neglected%20agriculture.%20This%20charge%20cannot%20be%20taken%20seriously.%20The%20facts%20are%20that%20in%20India%E2%80%99s%20first%20twenty%20one%20years%20of%20independence%20more%20has%20been%20done%20to%20foster%20change%20in%20agriculture%20and%20more%20change%20has%20actually%20taken%20place%20than%20in%20the%20preceding%20two%20hundred%20years%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E(c)%20Anticipating%20the%20Knowledge%20Revolution%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJawaharlal%20Nehru%20saw%20focus%20on%20scientific%20education%20at%20the%20highest%20level%20as%20a%20necessary%20part%20of%20achieving%20and%20maintaining%20sovereignty%20by%20reducing%20dependence%20on%20the%20advanced%20world.%20He%20was%20acutely%20aware%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20backwardness%20in%20science%20and%20technology%2C%20an%20area%20deliberately%20left%20barren%20in%20the%20colonial%20period%2C%20and%20therefore%20made%20massive%20efforts%20to%20overcome%20this%20shortcoming.%20An%20unprecedented%20increase%20occurred%20in%20the%20educational%20opportunities%20in%20science%20and%20technology%20in%20the%20universities%20and%20institutes%20set%20up%20in%20the%20early%20years%20after%20independence.%20Almost%20all%20the%20major%20institutions%20in%20this%20area%20from%20the%20Indian%20Institute%20of%20Technology%20(IIT)%2C%20Indian%20Institute%20of%20Management%20(IIM)%2C%20the%20Council%20of%20Scientific%20and%20Industrial%20Research%20(CSIR)%2C%20the%20Atomic%20Energy%20Commission%2C%20the%20Bhabha%20Atomic%20Research%20Centre%2C%20(with%20the%20first%20atomic%20reactor%20going%20critical%20in%201956%20and%20the%20first%20rocket%20tested%20from%20Thumba%20in%201963!)%2C%20the%20Indian%20National%20Committee%20for%20Space%20Research%20(the%20predecessor%20of%20Indian%20Space%20Research%20Organisation%2C%20ISRO)%2C%20the%20National%20Physical%20Laboratory%2C%20the%20National%20Chemical%20Laboratory%2C%20National%20Metallurgical%20Laboratory%2C%20the%20All%20India%20Institute%20of%20Medical%20Sciences%20(AIIMS)%2C%20The%20National%20Institute%20of%20Virology%2C%20The%20Defence%20Research%20and%20Development%20Organisation%20(DRDO)%20and%20numerous%20other%20such%20institutions%20were%20all%20set%20up%20in%20the%20Nehruvian%20era.%20(One%20must%20mention%20here%20that%20for%20Nehru%20cultivating%20%E2%80%98knowledge%E2%80%99%20was%20not%20to%20be%20limited%20to%20the%20scientific%20area.%20In%20the%201950s%2C%20under%20his%20initiative%2C%20the%20Sahitya%20Academy%2C%20Sangeet%20Natak%20Academy%2C%20National%20School%20of%20Drama%2C%20Lalit%20Kala%20Academy%20and%20the%20National%20Council%20for%20Applied%20Economic%20Research%2C%20NCAER%20%2C%20the%20Indian%20Statistical%20Institute%2C%20were%20set%20up%20as%20was%20the%20Film%20and%20Television%20Institute%20of%20India%2C%20FTII%2C%20in%201960%2C%20The%20National%20Institute%20of%20Design%20and%20the%20National%20Council%20of%20Educational%20Research%20and%20Training%2C%20NCERT%2C%20in%201961).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENational%20expenditure%20on%20scientific%20research%20and%20development%20kept%20growing%20rapidly%20with%20each%20plan.%20For%20example%2C%20it%20increased%20from%20Rs.%2010%20million%20in%201949%20to%20Rs.%204.5%20billion%20in%201977.%20Over%20roughly%20the%20same%20period%2C%20the%20stock%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20scientific%20and%20technical%20manpower%20increased%20more%20than%2012%20times%20from%20190%20thousand%20to%202.32%20million.%20A%20spectacular%20growth%20by%20any%20standards%2C%20a%20growth%20whose%20benefits%20India%20reaps%20today%20as%20the%20world%20moved%20towards%20a%20%E2%80%98knowledge%E2%80%99%20society%2C%20a%20move%20which%20Nehru%20anticipated.143%20It%20is%20because%20Nehru%20anticipated%20the%20knowledge%20revolution%20that%20India%20today%20is%20able%20to%20participate%20in%20this%20global%20phenomenon%20and%20nearly%20half%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20GDP%20is%20generated%20from%20the%20service%20sector%20a%20significant%20part%20of%20which%20is%20based%20on%20the%20knowledge%20revolution.%20It%20is%20not%20despite%20Nehru%20but%20because%20of%20his%20farsightedness%20that%20India%20has%20reached%20where%20it%20has.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20may%20add%20that%20the%20focus%20on%20scientific%20education%20at%20the%20higher%20level%20was%20not%20counterpoised%20to%20primary%20education%20as%20is%20often%20alleged.%20Nehru%E2%80%99s%20commitment%20to%20primary%20education%20from%20the%20days%20of%20the%201931%20Karachi%20Resolution%20drafted%20by%20him%2C%20which%20committed%20the%20state%20to%20providing%20free%20and%20compulsory%20basic%20education%2C%20remained%20steadfast.%20The%20Government%20system%20of%20primary%20school%20education%20during%20the%20Nehruvian%20era%2C%20insufficient%20though%20it%20was%2C%20is%20in%20stark%20contrast%20to%20the%20near%20destruction%20of%20that%20system%20in%20today%E2%80%99s%20India%20where%20even%20the%20poor%20are%20increasingly%20forced%20to%20access%20whatever%20little%20education%20they%20are%20able%20to%20from%20the%20rapacious%20private%20sector.%20Enrolment%20in%20schools%20increased%20from%2023.5%20million%20in%201950%E2%80%9351%20to%2067.7%20million%20in%201965%E2%80%9366%2C%20a%20significant%20increase%20of%20188.1%20per%20cent.%20(While%20the%20increase%20in%20admissions%20at%20the%20degree%20level%20for%20engineering%20and%20technology%20increased%20by%20502.4%20per%20cent%20in%20the%20same%20period%2C%20the%20huge%20difference%20is%20explained%20partly%20by%20the%20fact%20of%20the%20low%20base%20from%20which%20it%20started%20in%201950%E2%80%9351%2C%20only%204.1%20thousand%20admissions%2C%20increasing%20to%2024.7%20thousand%20in%201965%E2%80%9366%2C%20and%20partly%20because%20the%20need%20to%20catch%20up%20in%20this%20area%20was%20critical%20in%20maintaining%20a%20sovereign%2C%20independent%20path%20of%20economic%20development.)%20Rather%20than%20building%20on%20the%20public%20education%20system%20painstakingly%20built%20up%20in%20the%20Nehruvian%20era%20at%20the%20school%20level%2C%20as%20well%20as%2C%20at%20the%20highest%20level%2C%20it%20is%20either%20being%20allowed%20to%20die%2C%20or%20active%20efforts%20are%20made%20to%20dismantle%20it.%20The%20National%20Education%20Policy%20of%202020%20now%20being%20pushed%20is%20a%20good%20example%20of%20this%20dismantling%2C%20with%20the%20state%20increasingly%20withdrawing%20its%20role%20in%20education%20and%20handing%20over%20this%20sector%20to%20the%20private%20sector%20and%20even%20more%20ominously%20to%20foreign%20universities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKeeping%20Focus%20on%20the%20Poor%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENehru%E2%80%99s%20success%20in%20keeping%20India%20on%20the%20democratic%2C%20civil%20libertarian%20path%20against%20considerable%20odds%20(while%20most%20other%20post-colonial%20countries%20faltered%20on%20this%20count)%2C%20by%20itself%20ensured%20that%20the%20poor%20were%20not%20altogether%20left%20out%20of%20the%20development%20process%20or%20that%20their%20condition%20was%20not%20totally%20ignored.%20It%20is%20now%20well%20recognized%20that%20democracy%20is%20critical%20for%20the%20survival%20of%20the%20poor.%20It%20is%20democracy%20in%20India%20which%20has%20ensured%20that%20an%20inflationary%20path%20to%20growth%2C%20which%20hits%20the%20poor%20hardest%2C%20was%20never%20adopted.%20The%20trend%20rate%20of%20inflation%20in%20India%20since%20independence%20had%20not%20touched%20two%20digits%20for%20several%20decades.%20Till%201963%20it%20did%20not%20exceed%202%20per%20cent%20per%20annum.%20No%20government%20in%20India%20irrespective%20of%20their%20political%20ideology%20has%20been%20able%20to%20ignore%20the%20political%20implications%20of%20uncontrolled%20inflation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlso%2C%20it%20is%20democracy%20and%20civil%20liberties%20that%20ensured%20that%20no%20large%20scale%20famine%20deaths%20could%20occur%20in%20India%20since%20independence%2C%20despite%20some%20extreme%20conditions%20created%20by%20climatic%20shocks%2C%20while%20more%20than%2040%20million%20died%20in%20famines%20in%20China%20in%20the%20late%201950s%20and%2060s%2C%20which%20the%20world%20got%20to%20know%20decades%20later%20because%20of%20the%20absence%20of%20a%20free%20media.%20Amartya%20Sen%20has%20repeatedly%20emphasized%20the%20role%20of%20civil%20liberties%20and%20a%20free%20press%20in%20preventing%20such%20mass%20man-made%20disasters.%20With%20more%20than%2070%2C000%20newspapers%20and%20about%20700%20satellite%20channels%20and%20with%20nearly%2030%20newspapers%20having%20a%20daily%20readership%20of%20more%20than%20a%20million%20it%20is%20not%20easy%20to%20keep%20famine%20conditions%20under%20cover%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20political%20democracy%20was%20understood%20by%20Nehru%20to%20be%20a%20necessary%20condition%20for%20people%E2%80%99s%20empowerment%2C%20it%20was%20by%20no%20means%20taken%20to%20be%20sufficient.%20As%20he%20put%20it%20in%201952%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20poverty%20and%20low%20standards%20continue%20then%20democracy%2C%20for%20all%20its%20fine%20institutions%20and%20ideals%2C%20ceases%20to%20be%20a%20liberating%20force.%20It%20must%20therefore%20aim%20continuously%20at%20the%20eradication%20of%20poverty%E2%80%A6.%20In%20other%20words%2C%20political%20democracy%20is%20not%20enough.%20It%20must%20develop%20into%20economic%20democracy%20also.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENehru%20was%20deeply%20aware%20that%20active%20efforts%20had%20to%20be%20made%20and%20institutional%20structures%20created%20which%20would%20enable%20the%20mass%20of%20the%20people%20to%20achieve%20a%20life%20of%20dignity.%20He%20set%20up%20the%20massive%20Community%20Development%20Programme%20in%201952%20aimed%20at%20ameliorating%20all%20aspects%20of%20people%E2%80%99s%20lives%20in%20the%20remote%20villages%2C%20from%20improvement%20in%20agricultural%20methods%20to%20communications%2C%20education%20and%20health.%20His%20basic%20objective%20through%20this%20programme%20was%20%E2%80%9Cto%20unleash%20forces%20from%20below%20among%20our%20people%E2%80%9D%20by%20creating%20conditions%20in%20which%20spontaneous%20growth%20from%20below%20was%20possible.%20The%20ultimate%20aim%20was%20%E2%80%9Cprogressively%20producing%20a%20measure%20of%20equality%20in%20opportunity%20and%20other%20things%E2%80%9D.%20A%20veritable%20army%20of%20Village%20Level%20Workers%20(Gram%20Sewaks)%20and%20Block%20Development%20Officers%20was%20spread%20out%20in%20the%20countryside%20to%20achieve%20this%20task.%20As%20a%20tendency%20towards%20bureaucratization%20began%20to%20emerge%20in%20this%20programme%2C%20Nehru%20tried%20to%20integrate%20it%20with%20the%20Panchayati%20Raj%20institutions%20(elected%20local%20self-governing%20bodies)%20and%20set%20up%20a%20large%20programme%20of%20cooperatives%20in%20banking%2C%20marketing%20and%20other%20services%20benefiting%20and%20empowering%20millions%20of%20peasants.%20Emphasizing%20the%20critical%20role%20of%20local%20village%20level%20self-governing%20cooperative%20institutions%2C%20Nehru%20said%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20feel%20more%20and%20more%20that%20we%20must%20function%20more%20from%20below%20than%20from%20the%20top.%20The%20top%20is%20important%20of%20course%20and%20in%20the%20modern%20world%20a%20large%20measure%20of%20centralisation%20is%20inevitable.%20Yet%20too%20much%20centralization%20means%20decay%20at%20the%20roots%20and%20ultimately%20a%20withering%20of%20the%20branches%20and%20leaves%20and%20flowers.%20Therefore%20we%20have%20to%20encourage%20these%20basic%20organs%20in%20the%20village%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20struggle%20to%20make%20these%20local%20institutions%20function%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20most%20deprived%20was%20not%20an%20easy%20one%20in%20a%20society%20greatly%20divided%20by%20class%2C%20caste%20and%20gender.%20In%20fact%2C%20decades%20after%20Nehru%20passed%20away%2C%20Rajiv%20Gandhi%20took%20the%20initiative%20to%20re-invigorate%20Panchayati%20Raj%20by%20proposing%20that%20elections%20to%20these%20bodies%20be%20made%20mandatory%20and%20that%20the%20deprived%20castes%2C%20tribes%20and%20women%20be%20given%20adequate%20representation%20in%20them%2C%20which%20resulted%20in%20the%2073rd%20and%2074th%20amendments%20in%20the%20Indian%20Constitution%20in%201993.%20The%20process%20of%20trying%20to%20empower%20the%20poor%20and%20disadvantaged%20is%20still%20carrying%20on%20as%20it%20must%20in%20the%20future%2C%20but%20the%20foundation%20was%20laid%20by%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENehru%20was%20deeply%20influenced%20by%20Marxism%20since%20the%20late%201920s.%20His%20contribution%20in%20embedding%20and%20then%20making%20widely%20acceptable%20the%20socialist%20ideal%20of%20empowering%20the%20poor%20among%20the%20Indian%20people%20was%20immense.%20The%20fact%20that%20not%20only%20the%20Communists%20and%20Socialists%20but%20an%20overwhelming%20majority%20of%20nationalist%20opinion%20in%20India%20since%20the%20late%201930s%20accepted%20socialism%20as%20an%20objective%20was%20to%20a%20great%20extent%20because%20of%20Nehru.%20So%20deeply%20did%20this%20idea%20get%20rooted%20among%20the%20Indian%20people%20as%20a%20whole%20that%20as%20late%20as%201980%20when%20the%20decidedly%20right-wing%20Jan%20Sangh%2C%20which%20had%20nothing%20to%20do%20with%20socialism%20or%20the%20national%20movement%2C%20and%20whose%20predecessors%2C%20the%20Hindu%20Mahasabha%2C%20and%20heroes%2C%20like%20Savarkar%2C%20were%20accused%20of%20the%20assassination%20of%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%2C%20was%20reborn%20in%20its%20new%20avatar%20as%20the%20Bhartiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%2C%20it%20chose%20to%20declare%20its%20creed%20as%20%E2%80%98Gandhian%20Socialism%E2%80%99!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F03%2F04123429%2FNehru.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F03%2F04123429%2FNehru.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F03%2F04123429%2FNehru-300x169.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F03%2F04123429%2FNehru-1024x576.jpeg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-584956%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22675%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EIndia%E2%80%99s%20first%20Prime%20Minister%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%20and%20the%20Planning%20Commission%20in%201950.%20Photo%3A%20Twitter%2F%40INCIndia%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENehru%20was%20able%20to%20give%20the%20socialist%20ideal%20such%20wide%20acceptability%20in%20India%20partly%20because%20he%20made%20a%20very%20early%20break%20from%20a%20narrow%2C%20sectarian%20and%20rigid%20interpretation%20of%20Marxism%20which%20India%E2%80%99s%20leading%20historian%20of%20the%20modern%20and%20contemporary%20period%2C%20Bipan%20Chandra%2C%20called%20%E2%80%9CStalin%20Marxism%E2%80%9D.%20Nehru%20was%20among%20the%20first%20in%20the%20world%20to%20make%20this%20break%20from%20Stalin-Marxism.%20Roughly%20at%20the%20same%20time%20as%20the%20famous%20Italian%20Marxist%20Antonio%20Gramsci%2C%20(with%20whom%20comparisons%20have%20already%20been%20made%20in%20the%20beginning%20of%20the%20address)%2C%20Nehru%2C%20in%20the%20late%201930s%2C%20was%20groping%20for%20a%20strategy%20of%20social%20transformation%20in%20a%20democratic%20or%20semi%20democratic%20framework%2C%20which%20was%20different%20from%20the%20insurrectionary%20and%20violent%20Bolshevik%20model%20that%20was%20not%20suitable%20for%20such%20situations.%20Nehru%20was%20fortunate%20in%20being%20witness%20to%20and%20part%20of%20the%20Gandhian%20struggle%20for%20freedom%20which%20was%20till%20then%20and%20perhaps%20remains%20till%20today%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20only%20actual%20historical%20example%20of%20a%20semi-democratic%20or%20democratic-type%20state%20structure%20being%20replaced%20or%20transformed%2C%20of%20the%20broadly%20Gramscian%20theoretical%20perspective%20of%20a%20war%20of%20position%20being%20successfully%20practiced%E2%80%9D.%20The%20fact%20that%20Gramsci%20saw%20this%20%E2%80%9Cas%20the%20only%20possible%20strategy%E2%80%9D%20for%20social%20transformation%20%E2%80%9Cin%20the%20developed%20countries%20of%20the%20west%E2%80%9D%20underlines%20the%20huge%20significance%20of%20the%20Gandhian%20movement%20to%20the%20world%20as%20a%20whole.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELearning%20from%20the%20practice%20of%20the%20Gandhian%20movement%20made%20it%20easier%20for%20Nehru%20to%20break%20from%20the%20Stalin-Marxist%20paradigm%20and%20argue%20somewhat%20precociously%20that%2C%20while%20there%20could%20be%20no%20true%20democracy%20without%20socialism%2C%20there%20could%20be%20no%20socialism%20without%20democracy.%20He%20insisted%20that%20civil%20liberty%20and%20democracy%20had%20to%20be%20basic%20parts%20of%20socialism.%20The%20socialist%20transformation%20required%20societal%20consensus%2C%20the%20consent%20of%20the%20overwhelming%20majority%20of%20the%20people.%20It%20could%20not%20be%20a%20minority%20revolution%20led%20by%20a%20band%20of%20highly%20committed%20revolutionaries%2C%20a%20%E2%80%98dictatorship%20of%20the%20proletariat%E2%80%99.%20It%20was%20also%20not%20enough%20just%20to%20have%20a%20majority.%20To%20succeed%2C%20it%20had%20to%20be%20a%20socialism%20acceptable%20by%20all%20sections%2C%20by%20an%20overwhelming%20majority.%20Nehru%20was%20anticipating%20what%20later%20events%20were%20to%20validate%20and%20what%20was%20to%20be%20slowly%20accepted%20globally%20by%20increasing%20sections%20of%20the%20left.%20He%20made%20this%20shift%20long%20before%20this%20change%20was%20acceptable%20to%20any%20significant%20trend%20in%20the%20communist%20movement%20in%20India%20and%20the%20world.%20The%20emergence%20of%20Euro-communism%2C%20which%20made%20similar%20assumptions%2C%20occurred%20only%20in%20the%201970s%2C%20and%2080s.%20Nehru%E2%80%99s%20shift%20was%2C%20therefore%2C%20for%20very%20long%20analysed%20by%20the%20orthodox%20Left%20as%20the%20%E2%80%98diluting%E2%80%99%20of%20his%20commitment%20to%20socialism%20for%20various%20reasons%20such%20as%20pragmatic%20pressures%2C%20the%20influence%20of%20Gandhiji%20or%20even%20his%20alleged%20desire%20to%20be%20in%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20the%20late%201930s%2C%20Nehru%20began%20to%20veer%20towards%20the%20position%20that%20Socialism%20could%20not%20be%20brought%20about%20by%20coercion%20or%20force.%20How%20can%20you%20arrive%20at%20a%20consensus%20by%20force%3F%20He%20argued%20that%20to%20achieve%20the%20desirable%20end%20of%20socialist%20transformation%20one%20should%20not%20adopt%20the%20means%20of%20hatred%20and%20violence%2C%20and%20that%20a%20socialistic%20pattern%20of%20society%20could%20be%20achieved%20through%20non-violent%20and%20peaceful%20means.%20Fully%20in%20tune%20with%20the%20Gandhian%20notion%20that%20wrong%20means%20could%20not%20achieve%20right%20ends%2C%20he%20declared%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20always%20a%20close%20and%20intimate%20relationship%20between%20the%20end%20we%20aim%20at%20and%20the%20means%20adopted%20to%20attain%20it.%20Even%20if%20the%20end%20is%20right%20and%20the%20means%20are%20wrong%2C%20it%20will%20vitiate%20the%20end%20or%20divert%20us%20in%20a%20wrong%20direction%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlso%2C%20arriving%20at%20a%20socialist%20consensus%20would%20mean%20that%20one%20would%20have%20to%20view%20it%20as%20a%20process%20and%20not%20an%20event%20arrived%20at%20in%20a%20%E2%80%98revolutionary%20moment.%E2%80%99%20This%20would%20have%20to%20be%20a%20long%20drawn%20out%20process%20with%20its%20ups%20and%20downs%2C%20a%20process%20which%20may%20have%20to%20at%20times%20slow%20down%2C%20moderate%20or%20tone%20down%20its%20immediate%20goals%2C%20in%20order%20to%20carry%20the%20bulk%20of%20the%20people%20along%2C%20including%20those%20who%20held%20opposing%20positions.%20Nehru%20writing%20from%20prison%20in%20the%201940s%20describing%20his%20understanding%20of%20how%20the%20National%20Planning%20Committee%20(NPC)%2C%20set%20up%20by%20the%20Congress%20in%201938%2C%20should%20move%20in%20a%20socialist%20direction%2C%20argued%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9C%E2%80%A6this%20was%20to%20be%20attempted%20in%20the%20context%20of%20democratic%20freedom%20and%20with%20a%20large%20measure%20of%20cooperation%20of%20some%20at%20least%20of%20the%20groups%20who%20were%20normally%20opposed%20to%20the%20socialist%20doctrine.%20That%20cooperation%20seemed%20to%20me%20worthwhile%20even%20if%20it%20involved%20toning%20down%20or%20weakening%20of%20the%20plan%20in%20some%20respects%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENehru%20was%20to%20retain%20throughout%20his%20life%20this%20nuanced%20persuasive%20style%20of%20functioning%20while%20remaining%20resolute%20in%20his%20goals%2C%20which%20brought%20him%20the%20support%2C%20love%20and%20admiration%20of%20the%20millions%20in%20a%20manner%20which%20was%20surpassed%20only%20by%20Gandhiji.%20And%20as%20a%20true%20disciple%20of%20the%20master%2C%20while%20appealing%20to%20all%20sections%20of%20society%2C%20he%20succeeded%20in%20keeping%20his%20gaze%20focused%20on%20the%20poor%2C%20the%20oppressed%20and%20the%20disadvantaged.%20His%20great%20achievement%20was%20that%20he%20got%20a%20very%20large%20part%20of%20Indian%20society%2C%20individuals%20and%20institutions%2C%20to%20share%20his%20socialist%20vision.%20In%20the%20Nehruvian%20period%2C%20from%20the%20planning%20commission%20and%20the%20public%20sector%20bureaucracy%20to%20the%20media%20and%20popular%20films%2C%20the%20socialist%20objective%20was%20seen%20as%20a%20desirable%20one%2C%20not%20defined%20in%20any%20narrow%20fundamentalist%20way%20but%20as%20Nehru%20broadly%20outlined%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20land%20reforms%2C%20the%20Green%20Revolution%2C%20the%20Community%20Development%20Programme%2C%20the%20emergence%20of%20the%20public%20sector%2C%20the%20focus%20on%20education%20and%20health%20being%20a%20public%20responsibility%2C%20protecting%20of%20working%20class%20rights%2C%20the%20popularising%20of%20the%20socialist%20ideal%20were%20giant%20steps%20taken%20by%20Nehru%20that%20greatly%20contributed%20towards%20an%20equitable%20society.%20Many%20of%20these%20steps%20are%20being%20reversed%20today%20with%20the%20privatisation%20of%20public%20sector%20enterprises%20and%20more%20shockingly%20handing%20over%20education%20and%20health%20to%20the%20rapacious%20private%20sector%2C%20rapid%20informalisation%20of%20labour%20with%20no%20trade%20union%20rights%20and%20making%20a%20mockery%20of%20the%20socialist%20ideal.%20The%20results%20are%20there%20for%20the%20world%20to%20see.%20India%20is%20witnessing%20obscene%20levels%20of%20inequality%20where%20we%20boast%20of%20our%20large%20number%20of%20billionaires%20while%20nearly%20half%20our%20children%20are%20malnourished.%20The%20world%20was%20shocked%20by%20the%20images%20of%20floating%20dead%20bodies%20in%20the%20river%20Ganga%2C%20victims%20of%20the%20Corona%20epidemic%2C%20as%20the%20relatives%20of%20the%20deceased%20were%20too%20poor%20to%20do%20the%20last%20rites%20of%20their%20dear%20ones%20or%20that%20of%20thousands%20of%20migrant%20workers%20walking%20hundreds%20of%20miles%20to%20their%20villages%20at%20temperatures%20of%2045%20degrees%20centigrade%2C%20dragging%20their%20old%20and%20infirm%20and%20children%20to%20avoid%20starvation%20because%20of%20the%20sudden%20lockdown%20without%20adequate%20state%20support.%20We%20are%20slipping%20rapidly%20in%20the%20human%20development%20index%20and%20are%20today%20shamefully%20ranked%20111%20out%20of%20125%20countries%20in%20the%20Global%20Hunger%20Index%2C%20below%20many%20sub-Sahara%20African%20countries%20and%20much%20below%20every%20other%20South%20Asian%20country%2C%20with%20Sri%20Lanka%20at%2060%2C%20Nepal%2069%20and%20Bangladesh%2081!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESixty%20after%20his%20death%2C%20with%20infinitely%20higher%20economic%20capacity%20to%20empower%20the%20poor%2C%20when%20we%20falter%20miserably%20on%20this%20count%2C%20we%20realize%20how%20important%20it%20is%20to%20remember%20Nehru%E2%80%99s%20legacy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EScientific%20Temper%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENehru%E2%80%99s%20focus%20on%20the%20need%20to%20develop%20a%20%E2%80%98scientific%20temper%E2%80%99%2C%20a%20term%20he%20coined%20in%20his%20Discovery%20of%20India%2C%20which%20the%20Constitution%20of%20India%20reiterated%20in%20article%2051A%20laying%20down%20the%20fundamental%20duties%20of%20every%20citizen%20of%20India%2C%20is%20being%20made%20a%20mockery%20of%20today.%20Nehru%20said%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20scientific%20temper%20points%20out%20the%20way%20along%20which%20man%20should%20travel%E2%80%A6.%20It%20is%20the%20scientific%20approach%2C%20the%20adventurous%20and%20yet%20critical%20temper%20of%20science%2C%20the%20search%20for%20truth%20and%20new%20knowledge%2C%20the%20refusal%20to%20accept%20anything%20without%20testing%20and%20trial%2C%20the%20capacity%20to%20change%20previous%20conclusions%20in%20the%20face%20of%20evidence%2C%20the%20reliance%20on%20the%20observed%20fact%20and%20not%20pre-conceived%20theory%2C%20the%20hard%20discipline%20of%20the%20mind%20%E2%80%93%20all%20this%20is%20necessary%2C%20not%20merely%20for%20the%20application%20of%20science%20but%20for%20life%20itself%20and%20solution%20of%20its%20many%20problems%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENehru%20tried%20to%20imbibe%20this%20spirit%20in%20his%20thinking%20and%20action%20throughout%20his%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20a%20contrast%20today.%20The%20Guardian%20quoted%20the%20current%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20mixing%20up%20mythology%20about%20Gods%20and%20Goddesses%20with%20history%20and%20science%2C%20while%20inaugurating%20a%20new%20modern%20hospital%20in%20Mumbai%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20can%20feel%20proud%20of%20what%20our%20country%20achieved%20in%20medical%20science%20at%20one%20point%20of%20time%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20prime%20minister%20told%20a%20gathering%20of%20doctors%20and%20other%20professionals%20at%20a%20hospital%20in%20Mumbai%20%E2%80%A6%20%E2%80%9CWe%20all%20read%20about%20Karna%20in%20the%20Mahabharata.%20If%20we%20think%20a%20little%20more%2C%20we%20realise%20that%20the%20Mahabharata%20says%20Karna%20was%20not%20born%20from%20his%20mother%E2%80%99s%20womb.%20This%20means%20that%20genetic%20science%20was%20present%20at%20that%20time.%20That%20is%20why%20Karna%20could%20be%20born%20outside%20his%20mother%E2%80%99s%20womb%E2%80%A6.We%20worship%20Lord%20Ganesha.%20There%20must%20have%20been%20some%20plastic%20surgeon%20at%20that%20time%20who%20got%20an%20elephant%E2%80%99s%20head%20on%20the%20body%20of%20a%20human%20being%20and%20began%20the%20practice%20of%20plastic%20surgery%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Hindustan%20Times%20reported%20that%20Governor%20of%20Bengal%2C%20doing%20violence%20to%20both%20science%20and%20history%2C%20said%20%E2%80%9Cwhile%20addressing%20a%20science%20and%20engineering%20fair%20in%20Kolkata%20%E2%80%A6that%20mythological%20character%20Arjuna%E2%80%99s%20arrows%20had%20nuclear%20power%20and%20chariots%20mentioned%20in%20the%20Mahabharata%20actually%20flew%E2%80%9D.%20He%20has%20since%20been%20promoted%20to%20become%20the%20Vice%20President%20of%20India.%20The%20erstwhile%20RSS%20chief%20(sarsangchalak)%20K.S.%20Sudershan%2C%20an%20engineer%20by%20training%2C%20tells%20us%20about%20how%20Sage%20Bharadwaja%20and%20Raja%20Bhoj%20in%20times%20gone%20by%20not%20only%20%E2%80%98described%20the%20construction%20of%20aeroplanes%E2%80%99%20but%20discussed%20%E2%80%98details%20like%20what%20types%20of%20aeroplanes%20would%20fly%20at%20what%20height%2C%20what%20kind%20of%20problems%20they%20might%20encounter%2C%20how%20to%20overcome%20those%20problems%2C%20etc%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENo%20wonder%20Corona%20was%20being%20fought%20with%20state%20patronage%20with%20Gobar%20(cowdung)%2C%20Gomutra%20(cow%20urine)%2C%20Thali%20(metal%20plate)%20banging%2C%20Tali%20(clapping)%2C%20shining%20mobile%20phone%20torches%2C%20Ganga-snan%20(dip%20in%20the%20Ganges)%20and%20unverified%20medicines%20made%20by%20a%20much%20favoured%20yogi!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20sum%2C%20it%20is%20as%20if%20the%20political%20leaders%20have%20reversed%20their%20roles.%20From%20that%20of%20pulling%20up%20society%20and%20bringing%20it%20in%20line%20with%20the%20highest%20global%20civilizational%20values%2C%20a%20role%20performed%20by%20the%20leaders%20of%20the%20Indian%20national%20movement%20like%20Gandhiji%20and%20Nehru%2C%20to%20that%20of%20pushing%20society%20back%20by%20appealing%20to%20sectarian%20identities%2C%20acquisitive%20instincts%20and%20traditional%20prejudices.%20The%20hegemonic%20%E2%80%98Idea%20of%20India%E2%80%99%2C%20the%20%E2%80%98common%20sense%E2%80%99%20of%20the%20Indian%20people%20created%20by%20the%20Indian%20national%20movement%20is%20today%20severely%20challenged.%20And%20that%20challenge%20is%20not%20coming%20from%20a%20%E2%80%98backward%E2%80%99%2C%20%E2%80%98traditional%E2%80%99%20people%20but%20from%20their%20leaders%20and%20the%20state%20machinery.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENehru%E2%80%99s%20fantastic%20effort%20to%20raise%20India%20from%20what%20Tagore%20called%20the%20%E2%80%98mud%20and%20filth%E2%80%99%20left%20behind%20by%20the%20British%20has%20now%20been%20replaced%20with%20the%20Indian%20people%20being%20pushed%20back%20into%20that%20same%20%E2%80%98mud%20and%20filth%E2%80%99%20of%20ignorance%2C%20obscurantism%2C%20dis-empowerment%2C%20unfreedom%20and%20above%20all%20communal%20hatred.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704897046000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F14123424%2FJef_Rens_et_Jawaharlal_Nehru_-_1947.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fjawaharlal-nehru-in-our-past-present-and-future%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Nehru%E2%80%99s%20fantastic%20effort%20to%20raise%20India%20from%20what%20Tagore%20called%20the%20%E2%80%98mud%20and%20filth%E2%80%99%20left%20behind%20by%20the%20British%20has%20now%20been%20replaced%20with%20the%20Indian%20people%20being%20pushed%20back%20into%20that%20same%20%E2%80%98mud%20and%20filth%E2%80%99%20of%20ignorance%2C%2