%2FVP-n-BB.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20In%20an%20unusual%20message%20of%20support%2C%20wrestler%20Vinesh%20Phogat%20wrote%20to%20Bilkis%20Bano%20about%20the%20recent%20Supreme%20Court%20judgement%20in%20the%20latter%E2%80%99s%20favour%2C%20calling%20it%20a%20%E2%80%9Cvictory%20for%20all%20of%20us%20women%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBilkis%20%3Cem%3Eji%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20this%20is%20a%20victory%20for%20all%20of%20us%20women.%20You%20have%20fought%20a%20long%20struggle.%20We%20take%20courage%20looking%20at%20your%20journey%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fphogat_vinesh%2Fstatus%2F1744396543564906794%5C%22%3EPhogat%20said%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Hindi%20on%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBano%20is%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fin-her-own-words-what-bilkis-bano-went-through-in-2002%5C%22%3Esurvivor%20of%20a%20gruesome%20attack%3C%2Fa%3E%20during%20the%202002%20Gujarat%20riots%20in%20which%20she%20and%20her%20family%20members%20were%20gang-raped%20by%20a%20mob.%20Fourteen%20of%20her%20relatives%20were%20also%20slain%20in%20the%20incident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEleven%20people%20convicted%20and%20sentenced%20to%20life%20for%20the%20gang-rape%20and%20mass%20murder%20were%20released%20early%20by%20the%20Gujarat%20government%20in%202022%2C%20but%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fbilkis-bano-supreme-court-gujarat-not-competent-remission%5C%22%3Ethe%20Supreme%20Court%20cancelled%20their%20remission%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Monday%20(January%208)%20and%20ordered%20them%20to%20report%20back%20to%20prison.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPhogat%20is%20among%20the%20main%20faces%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ftag%2Fwrestlers-protest%5C%22%3Elast%20year%E2%80%99s%20protests%20by%20prominent%20wrestlers%3C%2Fa%3E%20against%20BJP%20MP%20and%20former%20Wrestling%20Federation%20of%20India%20chief%20Brij%20Bhushan%20Sharan%20Singh%2C%20who%20is%20accused%20of%20sexually%20harassing%20at%20least%20seven%20wrestlers.%20Singh%20has%20denied%20the%20allegations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPhogat%20is%20also%20the%20first%20Indian%20woman%20wrestler%20to%20have%20won%20a%20gold%20at%20both%20the%20Commonwealth%20and%20Asian%20Games%2C%20as%20well%20as%20the%20only%20Indian%20woman%20wrestler%20to%20win%20multiple%20medals%20at%20the%20World%20Wrestling%20Championships.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20other%20news%20related%20to%20the%20Supreme%20Court%E2%80%99s%20judgement%20on%20Monday%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fcities%2Fahmedabad%2Fbilkis-bano-case-convicts-not-at-home-in-dahod-villages-families-tight-lipped-9100866%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EIndian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%20reports%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20nine%20of%20the%2011%20convicts%20in%20the%20case%20went%20%E2%80%9Cmissing%E2%80%9D%20from%20the%20twin%20villages%20of%20Randhikpur%20and%20Singvad%20in%20Gujarat%E2%80%99s%20Dahod%20district.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBano%20was%20also%20in%20Randhikpur%20when%20the%20Godhra%20train%20burning%2C%20which%20triggered%20the%202002%20riots%2C%20occurred.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%20%7C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fbilkis-bano-order-meaning-womens-rights-modi%5C%22%3ESix%20Things%3A%20Bilkis%20Bano%20Convicts%20Being%20Sent%20Back%20to%20Prison%20Is%20a%20Verdict%20on%20Much%20More%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAkhambhai%20Chaturbhai%20Raval%20(87)%2C%20father%20of%20one%20of%20the%20convicts%2C%20Govind%20Nai%20(55)%2C%20claimed%20his%20son%20was%20innocent%20and%20blamed%20the%20conviction%20on%20%E2%80%9Cpolitical%20vendetta%20of%C2%A0%5Bthe%5D%20Congress%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20told%20%3Cem%3EIE%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20Govind%20had%20left%20the%20house%20%E2%80%9Ca%20week%20ago%E2%80%9D.%20However%2C%20its%20report%20also%20cites%20a%20local%20policeman%20as%20saying%20that%20Nai%20had%20left%20home%20on%20Saturday%20(January%206).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20parents%20are%20reported%20as%20also%20saying%20they%20are%20a%20%E2%80%9CHindu%20faith-abiding%20family%2C%20incapable%20of%20committing%20the%20crimes%E2%80%9D%20that%20have%20been%20alleged%20against%20their%20son%20as%20well%20as%20against%20Nai%E2%80%99s%20uncle%20and%20Akhambhai%E2%80%99s%20brother%2C%20Jashvant%20Nai%2C%20who%20is%20another%20of%20the%2011%20convicts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20wish%20and%20pray%20that%20he%20%5BNai%5D%20gets%20to%20do%20%3Cem%3Eseva%3C%2Fem%3E%20%5Bservice%5D%20at%20the%20%5BRam%5D%20%3Cem%3Emandir%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3Epratishthan%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%20Ayodhya.%20It%20is%20better%20to%20do%20seva%20than%20do%20nothing%20and%20roam%20around%20every%20day.%20He%20has%20not%20been%20able%20to%20do%20anything%20since%20he%20was%20released%20%5Bfrom%20prison%5D%2C%E2%80%9D%20Raval%20was%20quoted%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CGoing%20back%20to%20jail%20is%20not%20a%20big%20deal%20and%20it%20is%20not%20that%20he%20was%20out%20of%20jail%20unlawfully.%20He%20was%20released%20with%20due%20process%20of%20law%20and%20now%20the%20law%20has%20told%20him%20to%20go%20back%2C%20so%20he%20will%20go%20back.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F18150906%2FSupreme-Court-1024x683.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F18150906%2FSupreme-Court-1024x683.jpg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F18150906%2FSupreme-Court-300x200.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F18150906%2FSupreme-Court.jpg%201200w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-653640%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EA%20bench%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20said%20the%20Gujarat%20government%20had%20%E2%80%9Cacted%20in%20complicity%20with%20the%20convicts%E2%80%9D%20by%20remitting%20their%20sentence.%20Photo%3A%20Subhashish%20Panigrahi%2FWikimedia%20Commons.%20CC%20BY-SA%204.0.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Monday%2C%20a%20division%20bench%20of%20the%20apex%20court%20comprising%20Justices%20B.V.%20Nagarathna%20and%20Ujjal%20Bhuyan%20had%20said%20that%20the%20state%20of%20Gujarat%20%E2%80%9Cacted%20in%20complicity%20with%20the%20convicts%E2%80%9D%20and%20noted%20that%20%E2%80%9Cit%20was%20this%20very%20apprehension%20which%20led%20this%20Court%20to%20transfer%20the%20trial%20out%20of%20the%20State%E2%80%9D%20to%20Maharashtra%2C%20according%20to%C2%A0%3Cem%3ELiveLaw%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%C2%A0which%20live-tweeted%20the%20delivery%20of%20the%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20also%20noted%20that%20if%20the%20convicts%20can%20%E2%80%9Ccircumvent%20the%20consequences%20of%20their%20conviction%2C%20peace%20and%20tranquillity%20in%20the%20society%20will%20be%20reduced%20to%20a%20chimaera.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20key%20observation%20by%20the%20court%20was%3A%20%E2%80%9CWe%20hold%20that%20deprivation%20of%20liberty%20to%20the%20respondents%20(convicts)%20is%20justified.%20They%20have%20lost%20their%20right%20to%20liberty%20once%20they%20were%20convicted%20and%20imprisoned.%20Also%2C%20if%20they%20want%20to%20seek%20remission%20again%2C%20it%20is%20important%20that%20they%20have%20to%20be%20in%20jail.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704896684000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F10195043%2FVP-n-BB.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2F9-out-11-convicts-in-bilkis-bano-case-go-missing-report-says%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Meanwhile%2C%20the%20Indian%20Express%20has%20reported%20that%20nine%20out%20of%20the%2011%20convicts%20whose%20remission%20the%20apex%2