news-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Falexei-navalny-jokes-about-moscow-naked-party-in-video-call-from-arctic-penal-colony-13045382%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Falexei-navalny-jokes-about-moscow-naked-party-in-video-call-from-arctic-penal-colony-13045382%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20January%2022%20Ram%20Temple%20Inauguration%20Is%20a%20Political%20Event.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20Crucial%20Test%20for%20Indian%20Politics%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F27171854%2Fimage-1678.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20no%20god%20in%20that%20temple%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20the%20saint.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20King%20was%20enraged%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNo%20God%3F%20Oh%20Saint%2C%20aren%E2%80%99t%20you%20speaking%20like%20an%20atheist%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20throne%20studded%20with%20priceless%20gems%2C%20beams%20the%20golden%20idol%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20yet%2C%20you%20proclaim%20that%E2%80%99s%20empty%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20not%20empty%3B%20It%E2%80%99s%20rather%20full%20of%20the%20Royal%20pride.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYou%20have%20bestowed%20yourself%2C%20oh%20King%2C%20not%20the%20God%20of%20this%20world%E2%80%9D%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERemarked%20the%20saint.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%93%20Rabindranath%20Tagore%20(%E2%80%98Deeno%20Daan%E2%80%99)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%5B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmainstreamweekly.net%2Farticle9787.html%5C%22%3ETranslated%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20the%20original%20Bengali%20into%20English%20by%20Sandipto%20Das%20Gupta%5D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThus%20would%20have%20responded%20Tagore%C2%A0to%20the%20invitation%20of%20the%20Vishwa%20Hindu%20Parishad%20(VHP)%20to%20attend%20the%20opening%20ceremony%20of%20the%20Ram%20temple%2C%20which%20is%20not%20yet%20complete.%20He%20would%20have%20refused%20to%20even%20accept%20the%20invitation%20as%20it%20is%20not%20about%20Ram%20at%20all.%20It%20is%20a%20celebration%20of%20the%20victory%20of%20a%20deceitful%20and%20violent%20campaign%20of%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20to%20confuse%20the%20Hindus%20and%20present%20itself%20as%20the%20patron%20and%20guardian%20of%20Ram%20and%20Hindu%20interests%2C%20which%20could%20only%20be%20served%20by%20humiliating%20and%20violating%20Muslims.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20Tagore%20would%20have%20to%20find%20stronger%20words%20of%20rebuke%20for%20those%20representing%20the%20Ram%20Temple%20Trust.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20not%20only%20royal%20pride%20which%20drives%20the%20sacred%20spirit%20out%20of%20the%20%E2%80%98religious%E2%80%99%20space.%20Can%20a%20stolen%20land%20host%20piousness%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20party%2C%20which%20had%20once%20the%20great%20Tagore%20as%20its%20friend%2C%20seemed%20to%20be%20in%20great%20dilemma%3A%20whether%20to%20join%20the%20inauguration%20ceremony%20of%20the%20Ram%20temple%20in%20Ayodhya%20or%20not.%20However%2C%20on%20January%2010%20(Wednesday)%2C%20it%20declined%20the%20invitation%20to%20the%20Ram%20temple%20inauguration%20ceremony%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fbreaking-congress-declines-invitation-to-ram-temple-inauguration-calls-its-clearly-an-rss-bjp-event%5C%22%3Esaying%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%9Cit%E2%80%99s%20clearly%20an%20RSS%2FBJP%20ceremony%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20the%20same%20temple%2C%20which%20is%20being%20built%20on%20the%20land%20of%20the%20Babri%20Masjid%20after%20demolishing%20it%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fbabri-masjid-the-timeline-of-a-demolition%5C%22%3Ecriminal%20act%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20then%20usurping%20the%20land%20through%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fbabri-demolition-anniversary-doctrine-non-retrogression%5C%22%3Ejudicial%20fraud%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Many%20people%20were%20relishing%20the%20predicament%20of%20the%20Congress%20party.%20While%20some%20were%20applauding%20it%20as%20a%20masterstroke%20of%20the%20BJP%3A%20see%20how%20they%20have%20laid%20a%20trap%20for%20the%20Congress.%20However%2C%20with%20the%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20announcement%2C%20this%20dilemma%20seems%20to%20be%20have%20dissipated%20for%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%2C%20we%20all%20should%20question%20if%20this%20is%20only%20the%20problem%20of%20political%20parties%20or%20is%20it%20the%20problem%20of%20the%20entire%20country%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20we%20say%20country%2C%20then%20let%20us%20also%20honestly%20accept%20that%20this%20is%20a%20problem%20of%20all%20Hindus.%20Muslims%20do%20not%20care%20much%20about%20the%20construction%20of%20this%20temple%2C%20its%20date%2C%20who%20attends%20it%20and%20who%20does%20not.%20They%20have%20already%20paid%20the%20price%20for%20the%20construction%20of%20this%20temple.%20This%20temple%20would%20not%20have%20been%20possible%20without%20the%20demolition%20of%20the%20Babri%20Masjid.%20Moreover%2C%20the%20Ram%20temple%20campaign%20was%20intended%20to%20humiliate%20Muslims.%20If%20we%20remember%20the%20slogans%20of%20this%20campaign%2C%20they%20were%20more%20against%20Muslims%20than%20about%20Ram.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20temple%20will%20continue%20to%20remind%20Muslims%20of%20violence%20and%20bloodshed%20against%20them.%20And%20finally%2C%20Muslims%20cannot%20forget%20the%20ultimate%20injustice%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%20They%20know%20that%20this%20temple%20is%20not%20so%20much%20a%20monument%20of%20reverence%20for%20Ram%20as%20it%20is%20a%20symbol%20of%20hatred%20against%20Muslims%20and%20an%20imagined%20victory%20of%20Hindus%20over%20them.%20They%20also%20know%20that%20almost%20all%20the%20political%20parties%20in%20this%20country%20are%20Hindu%20parties.%20That%E2%80%99s%20why%20it%20is%20not%20only%20about%20the%20non-BJP%20parties%20which%20are%20yet%20to%20take%20a%20stand%20on%20this%20matter.%20It%20is%20also%20about%20Hindus.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20do%20not%20accept%20the%20invitation%2C%20there%20is%20a%20danger%20of%20the%20party%20losing%20sympathy%20of%20Hindus%20and%20if%20it%20accepts%20it%2C%20it%20will%20mean%20compromising%20its%20morality.%20However%2C%20it%20will%20also%20mean%20that%20there%20is%20still%20a%20sense%20of%20political%20morality%20left%20in%20this%20country.%20It%20is%20not%20about%20secularism%20in%20a%20superficial%20way%2C%20although%20that%20is%20also%20part%20of%20it.%20It%20is%20about%20the%20morality%20of%20justice%20in%20the%20broadest%20sense.%20We%20know%20that%20this%20temple%20is%20a%20symbol%20of%20a%20great%20injustice%2C%20and%20it%20is%20not%20appropriate%20to%20celebrate%20injustice.%20But%20before%20considering%20this%20aspect%2C%20some%20more%20questions%20crop%20up.%20The%20questions%20should%20be%20asked%20to%20those%20who%20do%20not%20see%20anything%20wrong%20with%20the%20temple%20and%20think%20that%20it%20is%20a%20sacred%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20know%20that%20this%20temple%20is%20still%20incomplete.%20The%20construction%20work%20is%20going%20on.%20Then%20what%20is%20the%20hurry%20to%20inaugurate%20the%20sanctum%20sanctorum%20when%20the%20temple%20is%20still%20being%20built%3F%20Many%20times%2C%20the%20house%20warming%20ritual%20is%20performed%20in%20an%20incomplete%20house%20due%20to%20some%20practical%20compulsions.%20For%20instance%2C%20a%20special%20person%20from%20the%20family%20is%20going%20abroad%2C%20someone%E2%80%99s%20parents%20have%20become%20so%20old%20that%20one%20does%20not%20know%20if%20they%20would%20be%20able%20to%20see%20their%20children%E2%80%99s%20own%20home%20in%20their%20lifetime%2C%20etc.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20why%20is%20there%20so%20much%20anxiety%20to%20install%20Ram%20Lalla%20in%20an%20incomplete%20temple%3F%20Is%20it%20because%20he%20is%20shivering%20in%20the%20cold%3F%20Or%20is%20it%20being%20done%20to%20protect%20Him%20from%20the%20rains%3F%20What%20is%20the%20reason%20for%20the%20hurry%3F%20Those%20who%20are%20sincere%20devotees%20of%20Ram%2C%20that%20is%2C%20not%20political%20devotees%20of%20Ram%2C%20are%20not%20going%20anywhere.%20They%20are%20not%20in%20a%20rush%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%2C%20however%2C%20is%20in%20a%20tearing%20hurry%20to%20install%20the%20minor%20Ram%20in%20the%20incomplete%20temple.%20Is%20it%20because%20another%20auspicious%20time%20will%20not%20come%20again%20for%20the%20next%20five%20years%3F%20We%20all%2C%20including%20those%20who%20call%20themselves%20true%20Ram%20devotees%2C%20know%20that%20there%20is%20only%20one%20reason%20for%20the%20rush%3A%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20which%20are%20expected%20to%20be%20held%20after%20three%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20inauguration%20should%20be%20done%20now%20so%20that%20BJP%20can%20boast%20of%20its%20achievement%20of%20getting%20%E2%80%98minor%20Ram%E2%80%99%20his%20home%20in%20this%20election%20campaign.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20also%20because%20the%20photos%20of%20Narendra%20Modi%20doing%20the%20%3Cem%3Ebhoomi%20pujan%3C%2Fem%3E%20on%20the%20land%20of%20Babri%20Masjid%C2%A0have%20become%20slightly%20old%2C%20even%20if%20they%20are%20still%20being%20used.%20But%20more%20photos%20are%20needed%2C%20to%20establish%20Narendra%20Modi%20as%20the%20%E2%80%98first%20Hindu%E2%80%99%20of%20India%2C%20him%20being%20the%20Purohit%20and%20the%20Yajman%20at%20the%20same%20time.%20He%20and%20his%20party%20need%20a%20constant%20supply%20of%20such%20photos.%20The%20photo%20of%20the%20prime%20minister%20consecrating%20%E2%80%98Ram%20Lalla%E2%80%99%20in%20Ayodhya%20will%20promote%20Modi%20as%20the%20civilisational%20man%2C%20the%20%E2%80%98king%E2%80%99%20who%20brought%20Ram%20back%20home.%20This%20photo%20has%20electoral%20significance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Narendra%20Modi%20takes%20part%20in%20the%20%3Cem%3Ebhoomi%20pujan%3C%2Fem%3E%20for%20the%20construction%20of%20a%20Ram%20temple%20in%20Ayodhya%2C%20August%205%2C%202020.%20Photo%3A%20PIB%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20photo%20of%20Modi%20performing%20the%20%E2%80%98Pran%20Pratistha%E2%80%99%20of%20%E2%80%98Ram%20Lalla%E2%80%99%20is%20crucial%20in%20the%20campaign%20to%20solidify%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20image%20as%20the%20chosen%20leader%20in%20the%20Hindu%20mindset.%20You%20might%20have%20heard%20the%20statement%20from%20Champat%20Rai%2C%20the%20secretary%20of%20the%20Ram%20Temple%20Trust.%20He%20asserts%20that%20the%20king%20is%20the%20incarnation%20of%20Vishnu%2C%20and%20according%20to%20him%2C%20Modi%20is%20the%20king%3B%20hence%2C%20he%20is%20considered%20an%20incarnation%20of%20Vishnu.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fits-a-ram-mandir-ramanand-tradition-to-be-followed-temple-trusts-secy-remarks-draw-criticism%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Temple%20Belongs%20to%20Ramanand%20Sect%2C%20Not%20to%20Sanyasis%2C%20Shaiva%20or%20Shakta%E2%80%99%3A%20Champat%20Rai%E2%80%99s%20Remarks%20Draw%20Ire%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMoral%20doubts%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20hopes%20that%20the%20images%20of%20the%20consecration%20of%20%E2%80%98Ram%20Lalla%E2%80%99%20in%20this%20new%20Ram%20temple%20in%20Ayodhya%20will%20influence%20Hindu%20psychology%20more%20than%20any%20other%20slogan%20or%20promise.%20You%20don%E2%80%99t%20need%20to%20be%20an%20analyst%20to%20say%20that%20this%20will%20go%20a%20long%20way%20in%20hiding%20the%20other%20failures%20of%20the%20BJP%20government.%20This%20photo%20will%20also%20be%20proof%20of%20the%20rise%20of%20a%20%E2%80%98Hindu%20nation%E2%80%99.%20A%20nation%20which%20has%20finally%20washed%20all%20the%20stains%20of%20the%20outsider%20Mughal%20era.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20are%20aware%20of%20all%20this%2C%20and%20so%20are%20the%20Congress%20and%20other%20non-BJP%20parties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20times%20of%20moral%20uncertainty%2C%20the%20Indian%20tradition%20of%20turning%20to%20what%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%20would%20have%20done%20still%20persists.%20Even%20for%20justifying%20questionable%20actions%2C%20big%20people%20take%20the%20name%20of%20Gandhi.%20Like%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20did%20recently%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fcji-invokes-dhwaja-on-temples-to-serve-as-inspiration-for-courts-draws-attention%23%3A~%3Atext%3DHe%2520is%2520reported%2520to%2520have%2Cas%2520judges%252C%2520as%2520citizens%25E2%2580%259D.%5C%22%3Ejustify%20his%20public%20display%20of%20a%20temple%20visit%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Gujarat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20would%20he%20have%20told%20the%20VHP%20or%20the%20Rashtriya%20Swayamsevak%20Sangh%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHad%20he%20been%20alive%2C%20the%20Temple%20Trust%20would%20have%20definitely%20invited%20Gandhi.%20This%20is%20ironic%2C%20because%20the%20person%20who%20assassinated%20Gandhi%20was%20a%20member%20of%20the%20organisations%20associated%20with%20this%20Trust.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20Gandhi%20were%20to%20receive%20this%20invitation%2C%20he%20would%20not%20have%20promptly%20rejected%20it.%20Gandhi%20rarely%20visited%20temples%2C%20and%20he%20didn%E2%80%99t%20need%20to%20prove%20his%20%E2%80%98Hindu-ness%E2%80%99%20by%20visiting%20temples%2C%20wearing%20saffron%2C%20or%20smearing%20%3Cem%3Echandan%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20%3Cem%3Etilak%3C%2Fem%3E%20on%20his%20forehead.%20Rather%2C%20he%20tried%20throughout%20his%20life%20to%20transcend%20his%20%E2%80%98Hindu-ness%E2%80%99%20and%20enrich%20it%20with%20new%20experiences.%20He%20never%20needed%20approval%20from%20any%20Shankaracharya%20or%20any%20religious%20guru.%20He%20was%20a%20confident%20Hindu%2C%20unlike%20our%20present-day%20politicians%20who%20often%20appear%20insecure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20Gandhi%20would%20not%20have%20said%20that%20since%20his%20Ram%20resided%20in%20his%20heart%2C%20he%20did%20not%20feel%20the%20need%20to%20visit%20any%20temple.%20It%20would%20have%20been%20a%20cowardly%20cover.%20Not%20for%20a%20brave%20man%20like%20Gandhi.%20He%20would%20have%20fought%20with%20his%20body%20and%20soul%20for%20this%20moment%20not%20to%20arrive.%20He%20would%20have%20started%20a%20movement%20for%20the%20demolished%20Babri%20Masjid%20to%20be%20rebuilt%20and%20returned%20to%20the%20Muslims.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%201947-48%2C%20numerous%20mosques%2C%20tombs%2C%20and%20dargahs%20in%20Delhi%20were%20damaged%20and%20seized%20by%20Hindus%20and%20Sikhs.%20Even%20the%20Connaught%20Place%20mosque%20was%20captured%2C%20with%20idols%20placed%20inside%20it.%20Gandhi%20had%20consistently%20emphasised%20the%20need%20to%20vacate%20the%20mosques%20that%20had%20been%20occupied.%20He%20further%20insisted%20on%20the%20evacuation%20of%20Islamic%20buildings%20taken%20over%20by%20refugees%2C%20a%20stance%20that%20caused%20outrage%20among%20them.%20This%20insistence%20made%20life%20uncomfortable%20for%20his%20friends%20in%20the%20government%2C%20but%20he%20remained%20steadfast%20in%20his%20stance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EObviously%2C%20Gandhi%20became%20unpopular%20among%20Hindus%20because%20of%20his%20stance.%20However%2C%20that%20fear%20could%20not%20make%20him%20change%20his%20stand%20or%20remain%20silent.%20Gandhi%20used%20to%20call%20a%20crime%20a%20crime%20and%20never%20let%20it%20go.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20accepted%20that%20two%20crimes%20were%20committed%20to%20convert%20Babri%20Masjid%20into%20a%20temple.%20Were%20the%20people%20involved%20in%20that%20crime%20punished%3F%20Far%20from%20being%20punished%2C%20those%20who%20planned%20the%20crime%20were%20given%20the%20land%20of%20the%20mosque%20to%20build%20the%20temple.%20How%20can%20any%20reasonable%20person%20accept%20this%3F%20Even%20if%20circumstances%20were%20hostile%2C%20how%20can%20one%20compromise%20with%20a%20crime%20and%20live%20with%20it%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20entire%20event%20is%20organised%20by%20the%20BJP.%20The%20RSS%20workers%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fvaranasi%2Fjoin-rss-campaign-for-ram-temple-consecration-ce