0raised%20in%20Kerala%2C%20Ajayan%20relocated%20to%20Bengaluru%20in%201999%20in%20pursuit%20of%20employment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20came%20to%20the%20city%20for%20a%20job%20and%20instantly%20fell%20in%20love%20with%20it.%20The%20climate%20and%20the%20rich%20culture%20motivated%20me%20to%20establish%20a%20life%20here.%20I%E2%80%99ve%20been%20working%20in%20the%20corporate%20sector%20ever%20since%2C%20building%20a%20home%20and%20a%20life%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20building%20his%20life%20in%20the%20city%2C%20there%20came%20a%20point%20when%20Ajayan%20desired%20to%20contribute%20to%20society%20by%20going%20beyond%20the%20routine.%20%E2%80%9CSooner%20or%20later%2C%20everyone%20experiences%20the%20urge%20to%20do%20something%20more%20meaningful.%20After%20working%20for%20numerous%20years%2C%20I%20felt%20the%20need%20to%20make%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F229014%2Findia-farmer-agriculture-reforms-central-government-nirmala-sitharaman-essential-commodities-act-contract-farming-india-nor41%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20positive%20impact%20%3C%2Fa%3Eon%20society.%20This%20idea%2C%20once%20planted%2C%20lingered%20with%20me%20for%20a%20long%20time%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20reflects.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202016%2C%20he%20decided%20to%20make%20a%20New%20Year%20resolution%20to%20serve%20society.%20%E2%80%9CI%20happened%20to%20visit%20an%20orphanage%20located%20on%20Mysore%20Road.%20Despite%20being%20well-run%2C%20it%20lacked%20several%20amenities%2C%20and%20there%20were%20a%20significant%20number%20of%20children.%20When%20I%20visited%20in%20January%2C%20considering%20the%20climate%20in%20Bangalore%20and%20other%20parts%20of%20the%20area%2C%20I%20noticed%20the%20children%20were%20sleeping%20on%20the%20floor.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22