E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20turning%20point%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Ajayan%20kept%20an%20eye%20on%20such%20opportunities%2C%20it%20was%20his%20father%E2%80%99s%20illness%20that%20made%20him%20think%20of%20establishing%20the%20Sanathya%20Foundation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%202015%2C%20my%20father%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F333669%2Fbasic-health-tests-we-should-do-regularly-heart-lungs-kidneys-cancer-detection-inspiring-story%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehad%20a%20stroke%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Kerala%2C%20so%20I%20brought%20him%20here.%20During%20his%20recovery%2C%20he%20experienced%20another%20fall%2C%20resulting%20in%20a%20broken%20thigh.%20This%20incident%20required%20us%20to%20admit%20him%20to%20the%20hospital%20once%20again%2C%20where%20he%20underwent%20surgery.%20Following%20the%20surgical%20procedure%2C%20we%20had%20to%20purchase%20a%20medical%20bed%20as%20he%20was%20on%20complete%20bed%20rest%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAjayan%E2%80%99s%20father%20remained%20bedridden%20for%20several%20weeks%2C%20undergoing%20physiotherapy%20and%20various%20treatments.%20%E2%80%9CGradually%2C%20his%20condition%20improved%2C%20allowing%20him%20to%20transition%20to%20a%20wheelchair.%20After%20about%20a%20month%2C%20he%20progressed%20to%20using%20a%20walker%20and%20eventually%20a%20walking%20stick%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhile%20he%20used%20the%20walking%20stick%20until%20the%20end%2C%20the%20other%20equipment%20became%20redundant.%20It%E2%80%99s%20impractical%20to%20keep%20a%20large%20bed%20at%20home%20when%20it%E2%80%99s%20no%20longer%20needed.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAjayan%20also%20realised%20that%20the%20cost%20of%20these%20items%20was%20quite%20expensive%20and%20might%20be%20unaffordable%20to%20many.%20%E2%80%9CI%20approached%20the%20sellers%20of%20these%20types%20of%20equipment%20an