E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704893841000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fmedical-equipment-2-1704891555.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D337918%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Bengaluru's%20Ajayan%20Namminipurthu%20started%20Sanathya%20Foundation%20to%20provide%20free%20medical%20equipment%2C%20such%20as%20wheelchairs%20and%20nebulisers%2C%20to%20people%20who%20cannot%20afford%20to%20buy%20new%20ones.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Tina%20Freese%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F337918%2Fbengaluru-sanathya-foundation-provides-free-wheelchair-nebulizer-medical-equipment-on-rent%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Why%20Congress%20Clearly%20Saying%20January%2022%20Is%20Part%20of%20RSS%2FBJP%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98Political%20Project%E2%80%99%20Matters%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F17172550%2FF6NXWAsXUAAXN2b.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20After%20almost%20two%20weeks%20of%20indecisiveness%2C%20the%20Congress%20on%20Wednesday%20(January%2010)%20decided%20to%20boycott%20the%20consecration%20ceremony%20of%20the%20new%20Ram%20Janmabhoomi%20Temple%20on%20January%2022.%20The%20party%20released%20a%20statement%2C%20saying%20that%20Congress%20president%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%2C%20leader%20of%20opposition%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20Adhir%20Ranjan%20Chowdhury%2C%20and%20former%20president%20Sonia%20Gandhi%2C%20who%20were%20invited%20to%20attend%20the%20ceremony%2C%20have%20declined%20the%20invitation%20to%20what%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fbreaking-congress-declines-invitation-to-ram-temple-inauguration-calls-its-clearly-an-rss-bjp-event%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20them%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9Cis%20clearly%20an%20RSS%2FBJP%20event%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CLord%20Ram%20is%20worshipped%20by%20millions%20in%20our%20country.%20Religion%20is%20a%20personal%20matter.%20But%20the%20RSS%2FBJP%20have%20long%20made%20a%20political%20project%20of%20the%20temple%20in%20Ayodhya.%20The%20inauguration%20of%20the%20incomplete%20temple%20by%20the%20leaders%20of%20the%20BJP%20and%20the%20RSS%20has%20been%20obviously%20brought%20forward%20for%20electoral%20gain.%20While%20abiding%20by%20the%202019%20Supreme%20Court%20judgment%20and%20honouring%20the%20sentiments%20of%20millions%20who%20revere%20Lord%20Ram%2C%20Shri%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%2C%20Smt.%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20and%20Shri%20Adhir%20Ranjan%20Chowdhury%20have%20respectfully%20declined%20the%20invitation%20to%20what%20is%20clearly%20an%20RSS%2FBJP%20event%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20statement%20read.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EHere%20is%20the%20statement%20of%20Shri%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FJairam_Ramesh%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40Jairam_Ramesh%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20General%20Secretary%20(Communications)%2C%20Indian%20National%20Congress.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FJcKIEk3afy%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FJcKIEk3afy%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Congress%20(%40INCIndia)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FINCIndia%2Fstatus%2F1745034149457477811%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJanuary%2010%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20many%2C%20who%20viewed%20the%20construction%20of%20the%20temple%20atop%20the%20dome%20of%20the%20demolished%20Babri%20Masjid%20as%20the%20most%20stark%20symbol%20of%20injustice%20in%20democratic%20India%2C%20the%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20decision%20will%20come%20as%20a%20delayed%20but%20welcome%20relief.%20It%20was%20surprising%20that%20the%20Congress%2C%20which%20had%20been%20politically%20critical%20of%20both%20the%20Ram%20Janmabhoomi%20movement%20led%20by%20the%20Sangh%20%3Cem%3Eparivar%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20the%20subsequent%20demolition%20remained%20so%20much%20in%20doubt%20before%20eventually%20declining%20the%20invitation.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIts%20indecision%20over%20the%20last%20two%20weeks%20came%20across%20as%20not%20merely%20unethical%20and%20inconsistent%20with%20its%20own%20politics%20of%20multiculturalism%20but%20also%20displayed%20a%20sheer%20lack%20of%20courage%20among%20the%20party%20leaders%20to%20take%20on%20the%20choreographed%20publicity%20blitzkrieg%20around%20the%20Ram%20Janmabhoomi%20temple%20by%20the%20BJP.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20was%20amply%20clear%20from%20the%20very%20beginning%20that%20the%20hype%20around%20the%20consecration%20ceremony%20of%20a%20temple%2C%20which%20is%20fated%20to%20remain%20a%20polarising%20symbol%20even%20in%20the%20future%2C%20was%20a%20blatant%20attempt%20by%20the%20Narendra%20Modi-led%20BJP%20to%20consolidate%20its%20own%20ranks%20and%20manufacture%20a%20mass%20hysteria%20to%20deflect%20attention%20from%20the%20more%20pressing%20issues%20of%20common%20people.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThat%20the%20saffron%20party%20had%20decided%20to%20perform%20the%20consecration%20ceremony%20even%20when%20the%20temple%20construction%20is%20not%20even%20fully%20complete%20was%20a%20clear%20indication%20of%20how%20the%20BJP%20was%20trying%20to%20milk%20the%20epochal%20event%20for%20its%20own%20electoral%20gains.%20Why%20the%20Congress%20could%20not%20point%20that%20out%20to%20the%20public%20persuasively%20is%20a%20question%20that%20many%20may%20continue%20to%20ask%20even%20now.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20fact%2C%20the%20whole%20hype%20generated%20by%20the%20Modi%20government%20around%20the%20Ram%20Janmabhoomi%20temple%20appears%20to%20be%20repetitive%20at%20best.%20In%20September%202023%2C%20the%20prime%20minister%20used%20a%20special%20session%20of%20the%20Parliament%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Famidst-opposition-boycott-pm-narendra-modi-inaugurates-new-parliament-building%5C%22%3Einaugurate%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20similarly%20incomplete%20Parliament%20building%20and%20table%20the%20historic%20women%E2%80%99s%20reservation%20Bill%20which%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fwomen-reservation-implementation-article-81-82-census-delimitation%5C%22%3Ehad%20no%20scope%20to%20be%20implemented%3C%2Fa%3E%20before%202029.%20The%20grand%20posturing%20came%20months%20ahead%20of%20five%20crucial%20assembly%20elections.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENow%2C%20when%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20are%20months%20away%2C%20the%20prime%20minister%20is%20all%20set%20to%20be%20the%20principal%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Ejajmaan%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(patron)%20in%20the%20consecration%20ceremony.%20Electioneering%20is%20written%20large%20all%20over%20the%20optics%20created%20by%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Congress%20seemed%20to%20cower%20under%20the%20fear%20of%20offending%20Hindus%20if%20it%20took%20a%20principled%20stance%20against%20the%20hype%20created%20around%20the%20temple%20%E2%80%93%20something%20that%20only%20showed%20the%20opposition%20in%20poor%20light.%20This%2C%20when%20the%20party%20lost%20miserably%20in%20the%20recent%20elections%20held%20in%20the%20Hindi%20heartland%20despite%20adopting%20a%20soft-Hindutva%20approach.%20The%20indecision%20appeared%20even%20more%20cowardly%20at%20a%20time%20when%20Congress%20leader%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20will%20soon%20embark%20on%20the%20second%20leg%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fmallikarjun-kharge-bharat-jodo-nyay-yatra-bjp%5C%22%3EBharat%20Jodo%20Yatra%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20centred%20around%20communal%20harmony%20and%20constitutional%20values.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20after%20much%20deliberation%2C%20the%20party%20has%20now%20done%20what%20is%20consistent%20with%20its%20own%20positions.%20It%20now%20needs%20to%20take%20its%20decision%20forward%20by%20mounting%20an%20ideological%20opposition%20to%20the%20palpable%20communal%20frenzy%20that%20is%20sought%20to%20be%20advanced%20with%20the%20success%20of%20its%20Ram%20Janmabhoomi%20movement%2C%20aided%20and%20abetted%20by%20judicial%20sanction.%20There%20are%20already%20strong%20voices%20within%20the%20larger%20Sangh%20%3Cem%3Eparivar%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20the%20demolition%20of%20Babri%20Masjid%20was%20merely%20a%20beginning%20in%20the%20long%20list%20of%20mosques%20that%20will%20be%20targeted%20in%20the%20future.%20Sangh%20%3Cem%3Eparivar%3C%2Fem%3E%20leaders%20have%20already%20started%20to%20advance%20communally%20polarising%20narratives%20around%20mosques%20across%20India.%20The%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livemint.com%2Fnews%2Findia%2Fgyanvapi-mosque-controversy-why-archaeological-survey-of-the-religious-site-was-requested-11690179229101.html%23%3A~%3Atext%3DThe%2520case%2520involves%2520a%2520dispute%2CVishwanath%2520temple%2520demolished%2520by%2520Aurangzeb.%5C%22%3EGyanvapi%20mosque%3C%2Fa%3E%20controversy%20in%20Varanasi%2C%20the%20case%20against%20Mathura%E2%80%99s%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fnews%2Fhow-to%2Fkrishna-what-is-mathuras-shahi-idgah-mosque-case-in-which-bhagwan-krishnas-friend-is-also-a-petitioner%2Farticleshow%2F106045278.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3EShahi%20Idgah%20mosque%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheprint.in%2Findia%2Fdatta-peetha-bababudangiri-how-karnatakas-hindu-muslim-shrine-became-ayodhya-of-the-south%2F786719%2F%5C%22%3EBaba%20Budangiri%20Idgah%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Karnataka%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fconstant-attempt-to-erode-medieval-architecture-heritage-historians-org-on-sunehri-bagh-mosque%5C%22%3ESunheri%20mosque%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Delhi%2C%20and%20many%20similar%20Islamic%20shrines%20have%20become%20suitable%20sites%20to%20keep%20India%20perpetually%20polarised%20along%20religious%20lines.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWho%20else%20but%20the%20biggest%20opposition%20party%20can%20counter%20such%20a%20narrative%3F%20The%20Congress%20needs%20to%20own%20its%20politics%20unapologetically%2C%20display%20an%20ethical%20strength%20to%20oppose%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20majoritarian%20narrative%2C%20and%20give%20voice%20to%20the%20voiceless%20of%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20Naya%20Bharat.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPrafulla%20Ketkar%2C%20editor%20of%20the%20Rashtriya%20Swayamsevak%20Sangh%E2%80%99s%20mouthpiece%20%3Cem%3EOrganiser%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20candidly%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Forganiser.org%2F2024%2F01%2F08%2F215029%2Fbharat%2Fram-mandir-ayodhya-reconstruction-of-national-consciousness%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Epointed%20out%20in%20his%20latest%20editorial%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20the%20celebrations%20by%20the%20Sangh%20%3Cem%3Eparivar%3C%2Fem%3E%20for%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Epran-pratishta%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E(consecration%20ceremony)%20of%20Ram%20Lalla%20in%20Ayodhya%20were%20not%20simply%20the%20culmination%20of%20the%20decades-old%20Ram%20Janmabhoomi%20movement%2C%20but%20the%20beginning%20of%20a%20%E2%80%9Creconstruction%20of%20national%20consciousness%E2%80%9D%2C%20a%20process%20where%20economic%20growth%20is%20necessarily%20accompanied%20by%20the%20so-called%20Hindu%20cultural%20resurgence.%20In%20other%20words%2C%20Ketkar%20believes%20that%20the%20consecration%20ceremony%20was%20a%20surefooted%20step%20towards%20%E2%80%9Creclaiming%E2%80%9D%20Indian%20civilisation%20from%20the%20clutches%20of%20Enlightenment%20values%20on%20which%20our%20founding%20fathers%20sought%20to%20build%20an%20independent%20India.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20was%20India%E2%80%99s%20first%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%2C%20who%20dived%20into%20the%20values%20of%20Enlightenment%20~%20rule%20of%20law%2C%20liberty%2C%20equality%2C%20fraternity%2C%20progress%2C%20tolerance%2C%20constitutional%20government%20pursuit%20of%20knowledge%2C%20and%20most%20importantly%2C%20separation%20of%20state%20and%20religion%20%E2%80%93%20to%20dream%20of%20a%20truly%20modern%20India.%20The%20religious%20polarisation%20around%20the%20Ayodhya%20event%20may%20be%20an%20appropriate%20moment%20for%20the%20grand-old%20party%20to%20reconnect%20with%20its%20roots%20and%20stand%20up%20on%20its%20own%20feet%20%E2%80%93%20at%20least%20for%20the%2060%25%20of%20Indian%20people%20who%20did%20not%20vote%20for%20the%20majoritarian%20politics%20of%20the%20BJP.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20decision%20of%20the%20topmost%20Congress%20leaders%20to%20decline%20invitation%20to%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Epran-pratishtha%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20ceremony%20in%20Ayodhya%20has%20shown%20that%20the%20grand-old%20party%20can%20still%20think%20beyond%20narrow%20electoral%20politics%2C%20and%20can%20build%20and%20consolidate%20an%20ideological%20opposition%20to%20mindless%20majoritarianism%20of%20the%20Sangh%20%3Cem%3Eparivar%3C%2Fem%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704893534000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F17172550%2FF6NXWAsXUAAXN2b.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fwhy-congress-clearly-saying-january-22-is-part-of-rss-bjps-political-project-matters%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Congress%20needs%20to%20own%20its%20politics%20unapologetically%2C%20display%20an%20ethical%20strength%20to%20oppose%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20majoritarianism%2C%20and%20give%20voice%20to%20the%20voiceless%20of%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20Naya%20Bharat.%20Who%20else%20but%20the%20biggest%20opposition%20party%20can%20counter%20a%20narrow%2C%20polarising%20narrative%20of%20the%20BJP%3F%22%2C%22a